WEBVTT

01:18.479 --> 01:20.514
Oppenheimer Dk.

01:21.515 --> 01:22.717
Oppenheimer Dk.

01:24.052 --> 01:25.653
As we begin, I believe you have

01:25.686 --> 01:27.688
a statement to read
into the record.

01:29.523 --> 01:30.725
Yes, Wako Honor.

01:30.758 --> 01:32.861
We're
not judges, Daktari.

01:32.895 --> 01:33.929
Hapana.

01:35.030 --> 01:36.430
Bila shaka.

01:41.636 --> 01:44.572
Members of the security board,

01:44.605 --> 01:46.909
the so-called
habari za dharau

01:46.942 --> 01:49.845
in your indictment of me
cannot be fairly understood,

01:49.878 --> 01:53.714
except in the context
of my life and my work.

01:54.682 --> 01:56.919
How
long did he testify?

01:56.952 --> 01:58.686
Honestly, I forget.

02:00.088 --> 02:02.057
The whole hearing took a month.

02:02.090 --> 02:03.524
An ordeal, hmm?

02:03.557 --> 02:05.227
Naam, I've only read
the transcripts.

02:07.795 --> 02:09.530
Who'd want to justify
their whole life?

02:09.562 --> 02:10.798
Wewe weren't there?

02:10.832 --> 02:13.135
As chairman, I
wasn't allowed to be.

02:13.168 --> 02:15.736
Are they really going
to ask about it?

02:15.770 --> 02:17.873
- It was years ago.
- Four years ago...

02:17.906 --> 02:18.941
Five.

02:19.808 --> 02:21.542
Oppenheimer still
divides America.

02:21.575 --> 02:23.946
The committee is gonna want
to know where you stood.

02:23.979 --> 02:26.081
Senator Thurmond asked me to say

02:26.114 --> 02:27.950
not to feel that
you're on trial.

02:27.983 --> 02:31.519
Oh, funny, I didn't
till you just said that.

02:31.552 --> 02:33.155
- Really, Mr. Strauss...
- It's Admiral.

02:33.188 --> 02:36.124
Um, Admiral Strauss.
This is a formality.

02:36.158 --> 02:38.659
Rais Eisenhower has asked
you to be in his cabinet.

02:38.693 --> 02:40.561
Senate really has no
choice but to confirm you.

02:40.594 --> 02:42.831
And if they bring
up Oppenheimer?

02:42.864 --> 02:45.233
When they bring up Oppenheimer,
you answer honestly.

02:45.267 --> 02:47.668
No senator can deny
you did your duty.

02:47.702 --> 02:49.838
It'll be uncomfortable.

02:49.871 --> 02:52.007
Who'd want to justify
their whole life?

02:56.945 --> 02:59.647
Why did you
leave Marekani?

03:01.749 --> 03:05.153
I, uh... I wanted to
study the new physics.

03:05.187 --> 03:06.721
Was there nowhere here?

03:06.754 --> 03:08.756
I thought Berkeley
had the leading

03:08.789 --> 03:10.624
theoretical physics department.

03:10.658 --> 03:13.228
Ndiyo. Once I built it.

03:13.261 --> 03:14.863
Lakini first I had to go to Europe.

03:14.896 --> 03:18.266
I went to Cambridge to study
under Patrick Blackett.

03:18.300 --> 03:20.902
Were you happier
there than in America?

03:20.936 --> 03:23.071
- Happier?
- Ndiyo.

03:27.042 --> 03:30.045
Hapana. No, I, uh...

03:33.048 --> 03:34.883
<i>I was homesick, um...</i>

03:35.750 --> 03:37.718
emotionally immature...

03:38.887 --> 03:44.026
<i>troubled by visions
of a hidden universe.</i>

03:55.070 --> 03:56.905
Useless in the lab.

04:01.943 --> 04:04.046
Christ, Oppenheimer.

04:04.079 --> 04:06.148
Have you had any sleep?

04:07.949 --> 04:09.184
Start again.

04:09.217 --> 04:11.719
I need to go to
the lecture, sir.

04:11.752 --> 04:13.155
Why?

04:13.188 --> 04:15.090
It's Niels Bohr.

04:17.892 --> 04:19.593
Damn,
completely forgot.

04:19.627 --> 04:21.829
Sawa. Let's go.

04:24.166 --> 04:26.077
Oh, no, not you, Oppenheimer.

04:26.101 --> 04:27.211
Wewe finish coating those plates.

04:27.235 --> 04:29.071
Wewe see them?

04:34.642 --> 04:36.610
Don't
forget to clean up!

05:07.775 --> 05:11.712
<i>Quantum physics
is not a step forward,</i>

05:11.745 --> 05:15.250
it is a new way to
understand reality.

05:15.283 --> 05:18.854
Einstein's opened the door,
now we are peering through,

05:18.887 --> 05:21.789
seeing a world inside our world.

05:21.823 --> 05:27.229
A world of energy and paradox
that not everyone can accept.

06:09.337 --> 06:10.771
Yeah, definitely.

06:10.805 --> 06:12.174
Je! all right?

06:13.408 --> 06:15.243
Niels, meet J.
Robert Oppenheimer.

06:15.277 --> 06:16.777
What's the
"J" stand for?

06:16.811 --> 06:18.779
Nothing, apparently.

06:18.813 --> 06:19.915
Wewe were at my lecture.

06:19.948 --> 06:21.349
Wewe asked the only
good question.

06:21.383 --> 06:23.118
No one's
denying his insight.

06:23.151 --> 06:25.229
It's his laboratory work that
leaves a little to be desired.

06:25.253 --> 06:27.093
I heard you
give the same lecture...

06:27.122 --> 06:30.325
At Harvard, yes, and you
asked the same question.

06:30.358 --> 06:31.459
Why ask again?

06:31.493 --> 06:33.094
Hadn't liked your answer.

06:34.462 --> 06:36.198
Did you like it
better yesterday?

06:36.231 --> 06:37.499
A lot.

06:37.532 --> 06:39.434
Wewe can lift the stone
without being ready

06:39.467 --> 06:41.836
for the snake that's revealed.

06:41.870 --> 06:44.005
Now it seems you're ready.

06:44.039 --> 06:46.341
Lakini you don't enjoy the lab?

06:46.374 --> 06:49.244
So get out of Cambridge with
its beakers and potions.

06:49.277 --> 06:52.247
Go somewhere they let you think.

06:53.248 --> 06:54.883
Wapi?

06:55.517 --> 06:56.518
Göttingen.

06:56.551 --> 06:58.486
- Born?
- Born.

06:58.520 --> 07:00.488
Get to Germany,
study under Max Born.

07:00.522 --> 07:03.158
Learn the ways of theory.

07:03.191 --> 07:04.226
I'll send word.

07:05.860 --> 07:07.963
Wormhole.

07:07.996 --> 07:09.364
How's your mathematics?

07:09.397 --> 07:11.366
Not good enough for the
physicist he wants to be.

07:11.399 --> 07:13.969
Algebra's like sheet music.

07:14.002 --> 07:16.471
The important thing isn't
"Can you read music?"

07:16.504 --> 07:17.505
It's "Can you hear it?"

07:17.539 --> 07:20.842
Can you hear the music, Robert?

07:21.810 --> 07:23.378
Yes, I can.

08:59.107 --> 09:00.608
The senator from Wyoming.

09:01.576 --> 09:04.045
Admiral Strauss, I'm
interested in your relationship

09:04.079 --> 09:06.948
with Dkt. J. Robert Oppenheimer.

09:06.981 --> 09:08.583
Wewe met him in 1947?

09:08.616 --> 09:09.584
Correct.

09:09.617 --> 09:11.386
Wewe were commissioner

09:11.419 --> 09:12.987
of the Tume ya Nishati ya Atomiki?

09:13.021 --> 09:16.958
I was, but I-I actually
met Robert in my capacity

09:16.991 --> 09:19.661
as board member of the
Institute for Advanced Study

09:19.694 --> 09:21.496
at Princeton because

09:21.529 --> 09:24.165
after the war, he
was world-renowned

09:24.199 --> 09:26.601
as the great man of physics,
and I was determined

09:26.634 --> 09:29.337
to get him to run the Institute.

09:38.513 --> 09:41.583
Oppenheimer Dk. An honor.

09:41.616 --> 09:42.951
Mr. Strauss.

09:42.984 --> 09:44.285
It's pronounced "straws."

09:45.186 --> 09:46.654
Oh-ppenheimer,
Oppenheimer.

09:46.688 --> 09:48.556
Whatever way you say it,
they know I'm Jewish.

09:50.091 --> 09:52.694
I'm president of Temple
Emanu-El in Manhattan.

09:52.727 --> 09:54.996
"Straws" is just the
Southern pronunciation.

09:55.029 --> 09:56.064
- Ah.
- Anyway,

09:56.097 --> 09:57.532
welcome to the Institute.

09:57.565 --> 09:59.200
I think you could
be very happy here.

09:59.234 --> 10:01.169
Yes, well, you'll
love the commute.

10:01.202 --> 10:02.537
The position comes
with that house

10:02.570 --> 10:04.038
for you and your wife

10:04.072 --> 10:06.241
and your, is it two children?

10:06.274 --> 10:07.075
Yes, two.

10:07.108 --> 10:10.044
I'm a great admirer
of your work.

10:10.078 --> 10:12.280
And you're a physicist
by training, Mr. Strauss?

10:12.313 --> 10:14.382
I'm sorry, uh,
common room 4:00 tea.

10:14.416 --> 10:17.185
No, I'm not trained in
physics or anything else.

10:17.218 --> 10:19.053
- I'm a self-made man.
- Ah.

10:19.087 --> 10:21.089
- I can relate to that.
- Really?

10:21.122 --> 10:23.458
Yes, my father was moja.

10:23.491 --> 10:27.061
And this would be your office.

10:36.237 --> 10:38.173
naambiwa he's there
most afternoons.

10:38.206 --> 10:40.308
Wewe know, Nimewahi wondered

10:40.341 --> 10:43.945
why you didn't involve him
in the Manhattan Project.

10:44.712 --> 10:48.216
Greatest scientific
mind of our time.

10:48.249 --> 10:50.118
Of his time.

10:50.151 --> 10:52.187
Einstein published his
Theory of Relativity

10:52.220 --> 10:55.156
more than 40 years ago now.

10:56.224 --> 10:58.660
Lakini never embraced the
quantum world it revealed.

10:58.693 --> 11:00.228
"God doesn't play dice."

11:00.261 --> 11:02.230
Precisely.

11:02.263 --> 11:05.066
Wewe never thought of studying
physics formally, Mr. Strauss?

11:05.099 --> 11:07.469
Naam, I had offers, but
I chose to sell shoes.

11:07.502 --> 11:11.005
Lewis Strauss was once
a lowly shoe salesman.

11:11.773 --> 11:13.675
No, just a shoe salesman.

11:13.708 --> 11:15.977
Huh.

11:17.245 --> 11:20.014
- I'd love to introduce you.
- No need.

11:21.115 --> 11:22.584
I have known him for years.

11:43.806 --> 11:45.507
Albert.

11:50.111 --> 11:54.315
Hiyo ilikuwa nini? What
did you say to him?

11:56.451 --> 11:57.485
Oh, he's fine.

11:59.354 --> 12:02.657
Mr. Strauss, there
are things in my past

12:02.690 --> 12:04.192
you ought to be aware of.

12:04.225 --> 12:06.127
Naam, as chairman of the AEC,

12:06.160 --> 12:07.629
I have access to
your faili ya usalama.

12:07.662 --> 12:08.663
I've read it.

12:08.696 --> 12:10.265
- Wewe ni not worried?
- Hapana.

12:10.298 --> 12:11.675
Why would I be worried
after everything

12:11.699 --> 12:13.167
you've done for your country?

12:13.201 --> 12:14.669
Naam, times change, Mr. Strauss.

12:14.702 --> 12:16.538
Naam, the purpose
of this institute

12:16.571 --> 12:19.240
is to provide a haven
for independent minds.

12:20.174 --> 12:23.177
Hiyo ni you. Wewe are
the man for the job.

12:23.211 --> 12:25.814
Naam, then I'll consider it.

12:25.848 --> 12:28.116
I'll see you at the
AEC meeting tomorrow.

12:32.520 --> 12:34.088
This is one of the
most prestigious

12:34.122 --> 12:35.858
appointments nchini.

12:35.891 --> 12:38.092
Yes, with a great commute.

12:38.126 --> 12:40.428
Hiyo ni why I'm considering it.

12:40.461 --> 12:42.230
<i>So,
Oppenheimer Dk brought</i>

12:42.263 --> 12:44.666
<i>your attention to
his past associations</i>

12:44.699 --> 12:45.834
<i>before you appointed him?</i>

12:45.868 --> 12:47.302
Ndiyo.

12:47.335 --> 12:49.170
And it didn't concern you?

12:49.203 --> 12:50.738
Just then, I was
entirely consumed

12:50.772 --> 12:54.542
with nini he must have said
to Einstein to sour him on me.

12:58.146 --> 12:59.347
Lakini later?

12:59.380 --> 13:01.316
Naam, we all know
nini happened later.

13:01.349 --> 13:03.718
Doctor, your, uh...
your time in Europe,

13:03.751 --> 13:05.320
you seemed to meet
with a wide range

13:05.353 --> 13:06.788
of other countries' physicists.

13:06.822 --> 13:07.823
Yes, that's right.

13:07.856 --> 13:10.124
Any Russians?

13:11.192 --> 13:12.627
None that spring to mind.

13:12.660 --> 13:15.563
If you'll just allow me to
continue with my statement...

13:15.597 --> 13:18.566
Mr. Robb, you'll have ample
opportunity to cross-examine.

13:20.803 --> 13:23.738
After Göttingen, I
moved on to Leiden in Holland

13:23.771 --> 13:26.809
<i>where I first met Je!idor Rabi.</i>

13:26.842 --> 13:29.344
Excuse me.

13:33.281 --> 13:35.617
A Yank, lecturing
on the new physics?

13:35.650 --> 13:36.718
This I have to hear.

13:36.751 --> 13:38.786
I'm an American myself.

13:38.821 --> 13:40.321
How surprising.

13:40.355 --> 13:41.422
Um...

13:41.456 --> 13:43.725
Let me know if you need
any help with the English.

13:57.705 --> 13:59.674
Wait, nini's he saying?

14:10.218 --> 14:11.252
No, thank you.

14:11.285 --> 14:13.254
It's a long way to Zurich.

14:13.287 --> 14:14.927
Wewe get any skinnier,
we're gonna lose you

14:14.957 --> 14:16.791
between the seat cushions.

14:16.825 --> 14:17.860
I'm Rabi.

14:17.893 --> 14:19.260
Oppenheimer.

14:19.293 --> 14:21.329
I caught your
lecture on molecules.

14:21.362 --> 14:22.497
Caught some of it.

14:23.631 --> 14:25.800
We're a couple of New York
Jews. How do you know Dutch?

14:25.834 --> 14:27.402
Naam, I thought
I'd better learn it

14:27.435 --> 14:28.612
when I got here this semester.

14:28.636 --> 14:30.238
Wewe learned enough
Dutch in six weeks

14:30.271 --> 14:31.974
to give a lecture on
quantum mechanics?

14:32.007 --> 14:33.508
Wanted to challenge myself.

14:33.541 --> 14:35.911
Quantum physics wasn't
challenging enough.

14:35.944 --> 14:37.679
<i>- Schvitzer.
- Schvitzer?</i>

14:37.712 --> 14:39.614
Show-off.

14:39.647 --> 14:41.492
Dutch in six weeks, but
you never learned Yiddish?

14:41.516 --> 14:43.584
They don't speak it so
much my side of the park.

14:43.618 --> 14:44.686
Screw you.

14:45.787 --> 14:47.288
Wewe homesick?

14:47.321 --> 14:48.723
Oh, you know it.

14:49.691 --> 14:52.694
Ever get the feeling our kind
isn't entirely welcome here?

14:52.727 --> 14:53.795
Physicists?

14:53.829 --> 14:55.329
'S funny.

14:55.363 --> 14:57.432
Not in the department.

14:57.465 --> 14:58.766
They're all Jewish too.

15:00.869 --> 15:02.270
Kula.

15:04.572 --> 15:06.708
There's a German you
have to seek out.

15:07.742 --> 15:10.278
- Heisenberg.
- Sawa.

15:19.454 --> 15:20.956
One might be led
to the presumption

15:20.989 --> 15:23.458
that behind the quantum world,

15:23.491 --> 15:27.361
there still hides a real world
in which causality holds,

15:27.395 --> 15:29.597
but such speculation seem to us,

15:29.630 --> 15:32.366
to say it explicitly,
fruitless. Asante.

15:32.400 --> 15:33.836
Have a great day.

15:39.041 --> 15:40.742
- Wonderful.
- Asante.

15:40.775 --> 15:42.010
Oppenheimer Dk.

15:42.044 --> 15:43.979
Oppenheimer, yes.

15:44.012 --> 15:45.881
I liked your paper on molecules.

15:45.914 --> 15:47.415
Probably because
you inspired it.

15:47.448 --> 15:48.960
If I inspire anything
else, let me know.

15:48.984 --> 15:50.024
We could publish together.

15:50.052 --> 15:51.887
I have to get back to America.

15:51.920 --> 15:53.654
Why? There's no one there

15:53.688 --> 15:55.891
taking quantum
mechanics seriously.

15:55.924 --> 15:57.525
Hiyo ni exactly why.

15:57.558 --> 15:59.995
He's pining for the
canyons of Manhattan.

16:00.028 --> 16:02.463
Canyons of New Mexico.

16:02.497 --> 16:03.640
- Wewe ni from New Mexico?
- Hapana.

16:03.664 --> 16:05.767
New York, but my brother
and I have a ranch

16:05.800 --> 16:07.903
outside Santa Fe.

16:07.936 --> 16:10.304
Hiyo ni the America
I miss right now.

16:10.338 --> 16:12.406
Then it's best you
get home, cowboys.

16:12.440 --> 16:14.052
Hiyo ni him.

16:14.076 --> 16:17.512
No, me and horses.
Sidhani hivyo.

16:17.545 --> 16:19.680
Nice to meet you.

16:21.415 --> 16:23.551
Did you ever encounter
Heisenberg again?

16:23.584 --> 16:26.487
Not in person, no, but, uh...

16:27.722 --> 16:29.825
you might say our paths crossed.

16:31.392 --> 16:33.594
On returning to America,
I accepted positions

16:33.628 --> 16:36.364
at both Caltech
and up at Berkeley.

16:40.068 --> 16:41.702
I got it,
it's all right.

17:00.421 --> 17:02.456
Dr. Lawrence,
I presume?

17:03.859 --> 17:05.093
Wewe must be Oppenheimer.

17:05.127 --> 17:06.661
Ndiyo.

17:06.694 --> 17:09.031
I hear you want to start a
school of quantum theory.

17:09.064 --> 17:10.731
I am starting it. Next door.

17:10.765 --> 17:12.599
- They put you in there?
- I asked for it.

17:12.633 --> 17:14.702
Wanted to be close to
you experimentalists.

17:14.734 --> 17:17.105
Theory will get you
only so far, huh?

17:17.138 --> 17:19.107
We're building a machine
to accelerate electrons.

17:19.141 --> 17:21.844
- Magnificent.
- Would you like to help?

17:21.877 --> 17:23.711
Build it? Oh, no.

17:23.743 --> 17:24.847
No, no.

17:24.880 --> 17:27.448
Lakini I am working on theories
Ningependa test with it.

17:27.481 --> 17:28.492
When do you start teaching?

17:28.516 --> 17:30.384
I've got my first in an hour.

17:30.418 --> 17:32.420
- Seminar?
- Pupil.

17:32.453 --> 17:35.690
One student? Hiyo ni?

17:35.723 --> 17:38.459
I'm teaching something no
one here has dreamt of.

17:38.492 --> 17:40.504
Lakini once people start hearing
nini you can do with it...

17:40.528 --> 17:41.997
There's no going back.

17:44.166 --> 17:46.467
- Oh. I must have missed the...
- Ah. Lo...

17:46.500 --> 17:48.502
- Mr. Lomanitz?
- Na.

17:49.704 --> 17:50.605
Ndiyo.

17:50.638 --> 17:52.740
Yes, this is it. Tafadhali.

17:52.773 --> 17:53.842
Take a seat.

17:58.713 --> 18:00.514
What do you know about
quantum mechanics?

18:00.548 --> 18:02.918
I have a grasp on the basics.

18:02.951 --> 18:04.518
Then you're doing it wrong.

18:05.753 --> 18:08.023
Je! light made up of
particles or waves?

18:08.056 --> 18:09.200
Quantum mechanics
says it's both.

18:09.224 --> 18:10.826
How could it be both?

18:10.859 --> 18:12.760
- It can't.
- It can't.

18:12.793 --> 18:17.665
Lakini it is. It's paradoxical,
and yet, it works.

18:24.806 --> 18:25.807
Now.

18:27.675 --> 18:29.644
Asante.

18:29.677 --> 18:32.680
Mr. Lomanitz. Wewe ni
gonna be okay.

18:32.713 --> 18:34.082
Mr. Snyder.

18:34.116 --> 18:35.650
Now let's consider a star.

18:35.683 --> 18:39.221
A star. A vast furnace
burning in outer space,

18:39.254 --> 18:42.657
fire pushing outwards
against its own gravity.

18:42.690 --> 18:44.126
Balanced.

18:44.159 --> 18:46.460
Lakini if that furnace cools...

18:47.829 --> 18:49.831
and gravity starts
winning, it contracts.

18:50.832 --> 18:51.799
Density increases.

18:51.833 --> 18:53.035
Correct.

18:53.068 --> 18:54.236
Increasing gravity.

18:54.269 --> 18:55.770
Increasing density.

18:55.804 --> 18:57.940
- And?
- It's a vicious cycle until...

18:57.973 --> 18:59.607
nini's the limit here?

19:00.775 --> 19:03.011
sijui.
See where the math takes us.

19:03.045 --> 19:04.822
I guarantee it's somewhere
no one's been before.

19:04.846 --> 19:06.747
Me?

19:06.781 --> 19:08.951
Yes, you. Wako math
is better than mine.

19:10.685 --> 19:12.787
<i>Oppenheimer Dk's file</i>

19:12.821 --> 19:15.223
<i>contained detail of his
activities in Berkeley.</i>

19:15.257 --> 19:16.724
Why would they
have started a file

19:16.757 --> 19:19.694
on Oppenheimer Dk
before the war?

19:19.727 --> 19:22.197
Naam, you'd have
to ask Mr. Hoover.

19:22.230 --> 19:24.099
I'm asking you, Admiral Strauss.

19:24.132 --> 19:27.069
Uh, my assumption is that

19:27.102 --> 19:30.238
it was connected to his, uh,

19:30.272 --> 19:32.808
left-wing political activities.

19:33.909 --> 19:35.585
Wewe shouldn't
let them bring up politics

19:35.609 --> 19:36.945
in the classroom, Oppie.

19:36.979 --> 19:38.713
I wrote that.

19:38.746 --> 19:42.017
Lawrence, you embrace the
revolution in physics.

19:42.050 --> 19:43.852
Can't you see it
everywhere else?

19:43.885 --> 19:45.988
Picasso, Stravinsky,
Freud, Marx.

19:46.021 --> 19:47.621
Naam, this
is America, Oppie.

19:47.655 --> 19:49.024
We had our revolution.

19:50.158 --> 19:52.660
Seriously, keep
it out of the lab.

19:52.693 --> 19:55.796
Naam, out of the
lab, my landlady

19:55.831 --> 19:58.632
is having a discussion
group tonight. Interested?

19:58.666 --> 20:00.735
I have sampled the
Berkeley political scene.

20:00.768 --> 20:02.804
It's all just
philosophy post-grads

20:02.838 --> 20:05.140
and Communists
talking integration.

20:05.173 --> 20:06.842
Wewe don't care
about integration.

20:06.875 --> 20:08.743
I want to vote for
it, not talk about it.

20:08.776 --> 20:10.778
'Specially on a Friday.
Come on, let's eat.

20:10.812 --> 20:13.148
I'm meeting
my brother there.

20:13.181 --> 20:15.059
<i>And how
would these activities</i>

20:15.083 --> 20:16.218
<i>have come to the attention</i>

20:16.251 --> 20:17.252
of the FBI?

20:17.285 --> 20:19.254
Naam, if I remember correctly,

20:19.287 --> 20:21.223
the FBI was taking
license plates

20:21.256 --> 20:23.591
outside suspected
Communist gatherings,

20:23.624 --> 20:25.626
<i>and his name popped up.</i>

20:33.201 --> 20:34.735
- Gotcha!
- Jesus Christ.

20:34.769 --> 20:37.072
- Pole. Hi, brother.
- Frank.

20:38.073 --> 20:39.808
Uh, you remember Jackie.

20:39.841 --> 20:41.309
Jioni.

20:41.343 --> 20:43.311
Let's go. Come.

20:43.345 --> 20:45.914
Right over there,
right over there.

20:46.848 --> 20:49.851
Robert. I want you
to meet Chevalier.

20:49.885 --> 20:53.587
Dr. Haakon Chevalier,
Dr. Robert Oppenheimer.

20:53.621 --> 20:54.789
- Pleasure.
- Pleasure.

20:54.823 --> 20:56.124
This is my little
brother, Frank.

20:56.158 --> 20:57.359
- And this is...
- Hello.

20:57.392 --> 20:59.327
- Still Jackie.
- Hello, Still Jackie.

20:59.361 --> 21:01.329
Chevalier, you're in languages?

21:01.363 --> 21:03.098
And your reputation
precedes you.

21:03.131 --> 21:04.866
- What have you heard?
- Excuse me.

21:04.900 --> 21:06.676
That you're teaching a radical
new approach to physics

21:06.700 --> 21:07.945
I have no chance
of understanding,

21:07.969 --> 21:09.347
but I hadn't heard
you're a Party member.

21:09.371 --> 21:11.672
- Uh, I'm not.
- Oh, not yet.

21:11.705 --> 21:13.683
Frank and I are thinking of
joining. Just the other day,

21:13.707 --> 21:15.353
- I was saying...
- I support a range of causes.

21:15.377 --> 21:17.012
The
Spanish Civil War?

21:17.045 --> 21:18.779
A democratic republic
being overthrown

21:18.814 --> 21:20.115
by fascist thugs, who wouldn't?

21:20.148 --> 21:21.817
Our government.

21:21.850 --> 21:23.327
They think that socialism is
a bigger threat than fascism.

21:23.351 --> 21:24.853
Not for long.

21:24.886 --> 21:26.687
Look at nini the Nazis
are doing to the Jews.

21:26.720 --> 21:29.291
I send funds to colleagues
in Germany to emigrate.

21:29.324 --> 21:31.359
I have to do something.

21:31.393 --> 21:34.762
My own work
is so abstract.

21:34.795 --> 21:36.364
What are you working on?

21:36.398 --> 21:38.333
What happens to the
stars when they die.

21:38.366 --> 21:39.800
Do stars die?

21:41.002 --> 21:42.304
Naam, if they do,

21:42.337 --> 21:44.239
they'd cool, then collapse.

21:44.272 --> 21:46.908
In fact, the bigger the star,

21:46.942 --> 21:49.643
<i>the more violent its demise.</i>

21:49.677 --> 21:51.213
The gravity gets so concentrated

21:51.246 --> 21:54.216
it swallows everything.

21:54.249 --> 21:55.217
Everything, even light.

21:55.250 --> 21:56.418
Can that really happen?

21:56.451 --> 21:58.253
The math says it can.

21:58.286 --> 21:59.720
If we can get published,

21:59.753 --> 22:01.332
then perhaps one day,
an astronomer finds moja.

22:01.356 --> 22:03.091
Lakini right now, all
I have is theory,

22:03.125 --> 22:04.993
which can't impact
people's lives.

22:05.026 --> 22:07.295
Naam, if you're going
to send money to Spain,

22:07.329 --> 22:08.897
do it through the
Communist Party.

22:08.930 --> 22:10.274
They can get it to
the front lines.

22:10.298 --> 22:12.700
Mary sent me with these.

22:13.401 --> 22:16.204
- I'm Jean.
- Robert.

22:16.238 --> 22:17.738
Haakon Chevalier.

22:17.771 --> 22:19.317
The union meeting at
Serber's last month?

22:19.341 --> 22:20.741
Right, right, yes.

22:20.774 --> 22:22.144
Oh, thank you.

22:22.177 --> 22:24.412
Robert here
says he's not a Communist.

22:24.446 --> 22:26.747
Naam, then he doesn't
know enough about it.

22:26.780 --> 22:29.151
Oh, I've read <i>Das Kapital,</i>
all three volumes.

22:29.184 --> 22:30.819
Does that count?

22:30.852 --> 22:32.830
It would make you better
read than most party members.

22:32.854 --> 22:35.157
Turgid stuff. There's
some thinking, um,

22:35.190 --> 22:36.358
"Ownership is theft."

22:36.391 --> 22:38.293
- "Property."
- "Property"?

22:38.326 --> 22:40.128
"Property," not "ownership."

22:40.162 --> 22:42.197
I'm sorry, I read it
in the original German.

22:42.230 --> 22:44.900
Well.

22:45.766 --> 22:47.135
It's not about the book.

22:47.169 --> 22:50.172
It's about the ideas. And
you sound uncommitted.

22:50.205 --> 22:51.840
Naam, I'm committed
to thinking freely

22:51.873 --> 22:54.309
about how to improve our world.

22:54.342 --> 22:56.444
Why limit yourself to one dogma?

22:56.478 --> 22:59.447
Wewe ni a physicist, you
pick and choose rules?

22:59.481 --> 23:01.049
Or do you use the discipline

23:01.082 --> 23:03.218
to channel your
energies into progress?

23:03.251 --> 23:05.654
I like a little wiggle room.

23:06.754 --> 23:08.957
Do you always tow
the party line?

23:10.325 --> 23:12.093
I like my wiggle room too.

23:22.237 --> 23:24.772
Je!

23:24.806 --> 23:25.974
Wait, wait, wait.

23:29.878 --> 23:31.479
Unexpected.

23:31.513 --> 23:33.415
- Je!
- For a physicist.

23:33.448 --> 23:36.218
Wewe only have a
shelf full of Freud?

23:36.251 --> 23:39.120
Naam, actually, my
background's more...

23:39.154 --> 23:40.989
Uh, Jungian?

23:42.123 --> 23:43.225
Wewe know analysis?

23:43.258 --> 23:45.793
When I was in
post-grad at Cambridge,

23:45.827 --> 23:47.128
I had a little trouble.

23:48.129 --> 23:50.865
- I'll bite.
- I tried to poison my tutor.

23:50.899 --> 23:51.900
Did you hate him?

23:51.933 --> 23:53.401
I liked him very much.

23:53.435 --> 23:55.337
Wewe just needed to get laid.

23:55.370 --> 23:56.938
Took my analyst two years,

23:56.972 --> 23:58.916
and I don't think they ever
put it that succinctly.

23:58.940 --> 24:00.275
Wewe have everyone convinced

24:00.308 --> 24:03.044
you're more complicated
than you actually are.

24:03.078 --> 24:05.080
We're all simple souls, I guess.

24:05.113 --> 24:06.281
I'm not.

24:09.150 --> 24:10.185
What's this?

24:10.218 --> 24:11.785
Sanskrit.

24:11.820 --> 24:13.121
Wewe can read this?

24:13.154 --> 24:14.956
I'm learning.

24:19.160 --> 24:20.962
Read this.

24:22.397 --> 24:24.032
Naam, in this part,

24:24.065 --> 24:26.268
Vishnu reveals his
multi-armed self...

24:26.301 --> 24:27.302
Hapana.

24:28.370 --> 24:30.238
Read the words.

24:33.608 --> 24:36.777
"Na sasa Nimekuwa Kifo.

24:42.217 --> 24:43.952
Destroyer of worlds."

25:14.883 --> 25:16.217
This'll do.

25:22.357 --> 25:23.958
Itapambazuka kabla ya mapambazuko.

25:23.992 --> 25:27.362
Air cools overnight, just
before dawn, it breaks.

25:30.031 --> 25:31.966
Come.

25:38.006 --> 25:41.476
Ah. So, I'm getting married.

25:41.509 --> 25:43.111
- Frank. Congratulations!
- Asante.

25:43.144 --> 25:44.946
- Asante.
- To Jackie?

25:44.979 --> 25:47.349
Yeah, to Jackie.

25:47.382 --> 25:48.483
The waitress.

25:48.516 --> 25:50.485
Oppie, you're right.
It's lettin' up.

25:50.518 --> 25:52.954
I'm gonna go see if
there's any stars.

25:52.987 --> 25:55.023
All your talk about
the common man,

25:55.056 --> 25:56.567
but Jackie's not good
enough for you, hmm?

25:56.591 --> 25:57.625
Mm-mm.

25:57.659 --> 25:59.160
We join the Party and you can't

25:59.194 --> 26:00.962
- hide your disapproval. Why?
- Oh, now, I...

26:00.995 --> 26:02.073
Je! that because that's
supposed to be your thing?

26:02.097 --> 26:03.631
I haven't joined
the Party, Frank.

26:03.665 --> 26:06.201
And I don't think she should
have convinced you to either.

26:06.234 --> 26:07.969
Half of the faculty
is Communist.

26:08.002 --> 26:09.070
Not that half.

26:10.405 --> 26:13.141
I'm your brother, Frank, and
I want you to be cautious.

26:13.174 --> 26:14.876
And I want to wring your neck.

26:17.278 --> 26:20.181
I won't live my life
afraid to make a mistake.

26:22.050 --> 26:25.387
Una furaha, nina furaha.

26:25.420 --> 26:26.955
So then I'm happy you're happy

26:26.988 --> 26:28.323
that I'm happy.

26:32.594 --> 26:34.195
I feel
like I could see

26:34.229 --> 26:36.331
one of those dark stars
that you're working on.

26:36.364 --> 26:38.933
Wewe can't. Hiyo ni
the whole point.

26:39.601 --> 26:41.302
Their gravity swallows light.

26:42.570 --> 26:45.640
It's like a kind
of hole in space.

26:45.673 --> 26:47.008
Je! Frank okay?

26:47.041 --> 26:49.444
Ndiyo. He just has
a shitty brother.

26:50.578 --> 26:52.247
It is special here.

26:54.616 --> 26:57.085
When I was a kid,

26:57.118 --> 27:00.155
I thought if I could find a way

27:00.188 --> 27:04.559
to combine physics
and New Mexico,

27:04.592 --> 27:07.128
my life would be
perfect.

27:08.196 --> 27:09.464
Little remote for that.

27:09.497 --> 27:10.632
Ndiyo.

27:10.665 --> 27:12.333
Let's get some sleep.

27:13.301 --> 27:14.702
That mesa
we saw today,

27:14.736 --> 27:17.238
one of my favorite
places in the world.

27:18.072 --> 27:19.541
And tomorrow we'll climb it.

27:19.574 --> 27:21.009
What's it called?

27:22.043 --> 27:24.112
Los Alamos.

27:27.215 --> 27:29.217
I didn't expect
to see you today.

27:30.385 --> 27:32.220
Do I have to make
an appointment?

27:34.155 --> 27:36.291
Habari! Hey,
get back here!

27:36.324 --> 27:37.459
Alvarez?

27:43.231 --> 27:46.067
Oppie! Oppie!

27:46.100 --> 27:48.102
Je! What is it?

27:48.136 --> 27:49.737
They've done it.
They've done it.

27:49.771 --> 27:51.039
Hahn and Strassmann in Germany.

27:51.072 --> 27:53.241
They split the uranium nucleus.

27:54.108 --> 27:55.977
How?

27:56.711 --> 27:58.613
Bombard it with neutrons.

27:58.646 --> 27:59.791
It's a
nuclear fission.

27:59.815 --> 28:01.449
They did it, they
split the atom.

28:01.483 --> 28:03.051
It's not possible.

28:09.190 --> 28:10.992
I'm gonna try to reproduce it.

28:17.632 --> 28:19.567
See? Can't be dmoja.

28:20.668 --> 28:24.072
Very
elegant. Quite clear.

28:24.105 --> 28:26.741
- There's just one problem.
- Wapi?

28:26.774 --> 28:28.576
Next door.

28:28.610 --> 28:30.545
Alvarez did it.

28:30.578 --> 28:32.714
Lakini then look...

28:32.747 --> 28:36.084
these fission pulses,
they're massive.

28:36.117 --> 28:39.387
I've seen 30 of these
in the past dakika kumi.

28:39.420 --> 28:42.257
Theory will take
you only so far.

28:43.758 --> 28:45.760
During the process...

28:45.793 --> 28:47.529
extra neutrons boil off,

28:47.562 --> 28:50.732
which could be used to
split other uranium atoms.

28:50.765 --> 28:52.166
Chain reaction.

28:52.200 --> 28:53.836
Wewe ni thinkin'
nini I'm thinkin'.

28:53.869 --> 28:56.638
Wewe, me, and every other
physicist around the world

28:56.671 --> 28:58.172
who's seen the news.

28:58.874 --> 29:00.675
I'm... nini? What
are we all thinking?

29:00.708 --> 29:04.479
A bomb, Alvarez.

29:05.647 --> 29:07.348
A bomb.

29:07.382 --> 29:10.585
Nilikuambia, Robert, no
more fucking flowers.

29:12.186 --> 29:13.731
I don't understand
nini you want from me.

29:13.755 --> 29:15.523
I don't want anything from you.

29:16.524 --> 29:18.560
Naam, you say that
and then you call.

29:18.593 --> 29:21.195
Naam, don't answer.

29:21.229 --> 29:23.231
I'll jibu kila wakati.

29:28.503 --> 29:29.437
Fine.

29:29.470 --> 29:32.173
Just no more flowers.

29:33.207 --> 29:34.576
Wewe ni not coming?

29:35.743 --> 29:38.546
Wewe have to know
when you're beakumi, Robert.

29:40.849 --> 29:42.584
It's not that simple, Hoke.

29:42.617 --> 29:44.786
Chevalier, good
to see you. It's...

29:44.820 --> 29:46.154
Ah, Barbara, good to see you

29:46.187 --> 29:48.656
and the illustrious
Oppenheimer Dk.

29:48.690 --> 29:49.858
I'm Eltenton.

29:49.892 --> 29:51.268
- Oh, pleasure.
- Tafadhali, tafadhali.

29:51.292 --> 29:52.460
Now, might you say a word

29:52.493 --> 29:55.229
about organized labor
on campuses, yes?

29:55.263 --> 29:56.798
Coming through! Coming through!

29:56.832 --> 29:58.409
- F.A.E.C.T.!
- I work at Shell.

29:58.433 --> 30:00.444
We've signed up chemists,
we've signed up engineers,

30:00.468 --> 30:02.337
so why not scientists
in academia?

30:02.370 --> 30:05.273
Oppie!
Oppie! Oppie!

30:05.306 --> 30:08.576
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!

30:08.610 --> 30:10.244
Oppie! Oppie!

30:10.278 --> 30:13.181
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!

30:16.351 --> 30:20.321
Teachers are unionized.
Why not professors?

30:20.355 --> 30:21.789
Don't you have somewhere to be?

30:21.824 --> 30:23.658
Lawrence, academics
have rights too.

30:23.691 --> 30:26.194
Look, it's not that.
I've got a group coming.

30:26.227 --> 30:29.430
- Naam, I'll sit in.
- Not this moja.

30:35.703 --> 30:37.372
Richard. Dr. Bush.

30:37.405 --> 30:39.474
What brings you two up north?

30:48.951 --> 30:50.318
Richard, you tell Ruth

30:50.351 --> 30:51.671
I'll be down to
Pasadena Thursday.

31:00.628 --> 31:03.264
Wako paper
on black holes is in!

31:03.297 --> 31:05.266
Oppie!

31:05.299 --> 31:08.937
Where's Hartland? Get
Hartland. Get Hartland.

31:08.971 --> 31:11.239
September 1st, 1939,

31:11.272 --> 31:13.508
the world's gonna
remember this day.

31:14.442 --> 31:15.920
Oh, Hartland. Our
paper, it's in print.

31:15.944 --> 31:18.680
Wewe've been upstaged.

31:22.283 --> 31:24.820
During the Battle of
Britain, I found myself

31:24.853 --> 31:27.588
increasingly out of sympathy
with the

31:27.622 --> 31:30.625
policy of neutrality that
Communists advocated.

31:30.658 --> 31:34.462
Right after Hitler invaded
Russia and we became allies,

31:34.495 --> 31:36.531
these Communist sympathies,
did they return?

31:36.564 --> 31:37.598
Hapana.

31:38.733 --> 31:42.336
I need to make clear that
my changing views on Russia

31:42.370 --> 31:43.604
did not mean a sharp break

31:43.638 --> 31:45.707
from those who held
different views.

31:45.740 --> 31:48.309
For a year or two, and
during a previous marriage,

31:48.342 --> 31:51.646
my wife Kitty had been a
Communist Party member.

31:54.282 --> 31:55.616
Oop!

31:55.650 --> 31:57.452
This way. This is where
I keep the good stuff.

31:57.485 --> 31:59.487
Naam, I thought this
was the Tolmans' house.

31:59.520 --> 32:01.723
I live with them
while I'm at Caltech.

32:01.756 --> 32:03.257
Do you two need anything?

32:03.291 --> 32:04.759
We're good, Ruthie.

32:05.861 --> 32:08.496
So, you're a biologist.

32:08.529 --> 32:11.733
Naam, somehow I have
graduated to housewife.

32:11.766 --> 32:14.903
Can you explain quantum
mechanics to me?

32:14.937 --> 32:15.971
Seems baffling.

32:16.004 --> 32:17.705
Yes, it is.

32:18.807 --> 32:21.609
Naam, this glass,

32:21.642 --> 32:22.543
this drink...

32:22.577 --> 32:25.680
this countertop,

32:25.713 --> 32:28.817
uh, our bodies...

32:28.851 --> 32:30.752
all of it.

32:30.785 --> 32:33.354
It's mostly empty space.

32:33.387 --> 32:35.891
Groupings of tiny energy
waves bound together.

32:35.924 --> 32:37.792
By nini?

32:37.826 --> 32:41.395
Forces of attraction strong
enough to convince us

32:41.429 --> 32:43.631
that matter is solid.

32:43.664 --> 32:46.801
Stop my body passing
through yours.

32:58.546 --> 33:00.048
Wewe ni married to Dr. Harrison.

33:00.082 --> 33:01.817
Not very.

33:03.852 --> 33:07.555
There is someone that I feel...

33:07.588 --> 33:09.024
Does she feel the same way?

33:09.057 --> 33:12.895
Sometimes. Not enough.

33:14.096 --> 33:17.065
Wewe know, I'm going
to New Mexico.

33:17.099 --> 33:18.901
To my ranch, with friends.

33:18.934 --> 33:20.301
Wewe should come.

33:21.103 --> 33:22.938
I meant with your husband.

33:22.971 --> 33:24.539
Yes, you did.

33:24.572 --> 33:27.475
Maana wewe know it won't
make a bit of difference.

33:31.445 --> 33:32.948
Why did you marry him?

33:32.981 --> 33:36.517
I was lost and he was kind.

33:38.686 --> 33:39.554
Lost?

33:39.587 --> 33:43.091
Naam, my previous
husband had died, and...

33:43.125 --> 33:45.560
at 28, I wasn't really
ready to be a widow.

33:45.593 --> 33:47.595
- Who was your first husband?
- Nobody.

33:47.628 --> 33:50.098
Lakini my second husband
was Joe Dallet.

33:50.132 --> 33:53.101
He was, um, from
money, like me, but...

33:53.135 --> 33:56.071
he was a union organizer
in Wewengstown, Ohio.

33:56.104 --> 33:57.371
Fell hard.

33:57.405 --> 33:58.673
How hard?

33:58.706 --> 34:00.374
Hard enough to spend
the next four years

34:00.408 --> 34:01.742
living off beans and pancakes,

34:01.776 --> 34:04.545
handing out the <i>Daily
Worker</i> at factory gates.

34:04.579 --> 34:07.082
By 36, I just told Joe I
couldn't take it anymore.

34:07.115 --> 34:08.984
Quit the Party and a year later,

34:09.016 --> 34:12.553
I wanted him back, so...
Him, not the <i>Daily Worker.</i>

34:12.587 --> 34:14.731
And he said, "Swell, I'll
meet you on my way to Spain."

34:14.755 --> 34:16.456
He went to fight
for the Loyalists?

34:16.489 --> 34:18.592
And then he went to the
brigades and I waited.

34:18.626 --> 34:19.694
And...

34:20.561 --> 34:21.929
Joe got himself killed

34:21.964 --> 34:24.364
first time he popped his
head out of the trench.

34:25.699 --> 34:28.136
Ideology got Joe
killed. For nothing.

34:28.170 --> 34:30.038
Spanish Republic isn't nothing.

34:30.072 --> 34:31.181
My husband offered
both our futures

34:31.206 --> 34:32.672
to stop one fascist bullet

34:32.706 --> 34:34.877
from embedding
itself in a mudbank.

34:35.775 --> 34:37.612
Hiyo ni the definition
of nothing.

34:37.645 --> 34:39.647
Seems a little reductive.

34:39.679 --> 34:41.415
Pragmatic.

34:41.449 --> 34:43.886
Now here I am.

34:46.121 --> 34:47.722
Wherever the hell this is.

34:54.762 --> 34:58.033
I didn't want you to
hear it from anyone else.

35:00.468 --> 35:03.805
Least you didn't bring
me flowers.

35:08.944 --> 35:12.513
We both know I'm not
nini you want, Jean.

35:13.547 --> 35:16.184
Yeah, but it's a door closing.

35:16.218 --> 35:17.618
Hapana.

35:19.187 --> 35:21.555
Not as far as I'm concerned, no.

35:22.757 --> 35:24.492
Wewe knocked her up, fast work.

35:24.525 --> 35:27.162
Can't keep a good man down.

35:27.195 --> 35:29.197
I meant her.

35:29.231 --> 35:31.233
She knew nini she wanted.

35:31.266 --> 35:33.201
What about the husband?

35:33.235 --> 35:34.702
We talked, um,

35:34.735 --> 35:36.671
they're getting a divorce, so...

35:36.704 --> 35:40.474
we can get married before
she starts showing.

35:40.508 --> 35:41.977
How civilized.

35:43.946 --> 35:45.047
Wewe idiot.

35:45.080 --> 35:46.848
This is your community.

35:46.882 --> 35:49.818
Wewe think the rules don't
apply to the golden boy?

35:50.986 --> 35:52.620
Brilliance makes up for a lot.

35:52.653 --> 35:55.157
Don't alienate the only
people in the world

35:55.190 --> 35:56.858
that understand nini you do.

35:58.592 --> 35:59.962
One day you might need them.

35:59.995 --> 36:02.730
F.A.E.C.T. MEMBERS
F.A.E.C.T.!

36:02.763 --> 36:03.975
The Federation
of Architects,

36:03.999 --> 36:07.135
Engineers, Chemists
and Technicians.

36:13.574 --> 36:16.111
Lomanitz, nini do
you get paid a month?

36:16.144 --> 36:17.288
Hiyo ni not the point, Lawrence.

36:17.312 --> 36:19.613
What do any of
you have in common

36:19.647 --> 36:22.250
with farm laborers
and dock workers?

36:22.284 --> 36:23.852
Plenty.

36:24.920 --> 36:27.456
Kila mtu nje. Now!

36:31.293 --> 36:32.693
Not you.

36:38.632 --> 36:39.600
What are you doing?

36:39.633 --> 36:41.303
It's a trade union.

36:41.336 --> 36:43.271
Filled with Communists.

36:43.305 --> 36:45.007
So? I haven't joined the Party.

36:45.040 --> 36:47.142
They won't let me bring
you onto the project

36:47.175 --> 36:48.877
because of this shit.

36:48.910 --> 36:50.687
They won't even let me tell
you nini the project is.

36:50.711 --> 36:53.148
Oh. I know
nini the project is.

36:53.181 --> 36:54.249
Oh, really?

36:54.282 --> 36:55.583
We've all heard about Einstein

36:55.616 --> 36:56.894
and Szilard's
letter to Roosevelt

36:56.918 --> 36:58.719
warning him the Germans
could make a bomb,

36:58.753 --> 37:01.622
and I know nini it means for
the Nazis to have a bomb.

37:01.655 --> 37:03.025
Oh, and I don't?

37:03.058 --> 37:05.693
It's not your people
they're herding into camps.

37:06.794 --> 37:07.795
It's mine.

37:07.829 --> 37:10.966
Wewe think that I tell
them about your politics.

37:12.067 --> 37:14.635
The next time you're
coming home from a meeting,

37:14.668 --> 37:16.704
why don't you take a look
in the rearview mirror?

37:16.737 --> 37:18.807
Listen to the sounds
on your phone line

37:18.840 --> 37:21.910
and stop being so goddamn naive.

37:23.211 --> 37:24.745
Why would they care nini I do?

37:24.779 --> 37:26.747
Because you're
not just self-important,

37:26.781 --> 37:28.950
you're actually important.

37:30.185 --> 37:31.552
Sawa.

37:32.187 --> 37:35.190
Sawa. I get it.

37:35.223 --> 37:37.292
If you could just
be a little more...

37:37.325 --> 37:38.827
Pragmatic.

37:38.860 --> 37:39.971
I'll talk to Lomanitz,
I'll talk to the others,

37:39.995 --> 37:42.097
you don't have to
worry. It's dmoja.

37:42.130 --> 37:43.899
Lawrence.

37:48.736 --> 37:50.738
Then welcome to the war.

37:50.771 --> 37:53.075
I filled out my
first security questionnaire

37:53.108 --> 37:54.376
and was informed

37:54.409 --> 37:56.211
that my involvement
with left-wing groups

37:56.244 --> 38:00.182
would not prove a bar to my
working juu ya atomiki program.

38:00.215 --> 38:02.951
<i>Why were
his Communist associations</i>

38:02.984 --> 38:06.088
not seen as a security
risk during the war?

38:06.121 --> 38:07.856
Senator, I can't possibly answer

38:07.889 --> 38:11.226
for kibali cha usalama granted
years before I ever met the man.

38:11.259 --> 38:13.261
Fine. What about after?

38:13.295 --> 38:15.230
Baada ya war, Oppenheimer Dk

38:15.263 --> 38:19.034
was the most respected
scientific voice in the world.

38:19.067 --> 38:21.103
Hiyo ni why I asked him
to run the Institute,

38:21.136 --> 38:24.239
that's why he advised the
Atomic Energy Commission.

38:24.272 --> 38:25.340
Simple as that.

38:25.373 --> 38:27.976
What are they accusing me of?

38:28.009 --> 38:29.777
I think they just want
to know nini happened

38:29.811 --> 38:32.314
between 1947 and 1954
to change your mind

38:32.347 --> 38:34.382
on Oppenheimer's
kibali cha usalama.

38:34.416 --> 38:37.152
I didn't. I was
chair of the AEC,

38:37.185 --> 38:40.754
but it wasn't me that brought
the charges against Robert.

38:40.788 --> 38:42.033
- Nani alifanya?
- Some former staff member

38:42.057 --> 38:43.992
of the Joint
Congressional Committee.

38:44.025 --> 38:47.095
He was a rabid
anti-Communist named Borden.

38:47.129 --> 38:49.431
He wrote to the FBI
demanding they take action.

38:49.464 --> 38:52.000
The FBI? Why not go
to the AEC, direct?

38:52.033 --> 38:54.735
Why get caught holding
the knife yourself?

38:54.768 --> 38:57.205
What did Borden have
against Oppenheimer?

38:57.239 --> 38:59.074
This was the McCarthy Era.

38:59.107 --> 39:04.012
People hounded out of jobs
for any hint of red. And then,

39:04.045 --> 39:05.713
<i>reading Oppenheimer's
security file,</i>

39:05.746 --> 39:07.916
<i>his Communist brother,
sister-in-law,</i>

39:07.949 --> 39:10.018
<i>fiancée, best friend, wife.</i>

39:10.051 --> 39:12.387
Hiyo ni before we even get
to the Chevalier incident.

39:12.420 --> 39:16.158
Lakini how would Borden have access
to Oppenheimer's security file?

39:16.191 --> 39:17.859
Because somebody gave it to him.

39:19.027 --> 39:21.695
Somebody who wanted
Robert silenced.

39:21.729 --> 39:23.331
- WHO?
- Who knows?

39:23.365 --> 39:25.901
Robert didn't take
care not to upset

39:25.934 --> 39:28.170
the power brokers in Washington.

39:28.203 --> 39:31.072
His opinions on the
atom became definitive

39:31.106 --> 39:34.009
and he wasn't always patient
with us mere mortals.

39:37.412 --> 39:39.848
I came in for plenty
of harsh treatment.

39:39.881 --> 39:43.051
There was an AEC vote

39:43.084 --> 39:45.053
on the export of
isotopu kwenda Norway,

39:45.086 --> 39:48.056
<i>and they drafted in Robert
to make me look like a fool.</i>

39:48.089 --> 39:49.790
Lakini,
Oppenheimer Dk,

39:49.824 --> 39:51.927
we've already heard from
Admiral Strauss that

39:51.960 --> 39:54.795
these isotopes could be
useful to our enemies

39:54.829 --> 39:56.140
in the production
of atomic weapons.

39:56.164 --> 39:58.033
Congressmen,
you could use a shovel

39:58.066 --> 39:59.510
in making atomic weapons.

39:59.534 --> 40:00.734
In fact, you do.

40:00.768 --> 40:02.304
Wewe could use a bottle of beer

40:02.337 --> 40:03.737
in making atomic weapons.

40:03.771 --> 40:05.240
In fact, you do.

40:05.273 --> 40:08.210
I say isotopes are less useful
than electronic components

40:08.243 --> 40:11.012
but more useful than a sandwich.

40:14.249 --> 40:16.117
<i>Genius is no
guarantee of wisdom.</i>

40:17.118 --> 40:19.888
How could this man who
saw so much be so blind?

40:29.397 --> 40:30.832
Kitty?

40:35.537 --> 40:37.472
Kitty?

40:37.505 --> 40:40.909
Kitty, the project...

40:41.876 --> 40:44.479
I'm in. I'm in.

40:44.512 --> 40:46.281
Let's celebrate.

40:51.920 --> 40:53.521
Shouldn't you go to him?

40:58.126 --> 41:01.296
I have been going to
him all fucking day.

41:25.053 --> 41:26.787
Come here, darling.

41:27.889 --> 41:29.457
I don't know how to say this.

41:29.491 --> 41:32.193
I'm... I'm ashamed to ask.

41:32.227 --> 41:34.162
Anything.

41:34.195 --> 41:34.996
Take Peter.

41:35.030 --> 41:38.066
- Sure.
- No, for-for a while, Hoke.

41:38.099 --> 41:40.068
A while.

41:41.636 --> 41:43.438
Does Kitty know you're here?

41:43.471 --> 41:45.206
Yes, of course she knows.

41:46.074 --> 41:48.076
Of course she knows.

41:48.109 --> 41:51.813
We're awful people.
Selfish, awful people.

41:53.315 --> 41:54.316
Forget I asked.

41:54.349 --> 41:56.184
Selfish, awful people,

41:56.217 --> 41:58.620
they don't know they're
selfish and awful.

41:58.653 --> 42:01.222
Sit, sit, sit.

42:02.257 --> 42:06.361
Robert, wewe see beyond
the world we live in.

42:08.063 --> 42:10.632
There is a price to
be paid for that.

42:10.665 --> 42:12.233
Of course we'll help you.

42:23.178 --> 42:25.347
Everything's
changing, Robert.

42:25.380 --> 42:27.349
Having a child was
always going to change...

42:27.382 --> 42:31.486
No, the world, it's pivoting
in some new direction.

42:31.519 --> 42:33.922
It's reforming.

42:35.690 --> 42:37.392
This is your moment.

42:38.560 --> 42:40.237
We're putting together a
group to study feasibility...

42:40.261 --> 42:43.064
"We" shouldn't be doing
anything. Wewe should.

42:43.965 --> 42:46.101
Lawrence won't get this dmoja.

42:46.134 --> 42:48.269
Or Tolman or Rabi. Wewe will.

42:57.112 --> 42:59.247
Who are the uniforms?

43:00.048 --> 43:01.950
I thought you might know.

43:02.984 --> 43:05.253
Oppenheimer Dk.

43:05.286 --> 43:07.255
I'm Colonel Groves.

43:07.288 --> 43:09.524
This is Lieutenant
Colonel Nichols.

43:09.557 --> 43:11.059
Have that dry-cleaned.

43:16.965 --> 43:19.033
Naam, if that's how you
treat Lieutenant Colonel,

43:19.067 --> 43:22.437
I'd hate to see how you
treat a humble physicist.

43:22.470 --> 43:24.539
Ah, if I ever meet
one, I'll let you know.

43:24.572 --> 43:26.074
Lo.

43:26.107 --> 43:27.675
Theaters of combat
all over the world,

43:27.709 --> 43:29.644
but I have to stay
in Washington.

43:29.677 --> 43:32.380
- Kwa nini?
- I built the Pentagon.

43:32.414 --> 43:35.049
The brass likes it so much
they made me take over

43:35.083 --> 43:37.218
the Manhattan Engineer District.

43:37.252 --> 43:38.386
Which is?

43:38.420 --> 43:41.689
Oh, don't be a smart ass. Wewe
know damn well nini it is.

43:41.723 --> 43:43.425
Wewe and half of every
physics department

43:43.458 --> 43:46.294
across the country.
Hiyo ni problem number moja.

43:46.327 --> 43:48.062
I thought problem
number one would be

43:48.096 --> 43:49.364
securing enough uranium ore.

43:49.397 --> 43:52.500
1,200 tons bought the
day I took charge.

43:52.534 --> 43:53.701
Processing?

43:53.735 --> 43:55.937
Just broke ground at
Oak Ridge, Tennessee.

43:56.738 --> 43:58.440
Now I'm looking for
a project director.

43:58.473 --> 44:00.575
And my name came up?

44:00.608 --> 44:01.676
Nope.

44:02.812 --> 44:05.046
Even though you brought
quantum physics to America.

44:05.079 --> 44:06.448
Which made me curious.

44:06.481 --> 44:08.349
What have you found out?

44:09.250 --> 44:11.753
Wewe ni a dilettante,
a womanizer,

44:11.786 --> 44:13.121
a suspected Communist...

44:13.154 --> 44:14.556
I'm a New Deal Democrat.

44:14.589 --> 44:16.191
I said "suspected."

44:16.224 --> 44:20.462
Unstable, theatrical,
egotistical, neurotic...

44:20.495 --> 44:21.529
Nothing good, no?

44:21.563 --> 44:23.231
Not even "he's
brilliant, but..."

44:23.264 --> 44:25.066
Naam, brilliance is
taken for granted

44:25.099 --> 44:26.601
in your circle, so no.

44:26.634 --> 44:28.603
No, the only person who
had anything good to say

44:28.636 --> 44:30.371
was Richard Tolman.

44:30.405 --> 44:32.507
Tolman thinks you
have integrity,

44:32.540 --> 44:34.676
but he also strikes me as a guy

44:34.709 --> 44:37.078
who knows more about
science than people.

44:37.111 --> 44:41.082
Yet here you are. Wewe
don't take much on trust.

44:41.115 --> 44:43.117
I don't take anything on trust.

44:46.688 --> 44:48.423
Why don't you have
a Nobel Prize?

44:48.456 --> 44:49.524
Why aren't you a general?

44:49.557 --> 44:50.734
They're making me one for this.

44:50.758 --> 44:52.126
Perhaps I'll have the same luck.

44:52.160 --> 44:53.761
A Nobel Prize for making a bomb?

44:53.795 --> 44:56.130
Alfred Nobel invented dynamite.

44:58.566 --> 45:00.201
So how would you proceed?

45:01.703 --> 45:04.405
Wewe ni talking
about turning theory

45:04.439 --> 45:06.608
into a practical weapons system

45:06.641 --> 45:07.775
faster than the Nazis.

45:07.810 --> 45:09.544
Who have a 12-month head start.

45:09.577 --> 45:10.712
Eighteen.

45:10.745 --> 45:12.113
How could you
possibly know that?

45:12.146 --> 45:14.182
Our fast neutron
research took six months.

45:14.215 --> 45:15.726
The man they've
undoubtedly put in charge

45:15.750 --> 45:17.151
will have made that
leap instantly.

45:17.185 --> 45:18.395
Who do you think
they put in charge?

45:18.419 --> 45:19.521
Werner Heisenberg.

45:19.554 --> 45:22.123
He has the most
intuitive understanding

45:22.156 --> 45:23.826
of atomic structure
I have ever seen.

45:23.859 --> 45:25.560
- Wewe know his work?
- I know him.

45:25.593 --> 45:27.438
<i>Just like I know Walther
Bothe, von Weizsäcker, Diebner.</i>

45:27.462 --> 45:30.265
In a straight race,
the Germans win.

45:30.298 --> 45:33.034
- We've got one hope.
- Which is?

45:33.635 --> 45:35.270
Anti-Semitism.

45:36.404 --> 45:37.405
Je!

45:37.438 --> 45:40.275
Hitler called quantum
physics "Jewish science."

45:40.308 --> 45:42.143
Said it right to
Einstein's face.

45:42.176 --> 45:45.413
Our one hope is that Hitler
is so... so blinded by hate

45:45.446 --> 45:47.248
that he's denied Heisenberg
proper resources,

45:47.282 --> 45:49.217
because it'll take
vast resources.

45:49.250 --> 45:50.795
Our nation's best
scientists working together.

45:50.819 --> 45:52.220
Right now, they're scattered.

45:52.253 --> 45:53.856
Which gives us
compartmentalization.

45:53.889 --> 45:55.757
All minds have to
see the whole task

45:55.790 --> 45:57.158
to contribute efficiently.

45:57.191 --> 45:59.427
Poor security may
cost us the race.

45:59.460 --> 46:01.296
Inefficiency will.

46:01.329 --> 46:03.164
The Germans know
more than us anyway.

46:03.197 --> 46:05.300
The Russians don't.

46:05.333 --> 46:09.270
Remind me, who are
we at war with?

46:09.304 --> 46:11.739
Somebody with your past
doesn't want to be seen

46:11.773 --> 46:13.374
downplaying the importance

46:13.408 --> 46:16.144
of security from our
Communist allies.

46:16.177 --> 46:18.847
Point taken. Lakini, no.

46:18.881 --> 46:21.182
Wewe don't
get to say "no" to me.

46:21.215 --> 46:23.484
It's my job to say "no"
to you when you're wrong.

46:23.518 --> 46:25.520
So you have the job now?

46:25.553 --> 46:27.622
Uh, I'm considering it.

46:30.325 --> 46:32.660
I'm starting to see where
you got your reputation.

46:33.862 --> 46:36.297
My favorite response,

46:36.331 --> 46:38.666
"Oppenheimer couldn't
run a hamburger stand."

46:40.635 --> 46:41.635
I couldn't.

46:43.471 --> 46:45.640
Lakini I can run the
Manhattan Project.

46:46.507 --> 46:48.676
There's a way to
balance these things.

46:48.710 --> 46:52.915
Keep the Rad Lab here at
Berkeley under Lawrence.

46:52.948 --> 46:55.216
Met Lab in Chicago,
under Szilard.

46:55.249 --> 46:57.685
Large-scale refining, where
did you say? Tennessee.

46:57.719 --> 46:59.387
- And Hanford.
- And Hanford.

46:59.420 --> 47:03.491
All America's industrial might
and scientific innovation,

47:03.524 --> 47:04.893
connected by rail.

47:04.927 --> 47:06.594
Focused on one goal.

47:06.628 --> 47:09.330
One point in space and time.
And it comes together here.

47:09.364 --> 47:11.666
<i>A secret laboratory. In
the middle of nowhere,</i>

47:11.699 --> 47:13.167
<i>secure, self-sufficient,</i>

47:13.201 --> 47:14.569
equipment, housing, the works.

47:14.602 --> 47:16.771
Keep everyone there
until it's dmoja.

47:16.805 --> 47:18.841
It'll need a school,
stores, a church.

47:18.874 --> 47:20.308
Why?

47:20.341 --> 47:21.652
<i>If we don't
let scientists</i>

47:21.676 --> 47:23.387
bring their families,
we'll never get the best.

47:23.411 --> 47:25.480
Wewe want security, build
a town, build it fast.

47:25.513 --> 47:26.581
Wapi?

47:30.585 --> 47:32.553
Welcome kwa Los Alamos.

47:32.587 --> 47:35.390
Now, there's a boys school
we'll have to commandeer,

47:35.423 --> 47:37.401
and the local Indians come
up here for burial rites.

47:37.425 --> 47:40.662
Lakini, apart from that, nothing.
Forty miles. Any direction.

47:40.695 --> 47:42.630
Inatosha find the perfect spot.

47:42.664 --> 47:45.166
- For?
- Success.

47:50.438 --> 47:52.440
Build him a town. Fast.

47:53.474 --> 47:55.978
Let's go recruit
some scientists.

47:56.011 --> 47:58.346
Why would I leave my family?

47:58.379 --> 47:59.824
Nilikuambia, you can
bring your family.

47:59.848 --> 48:01.282
I'm not a soldier, Oppie.

48:01.315 --> 48:03.418
A soldier? He's a general.

48:03.451 --> 48:05.286
I've got all the soldier I need.

48:05.319 --> 48:06.889
What can I tell them?

48:06.922 --> 48:09.257
Heisenberg, Diebner,
Bothe and Bohr.

48:09.290 --> 48:10.591
What do these men
have in common?

48:10.625 --> 48:12.627
The greatest minds
on atomic theory.

48:12.660 --> 48:13.996
- Yes, and?
- Uh...

48:14.029 --> 48:17.298
As much as you like,

48:17.331 --> 48:19.467
until you feel my
boot on your balls.

48:19.500 --> 48:22.270
Wewe know isotopes and
you know explosives

48:22.303 --> 48:23.604
better than anyone in the world.

48:23.638 --> 48:26.240
Lakini you can't tell
us nini you're doing?

48:29.310 --> 48:31.546
- sijui.
- The Nazis have them.

48:31.579 --> 48:33.715
- Niels Bohr's in Copenhagen.
- Under Nazi occupation.

48:33.748 --> 48:35.616
Did they stop printing
newspapers in Princeton?

48:35.650 --> 48:37.986
Why would we go to
the middle of nowhere

48:38.020 --> 48:39.487
for who knows how
long?

48:39.520 --> 48:41.622
For a year or two. Or three.

48:42.623 --> 48:46.227
Uh, Mkuu, could
you give us a moment?

48:47.295 --> 48:50.364
It's about unleashing
the strong force...

48:51.499 --> 48:52.901
before the Nazis do.

48:52.935 --> 48:54.870
Oh, my God.

48:54.903 --> 48:56.014
Niels won't work for the Nazis.

48:56.038 --> 48:57.338
No, never.

48:57.371 --> 48:59.674
Lakini while they
have him, we don't.

48:59.707 --> 49:00.876
Hiyo ni why I need you.

49:00.909 --> 49:02.878
Why would you think I'd do that?

49:02.911 --> 49:04.746
"Why?" "Why?"

49:04.779 --> 49:06.991
How about because this is the
most important fucking thing

49:07.015 --> 49:09.017
to ever happen in the
history of the world.

49:09.051 --> 49:10.485
How about that?

49:11.053 --> 49:12.487
Fuck.

49:17.425 --> 49:19.794
They are not gonna let
me onto this project.

49:19.828 --> 49:21.897
And failing a security
check is not gonna be good

49:21.930 --> 49:23.598
for a career, even
after the war.

49:23.631 --> 49:26.400
So you're a fellow
traveler. So nini?

49:26.434 --> 49:27.802
This is a national emergency.

49:27.836 --> 49:31.006
I've got some skeletons,
they put me in charge.

49:31.039 --> 49:32.340
They need us.

49:32.373 --> 49:34.542
Until they don't.

49:37.612 --> 49:40.015
Je! there any chance of
getting Bohr out of Denmark?

49:40.048 --> 49:43.051
Nah, no dice. I checked
with the British.

49:43.085 --> 49:45.386
Until we get Allied boots
back onto the continent,

49:45.419 --> 49:46.822
there's just no way.

49:48.356 --> 49:49.791
Je! he that important?

49:49.825 --> 49:52.861
How many people do you know
who proved Einstein wrong?

49:53.929 --> 49:56.031
Wewe know, it really would
be quicker to take a plane.

49:56.064 --> 49:57.799
No, plane's too risky.

49:57.833 --> 50:00.301
Country needs us.

50:02.670 --> 50:03.771
The Harvard guys,

50:03.806 --> 50:06.374
they say the building's too
small for the cyclotron.

50:08.609 --> 50:10.511
Get them together
with the architects.

50:13.714 --> 50:15.716
When's this place
supposed to open?

50:18.821 --> 50:19.821
Mbili months.

50:20.755 --> 50:23.025
Robert, wewe're the
great improviser,

50:23.058 --> 50:25.093
but this...

50:25.127 --> 50:26.727
you can't do in your head.

50:27.762 --> 50:29.363
Four divisions.

50:30.498 --> 50:34.102
Experimental, Theoretical,
Metallurgical, Ordnance.

50:34.136 --> 50:35.103
Who's running Theoretical?

50:35.137 --> 50:36.537
I am.

50:36.571 --> 50:37.782
Hiyo ni nini
I was afraid of.

50:37.806 --> 50:39.674
Wewe ni spread too thin.

50:40.876 --> 50:42.577
So you take Theoretical.

50:45.147 --> 50:48.382
I'm not coming here, Robert.

50:54.022 --> 50:55.690
Kwa nini sivyo?

51:01.562 --> 51:05.633
Wewe drop a bomb and it falls
on the just and the unjust.

51:06.902 --> 51:09.537
I don't wish the culmination
of three centuries of physics

51:09.570 --> 51:11.974
to be a weapon of
mass destruction.

51:21.183 --> 51:22.516
Izzy.

51:23.651 --> 51:27.788
I don't know if we can be
trusted with such a weapon.

51:29.157 --> 51:32.460
Lakini I know the Nazis can't.

51:35.864 --> 51:38.666
We have no choice.

51:40.068 --> 51:41.502
Then...

51:42.838 --> 51:45.207
the second thing you'll
have to do is appoint

51:45.240 --> 51:47.508
Hans Bethe to run the
Theoretical division.

51:49.878 --> 51:51.712
Wait, nini was the first?

51:51.746 --> 51:54.216
Take off that
ridiculous uniform.

51:54.249 --> 51:55.449
Wewe ni a scientist.

51:55.483 --> 51:57.085
Groves is insisting we join.

51:57.119 --> 51:59.553
Tell Groves to go
shit in his hat.

51:59.587 --> 52:03.058
They need us for who
we are. So be yourself.

52:03.091 --> 52:05.060
Only better.

52:44.099 --> 52:46.134
This is the only key.

52:46.168 --> 52:47.601
And Teller's already here.

52:47.635 --> 52:49.503
Shall I just show him in?

52:49.537 --> 52:51.206
No, let's wait for the others.

52:59.147 --> 53:00.148
Let's get started.

53:00.182 --> 53:02.250
Hello, Edward.

53:02.284 --> 53:03.986
Ndiyo.

53:04.019 --> 53:05.720
Gentlemen, so, we will work here

53:05.753 --> 53:08.756
until the T-section at
Los Alamos is finished.

53:08.789 --> 53:11.093
- Edward, can I please...
- It is more important.

53:13.161 --> 53:15.130
When I calculated
the chain reaction,

53:15.163 --> 53:17.866
I found a rather
troubling possibility.

53:17.899 --> 53:20.002
Hapana.

53:20.035 --> 53:21.269
Lakini this can't be right.

53:21.303 --> 53:23.238
Show me how you did
mahesabu yako.

53:23.271 --> 53:24.672
Ndiyo.

53:28.176 --> 53:29.244
It's exponential.

53:29.277 --> 53:31.746
Hapana. No, no, no. Hapana.

53:34.282 --> 53:36.284
This is fantasy.

53:36.318 --> 53:38.586
Teller's calculations
can't be right.

53:38.619 --> 53:41.289
Do them yourself while
I go to Princeton.

53:41.323 --> 53:43.158
- Kwa ajili ya nini?
- To talk to Einstein.

53:43.191 --> 53:45.760
Naam, there's not much common
ground between you two.

53:45.793 --> 53:48.830
Hiyo ni why I should
get his view.

53:52.267 --> 53:54.269
- Albert.
- Hmm?

53:54.302 --> 53:57.205
Ah. Oppenheimer Dk.

53:57.239 --> 53:58.706
Naam, have you met Dr. Gödel?

53:58.739 --> 54:00.308
We walk here most days.

54:00.342 --> 54:05.147
Trees are the most
inspiring structures.

54:05.180 --> 54:06.647
Albert, might I have a word?

54:06.680 --> 54:10.085
Bila shaka. 'Scuse me, Kurt.

54:11.086 --> 54:14.022
Wewe know, some days,
Kurt refuses to eat.

54:14.056 --> 54:15.656
Even in Princeton.

54:15.689 --> 54:18.793
He's convinced that the
Nazis can poison his food.

54:18.827 --> 54:20.095
Mm.

54:20.128 --> 54:21.963
Hmm? Huh.

54:23.832 --> 54:25.666
Wha...

54:30.205 --> 54:33.041
Whose... Whose work is this?

54:33.075 --> 54:34.109
Teller's.

54:35.243 --> 54:37.711
What do you take it to mean?

54:37.745 --> 54:39.680
Neutrons smash into nucleus,

54:39.713 --> 54:43.751
releasing neutrons to
smash into other nuclei.

54:43.784 --> 54:45.987
Criticality, a
point of no return,

54:46.021 --> 54:47.621
massive explosive force.

54:47.655 --> 54:49.991
Lakini this time, the chain
reaction doesn't stop.

54:50.892 --> 54:53.862
It would ignite the atmosphere.

54:54.930 --> 54:56.898
When we detonate
an atomic device,

54:56.932 --> 54:59.101
we might start a
chain reaction that...

55:00.068 --> 55:01.602
destroys the world.

55:02.770 --> 55:04.672
So here we are, hmm?

55:04.705 --> 55:09.010
Lost in your quantum
world of probabilities

55:09.044 --> 55:10.778
and needing certainty.

55:10.812 --> 55:13.681
Can you run the
calculations yourself?

55:13.714 --> 55:15.117
About the only thing

55:15.150 --> 55:18.420
you and I have in common is
a disdain for mathematics.

55:18.453 --> 55:21.022
Who's working on
this in-in Berkeley?

55:21.056 --> 55:22.357
Hans Bethe.

55:22.390 --> 55:24.226
Naam, he'll get to the truth.

55:25.861 --> 55:28.729
And if the truth
is catastrophic?

55:28.762 --> 55:30.065
Then you stop.

55:30.098 --> 55:33.835
And you share your
findings with the Nazis.

55:33.869 --> 55:37.005
So neither side
destroys the world.

55:40.208 --> 55:41.243
Robert.

55:42.710 --> 55:45.914
This is yours, not mine.

55:58.792 --> 56:00.195
Teller's wrong.

56:00.228 --> 56:01.429
He's wrong.

56:11.106 --> 56:13.808
When you know Teller's
critical assumptions,

56:13.842 --> 56:15.177
the real picture emerges.

56:15.210 --> 56:17.012
Bottom line?

56:17.045 --> 56:19.147
The chances of an
uncontrolled nuclear reaction

56:19.181 --> 56:20.182
are near zero.

56:20.215 --> 56:22.851
Near zero.

56:22.884 --> 56:25.153
- Oppie, this is good news.
- Mm.

56:26.488 --> 56:27.721
Can you run them again?

56:27.755 --> 56:29.491
No, you'll get the same answer.

56:29.524 --> 56:31.102
Till they actually detonate
one of these things,

56:31.126 --> 56:33.962
the best assurance you're
going to get is this.

56:33.995 --> 56:35.063
Near zero.

56:37.265 --> 56:39.935
Theory
will take you only so far.

56:39.968 --> 56:41.469
- Mm.
<i>- Hello!</i>

56:41.503 --> 56:42.813
- Hello, you.
- Hi.

56:42.837 --> 56:44.172
We missed him.

56:44.206 --> 56:45.340
Wewe want to adopt?

56:45.373 --> 56:46.774
She's kidding.

56:46.808 --> 56:48.742
We wanted to see
you before we left.

56:48.776 --> 56:51.947
For parts unknown.

56:51.980 --> 56:54.516
Wewe know who
I ran into the other day?

56:54.549 --> 56:56.184
Eltenton.

56:56.218 --> 56:57.485
Oh.

56:57.519 --> 56:59.221
The chemist from
Shell? The union guy?

56:59.254 --> 57:03.124
Ndiyo. He...
The, uh, F.A.E.C.T. guy.

57:03.158 --> 57:06.528
He was moaning about how
we're handling the war.

57:06.561 --> 57:08.762
How so?

57:08.796 --> 57:11.533
Lack of cooperation
with our allies.

57:11.566 --> 57:13.902
Apparently our
government's not sharing

57:13.935 --> 57:16.037
any research with the Russians.

57:16.071 --> 57:17.038
Naam, he said,

57:17.072 --> 57:19.808
"Most scientists think
the policy is stupid."

57:23.144 --> 57:24.980
- Oh, yeah?
- Ndiyo.

57:25.013 --> 57:27.382
He mentioned that if anyone

57:27.415 --> 57:30.385
had anything they
wanted to pass on,

57:30.418 --> 57:32.254
uh, going around
official channels,

57:32.287 --> 57:34.222
that he could help.

57:42.864 --> 57:44.532
That would be treason.

57:44.566 --> 57:47.402
Ndiyo, bila shaka.

57:47.435 --> 57:49.237
I just thought you should know.

57:52.374 --> 57:53.842
The brat is down.

57:53.875 --> 57:55.243
Where are the martinis?

58:00.448 --> 58:01.950
Coming right up.

58:01.983 --> 58:03.451
<i>Conversation ended there.</i>

58:03.485 --> 58:05.587
Nothing in our
long-standing friendship

58:05.620 --> 58:07.188
would have led me to believe

58:07.222 --> 58:09.958
that Chevalier was actually
seeking information,

58:09.991 --> 58:12.460
and I am certain
that he had no idea

58:12.494 --> 58:14.795
of the work in
which I was engaged.

58:19.334 --> 58:21.303
It has long been clear to me

58:21.336 --> 58:24.039
that I should have reported
this incident at once.

58:24.072 --> 58:25.583
<i>The
Oppenheimer situation</i>

58:25.607 --> 58:28.510
<i>highlights the tension
between scientists</i>

58:28.543 --> 58:30.145
and the security apparatus.

58:30.178 --> 58:32.047
In hopes of learning
how the nominee handled

58:32.080 --> 58:34.416
such issues during
his time at the AEC,

58:34.449 --> 58:37.952
we'll have a scientist
appearing before the committee.

58:38.620 --> 58:40.188
Who are they bringing in?

58:40.221 --> 58:41.189
They hadn't said.

58:41.222 --> 58:42.590
Mheshimiwa Mwenyekiti,
if I may,

58:42.624 --> 58:45.160
I'm nominated for
Commerce Secretary.

58:45.193 --> 58:47.495
Why seek the opinion
of scientists?

58:47.529 --> 58:49.864
This is a Cabinet post, Admiral.

58:49.898 --> 58:52.067
We seek a wide range of opinion.

58:52.100 --> 58:54.903
Naam, Ningependa know the name
of the scientist testifying.

58:54.936 --> 58:56.438
I'd like the chance
to cross-examine.

58:56.471 --> 58:58.606
This is not a court.

58:58.640 --> 59:01.042
Formality, huh?

59:01.076 --> 59:02.353
No
presidential Cabinet nominee

59:02.377 --> 59:04.946
has failed to be
confirmed since 1925.

59:04.979 --> 59:07.082
This is just how
the game is played.

59:07.115 --> 59:08.416
It's in the bag, Lewis.

59:08.450 --> 59:09.651
So play nice.

59:09.684 --> 59:11.953
<i>They bring in a
scientist, so nini?</i>

59:11.986 --> 59:13.988
Wewe don't know scientists
like I do, Counselor.

59:14.022 --> 59:16.057
They resent anyone who
questions their judgment,

59:16.091 --> 59:18.093
<i>especially if you're
not one of them.</i>

59:18.126 --> 59:19.427
I was chair of the AEC.

59:19.461 --> 59:21.896
I'm easy to blame for
nini happened to Robert.

59:21.930 --> 59:23.231
We can't have the
Senate thinking

59:23.264 --> 59:26.368
the scientific community
doesn't support you, sir.

59:26.401 --> 59:28.236
Or should we pivot?

59:28.269 --> 59:30.238
- To nini?
- And embrace it.

59:30.271 --> 59:33.041
"I fought Oppenheimer,
and the US won."

59:33.074 --> 59:34.642
I-I don't think we
need to go there.

59:34.676 --> 59:36.954
Je!n't there someone we can call
who knows nini really happened?

59:36.978 --> 59:38.418
- Teller.
- He'll make an impression.

59:38.446 --> 59:40.524
Can you get the name of the
scientist they've called?

59:40.548 --> 59:42.117
- Probably.
- Find out if he was

59:42.150 --> 59:44.519
based in Chicago or Los
Alamos during the war.

59:44.552 --> 59:45.920
Why does that matter?

59:45.954 --> 59:47.164
Naam, if he was
based in Chicago,

59:47.188 --> 59:48.599
then he worked under
Szilard and Fermi,

59:48.623 --> 59:50.925
not the cult of
Oppie at Los Alamos.

59:50.959 --> 59:52.193
Robert built that damn place.

59:52.227 --> 59:54.996
He was founder, mayor, sheriff,

59:55.029 --> 59:56.431
all rolled into moja.

01:00:09.377 --> 01:00:11.179
Inachohitaji ni saloon tu.

01:00:39.607 --> 01:00:42.177
Hakuna jikoni.

01:00:42.210 --> 01:00:46.147
Kweli? Tutarekebisha hilo.

01:00:52.053 --> 01:00:55.457
Waya yenye miiba, bunduki.

01:00:55.490 --> 01:00:56.591
Oppie.

01:00:56.624 --> 01:00:58.259
Tuko vitani, Hans.

01:01:00.662 --> 01:01:03.231
Halifax. 1917.

01:01:03.264 --> 01:01:06.234
Meli ya mizigo iliyobeba silaha
hulipuka bandarini.

01:01:08.636 --> 01:01:11.573
Kubwa na ghafla
mmenyuko wa kemikali.

01:01:15.243 --> 01:01:18.079
Kubwa lililotengenezwa na mwanadamu
mlipuko katika historia.

01:01:18.112 --> 01:01:20.081
Sasa hebu tuhesabu jinsi gani
zaidi ya uharibifu

01:01:20.114 --> 01:01:22.784
ingekuwa
ikiwa ni nyuklia

01:01:22.818 --> 01:01:24.486
na si mmenyuko wa kemikali.

01:01:24.519 --> 01:01:28.156
Kuonyesha nguvu ndani
masharti ya tani za TNT.

01:01:28.189 --> 01:01:29.691
Lakini itakuwa maelfu.

01:01:29.724 --> 01:01:33.161
Naam, basi kilotons.

01:01:36.731 --> 01:01:40.101
Kwa kutumia U-235,

01:01:40.134 --> 01:01:42.704
- bomu litahitaji ...
- Uh-uh.

01:01:42.737 --> 01:01:45.808
Pole. Gadget mapenzi
wanahitaji nyanja ya pauni 33

01:01:45.841 --> 01:01:47.308
kuhusu ukubwa huu.

01:01:47.342 --> 01:01:51.145
Au kutumia plutonium,
nyanja ya pauni kumi.

01:01:52.547 --> 01:01:53.781
Hapa ni kiasi cha uranium

01:01:53.816 --> 01:01:57.151
Oak Ridge iliyosafishwa
mwezi uliopita.

01:01:59.554 --> 01:02:03.558
Na mmea wa Hanford
ilifanya plutonium kiasi hiki.

01:02:04.692 --> 01:02:07.795
Sasa, kama tunaweza
kuboresha kiasi hiki,

01:02:07.830 --> 01:02:10.632
tunahitaji njia ya kuwalipua.

01:02:10.665 --> 01:02:12.767
Je, tunakuchosha, Edward?

01:02:12.800 --> 01:02:14.402
Kidogo, ndio.

01:02:14.435 --> 01:02:15.670
Naweza kuuliza kwa nini?

01:02:15.703 --> 01:02:17.138
Sisi sote
aliingia kwenye chumba hiki

01:02:17.171 --> 01:02:19.107
kujua fission
bomu liliwezekana.

01:02:19.140 --> 01:02:21.743
Vipi tutaiacha
na kitu kipya?

01:02:21.776 --> 01:02:22.777
Kama vile?

01:02:22.811 --> 01:02:25.547
Badala ya uranium au plutonium,

01:02:25.580 --> 01:02:26.581
tunatumia hidrojeni.

01:02:28.149 --> 01:02:29.760
- Hidrojeni nzito.
-Hidrojeni.

01:02:29.784 --> 01:02:32.554
Deuterium. Unaona?

01:02:32.587 --> 01:02:34.289
Tunaunganisha atomi pamoja

01:02:34.322 --> 01:02:37.392
chini ya shinikizo kubwa
kushawishi mmenyuko wa fusion.

01:02:38.326 --> 01:02:41.162
Basi hatutapata kilotoni,

01:02:41.195 --> 01:02:42.263
lakini megatoni.

01:02:42.297 --> 01:02:43.231
kubwa
mmenyuko wa fission...

01:02:43.264 --> 01:02:44.833
Sawa, subiri, subiri.

01:02:44.867 --> 01:02:49.571
Kwa hivyo unazalishaje vya kutosha
kulazimisha kuunganisha atomi za hidrojeni?

01:02:49.604 --> 01:02:51.673
Bomu ndogo ya fission.

01:02:51.706 --> 01:02:53.408
Hapo tupo.

01:02:55.343 --> 01:02:57.145
Naam, kwa kuwa tunaenda
kuhitaji moja hata hivyo,

01:02:57.178 --> 01:02:59.147
tunaweza kurudi
biashara iliyopo?

01:02:59.180 --> 01:03:00.524
Suala la isotopu

01:03:00.548 --> 01:03:04.185
haikuwa yako muhimu zaidi
kutokubaliana kwa sera

01:03:04.218 --> 01:03:05.854
akiwa na Dk. Oppenheimer.

01:03:05.888 --> 01:03:08.289
Ilikuwa hidrojeni
bomu, sivyo?

01:03:08.323 --> 01:03:11.192
Lo, kama wenzake,
tulikubali kutokubaliana

01:03:11.225 --> 01:03:13.227
juu ya mambo mengi, uh,

01:03:13.261 --> 01:03:14.495
na, vizuri, mmoja wao

01:03:14.529 --> 01:03:17.599
ilikuwa hitaji la
Mpango wa H-bomu, ndio.

01:03:30.445 --> 01:03:33.214
Asante kwa kukutanisha
kwa taarifa fupi.

01:03:33.247 --> 01:03:34.716
Siwezi kuamini.

01:03:35.717 --> 01:03:37.251
Naam, sisi hapa.

01:03:37.285 --> 01:03:39.287
Nishike. Tunajua nini?

01:03:39.320 --> 01:03:41.824
Moja ya B-29 zetu zimeisha
Pasifiki ya Kaskazini

01:03:41.857 --> 01:03:43.358
imegundua mionzi.

01:03:43.391 --> 01:03:45.159
Je! tunazo karatasi za vichungi?

01:03:45.193 --> 01:03:47.195
Hakuna shaka hii ni nini.

01:03:47.228 --> 01:03:48.439
Ikulu ya Marekani inasema
kuna shaka.

01:03:48.463 --> 01:03:49.898
Mawazo ya kutamani, ninaogopa.

01:03:49.932 --> 01:03:52.634
Je, hizo ni za masafa marefu
karatasi za vichungi vya kugundua?

01:03:53.568 --> 01:03:55.637
Ni mtihani wa atomiki.

01:03:58.272 --> 01:03:59.674
Warusi wana bomu.

01:03:59.707 --> 01:04:03.444
Tunapaswa kuwa miaka
mbele yao, lakini wengine ...

01:04:03.478 --> 01:04:05.780
Mlikuwa nini jamani
Hufanya kazi Los Alamos

01:04:05.814 --> 01:04:06.949
Je, usalama haukuwa mkali?

01:04:06.982 --> 01:04:08.483
Bila shaka ilikuwa.
Hukuwepo.

01:04:08.516 --> 01:04:10.919
- Ilikuwa ...
- Nisamehe, daktari ...

01:04:10.953 --> 01:04:13.388
lakini nilikuwepo.

01:04:14.455 --> 01:04:15.790
Sasa tunaweza kuzingatia

01:04:15.824 --> 01:04:17.759
mechanics halisi
ya mlipuko.

01:04:17.792 --> 01:04:18.927
Mawazo yoyote?

01:04:18.961 --> 01:04:20.695
naita
hii "risasi."

01:04:20.728 --> 01:04:24.265
Sisi moto chunk ya fissionable
nyenzo ndani ya nyanja kubwa

01:04:24.298 --> 01:04:26.801
kwa nguvu ya kutosha
kufikia umuhimu.

01:04:26.835 --> 01:04:28.503
Je, tunafikiri nini? Mtu yeyote?

01:04:28.536 --> 01:04:30.338
nimekuwa
kufikiria juu ya implosion.

01:04:30.371 --> 01:04:32.340
Vilipuzi karibu na
mlipuko wa ndani,

01:04:32.373 --> 01:04:34.409
kuponda nyenzo.

01:04:34.442 --> 01:04:36.377
Ningependa
kuchunguza wazo hilo.

01:04:36.411 --> 01:04:38.713
Nitazungumza na Ordnance,
kukufanya ulipue mambo.

01:04:39.714 --> 01:04:40.816
Maendeleo?

01:04:40.849 --> 01:04:42.684
Nimefurahi kukuona pia.

01:04:42.717 --> 01:04:44.485
Kutana na kikosi cha Uingereza.

01:04:44.519 --> 01:04:46.354
Dk. Oppenheimer, Klaus Fuchs.

01:04:46.387 --> 01:04:48.256
Umekuwa Muingereza kwa muda gani?

01:04:48.289 --> 01:04:49.500
Tangu Hitler alisema
mimi sikuwa Mjerumani.

01:04:49.524 --> 01:04:53.327
Uh-ha. Njoo, karibu
kwa Los Alamos.

01:04:53.361 --> 01:04:55.229
Shule inaendelea.

01:04:55.263 --> 01:04:57.565
Baa. Inakimbia kila wakati.

01:04:57.598 --> 01:05:00.601
Na nilifikiria njia
kupunguza wafanyakazi wa msaada.

01:05:01.569 --> 01:05:03.571
- Je!
- Bi Serber, ndiyo.

01:05:03.604 --> 01:05:05.007
Nimetoa kazi
kwa wake wote.

01:05:05.040 --> 01:05:06.507
Msimamizi, wasimamizi wa maktaba, hesabu.

01:05:06.541 --> 01:05:08.844
Tunapunguza wafanyikazi,
kuweka familia pamoja.

01:05:08.877 --> 01:05:11.446
- Je, wanawake hawa wamehitimu?
- Usiwe na ujinga.

01:05:11.479 --> 01:05:13.849
Hizi ni baadhi ya mkali zaidi
akili katika jamii yetu.

01:05:13.882 --> 01:05:15.450
Na wao tayari
usalama umeondolewa.

01:05:15.483 --> 01:05:17.361
Nimekujulisha Mkuu
Groves umekuwa ukishikilia

01:05:17.385 --> 01:05:18.854
mtambuka
majadiliano ya wazi

01:05:18.887 --> 01:05:20.588
- kwa msingi wa usiku.
- Wafunge.

01:05:20.621 --> 01:05:22.958
Compartmentalization ni
ufunguo wa kudumisha usalama...

01:05:22.991 --> 01:05:24.492
Ni wanaume wa juu tu.

01:05:24.525 --> 01:05:26.360
Ambao labda wanawasiliana
pamoja na wasaidizi.

01:05:26.394 --> 01:05:27.595
Wanaume hawa sio wajinga.

01:05:27.628 --> 01:05:29.464
- Wanaweza kuwa wenye busara.
- Siipendi.

01:05:29.497 --> 01:05:32.400
Hupendi chochote cha kutosha
ili kuwa mtihani wa haki.

01:05:37.940 --> 01:05:40.475
Mara moja kwa wiki. Wanaume wa juu tu.

01:05:40.508 --> 01:05:41.877
Ningependa kuleta
ndugu yangu hapa.

01:05:41.910 --> 01:05:43.377
Hapana.

01:05:44.012 --> 01:05:45.780
Lo, Nichols...

01:05:46.915 --> 01:05:48.851
Bado sijasikia
kwamba kibali changu cha usalama

01:05:48.884 --> 01:05:50.451
- imeidhinishwa.
- Haijafanya hivyo.

01:05:50.485 --> 01:05:51.854
Tutaenda Chicago kesho.

01:05:51.887 --> 01:05:52.921
Hapana, unapaswa kusubiri.

01:05:54.123 --> 01:05:55.232
Unafahamu kuwa Wanazi
kuwa na mwanzo wa miaka miwili.

01:05:55.256 --> 01:05:58.326
Dr. Oppenheimer, ukweli
kwamba kibali chako cha usalama

01:05:58.359 --> 01:06:00.361
inadhihirika kuwa ngumu
kupata sio kosa langu.

01:06:00.394 --> 01:06:01.662
Ni yako.

01:06:01.696 --> 01:06:03.631
Labda isiwe kosa lako,
lakini ni shida yako.

01:06:03.664 --> 01:06:04.665
Kwa sababu ninaenda.

01:06:04.699 --> 01:06:08.469
Na ngapi
watu walikuwa katika haya, uh,

01:06:08.503 --> 01:06:10.705
- majadiliano ya wazi?
- Nyingi mno.

01:06:10.738 --> 01:06:12.083
Compartmentalization ilikuwa
inapaswa kuwa itifaki.

01:06:12.107 --> 01:06:14.042
Tulikuwa katika mbio
dhidi ya Wanazi.

01:06:14.076 --> 01:06:16.511
Na sasa mbio ni
dhidi ya Soviets.

01:06:16.544 --> 01:06:18.056
- Sio isipokuwa tuanze.
- Robert.

01:06:18.080 --> 01:06:21.482
Walifyatua tu bunduki ya kuanzia.

01:06:21.516 --> 01:06:23.484
Ni nini asili ya
kifaa walicholipua?

01:06:23.518 --> 01:06:25.063
Data
inaonyesha inaweza kuwa

01:06:25.087 --> 01:06:27.388
kifaa cha plutonium implosion.

01:06:27.421 --> 01:06:30.525
Kama wewe
iliyojengwa huko Los Alamos.

01:06:30.558 --> 01:06:32.393
Warusi wana bomu,

01:06:32.426 --> 01:06:33.704
Truman anahitaji
kujua nini kinafuata.

01:06:33.728 --> 01:06:35.530
Nini kinafuata? Mazungumzo ya silaha.

01:06:35.563 --> 01:06:37.431
- Mazungumzo ya silaha.
- Ni wazi.

01:06:38.366 --> 01:06:39.567
Vipi kuhusu Super?

01:06:39.600 --> 01:06:41.335
Truman hata anajua kuhusu hilo?

01:06:41.369 --> 01:06:43.371
Je, tulimueleza kwa ufupi kuhusu hilo?

01:06:43.404 --> 01:06:44.472
Si hasa.

01:06:44.505 --> 01:06:45.808
Bado hatujui

01:06:45.841 --> 01:06:47.608
ikiwa ni bomu ya hidrojeni
inawezekana kitaalam.

01:06:47.642 --> 01:06:49.553
Kweli, ufahamu wangu ni
huyo Mwambizi alipendekeza?

01:06:49.577 --> 01:06:51.412
- Ndiyo.
- Kwa Los Alamos?

01:06:51.445 --> 01:06:53.091
Miundo ya Teller imekuwa daima
imekuwa pori isiyowezekana.

01:06:53.115 --> 01:06:55.449
Ingekuwa wewe
toa kwa gari la ng'ombe.

01:06:55.483 --> 01:06:56.760
- Sio ndege.
- Oppie.

01:06:56.784 --> 01:07:00.488
Samahani, Dk. Lawrence,
unataka kutoa maoni?

01:07:01.722 --> 01:07:02.825
Hapana.

01:07:04.692 --> 01:07:06.962
Kwa sababu kama inaweza
tuweke mbele tena,

01:07:06.995 --> 01:07:10.032
Rais wa
Marekani

01:07:10.065 --> 01:07:12.067
inahitaji kujua juu yake.

01:07:13.601 --> 01:07:15.403
Na ikiwa Warusi
tayari kujua kuhusu hilo,

01:07:15.436 --> 01:07:18.439
kutoka kwa mpelelezi huko Los Alamos,

01:07:18.472 --> 01:07:19.774
basi lazima tuende.

01:07:19.808 --> 01:07:22.777
Hakuna uthibitisho hapo
alikuwa jasusi huko Los Alamos.

01:07:22.811 --> 01:07:23.879
Robert.

01:07:28.716 --> 01:07:30.484
Wanaiweka chini
uwanja wa mpira?

01:07:30.518 --> 01:07:32.453
Uga hautumiki tena.

01:07:32.486 --> 01:07:34.722
Vile vile.

01:07:36.024 --> 01:07:38.459
- Oppie.
- Dk Fermi.

01:07:41.163 --> 01:07:42.496
Nasikia una mji mdogo.

01:07:42.530 --> 01:07:43.764
Ndiyo. Njoo uone.

01:07:45.499 --> 01:07:49.604
Nani angeweza kufikiria moja kwa moja
mahali kama hiyo? Huh?

01:07:49.637 --> 01:07:51.572
Kila mtu atakuwa kichaa.

01:07:51.606 --> 01:07:55.476
Asante kwa kura
wa kujiamini, Szilard.

01:07:55.509 --> 01:07:59.147
Je, sisi kweli... tunafanya kweli
unahitaji hiyo katika maelezo?

01:07:59.181 --> 01:08:01.616
Unaenda lini
ili kuijaribu?

01:08:01.649 --> 01:08:02.683
Tulifanya hivyo.

01:08:02.717 --> 01:08:07.089
Ya kwanza ya kujitegemea
mmenyuko wa mnyororo wa nyuklia.

01:08:07.122 --> 01:08:08.756
Je Groves hakukuambia?

01:08:08.789 --> 01:08:10.424
Hapana.

01:08:14.930 --> 01:08:18.033
Moja kwa wakati,
tafadhali, mmoja baada ya mwingine.

01:08:18.066 --> 01:08:19.533
Dk Oppenheimer?

01:08:20.635 --> 01:08:23.104
Nilijaribu Wafanyakazi. Wao
aliuliza kama naweza kuandika.

01:08:23.138 --> 01:08:24.438
Je, unaweza?

01:08:24.471 --> 01:08:25.606
Harvard alisahau kufundisha hivyo

01:08:25.640 --> 01:08:27.475
juu ya mhitimu
kozi ya kemia.

01:08:28.844 --> 01:08:31.746
Condon, weka Bibi Hornig
hapa kwenye timu ya plutonium.

01:08:37.518 --> 01:08:39.187
Nini kuzimu
unafanya huko Chicago?

01:08:39.220 --> 01:08:40.688
Kutembelea Met?

01:08:40.720 --> 01:08:41.732
- Kwa nini? Kwa nini?
- Kweli, huwezi kuongea na ...

01:08:41.756 --> 01:08:43.791
Kwa sababu tuna kila haki ...

01:08:43.825 --> 01:08:46.161
Una tu
haki ninazokupa.

01:08:46.194 --> 01:08:47.662
Hakuna zaidi, si chini.

01:08:47.694 --> 01:08:50.131
Sisi ni watu wazima kujaribu
kuendesha mradi hapa.

01:08:50.165 --> 01:08:51.867
Huu ni ujinga.

01:08:51.899 --> 01:08:53.667
Mwambie.

01:08:53.701 --> 01:08:56.837
Compartmentalization ni
itifaki tuliyokubaliana.

01:08:57.973 --> 01:08:59.207
Inatosha wazimu huu.

01:08:59.241 --> 01:09:01.609
Hakuna mtu anayeweza kufanya kazi chini yake
masharti haya.

01:09:01.642 --> 01:09:06.081
Unajua nini,
Generalissimo? niliacha.

01:09:06.113 --> 01:09:07.515
Asante kwa lolote.

01:09:09.617 --> 01:09:11.118
Bora zaidi
mbali bila yeye.

01:09:12.553 --> 01:09:13.587
Je, wewe si wasiwasi zaidi

01:09:13.621 --> 01:09:15.991
kuhusu busara zake huko nje?

01:09:16.024 --> 01:09:18.426
Tutamfanya auawe.

01:09:19.261 --> 01:09:21.830
Nilikuwa natania tu.

01:09:21.863 --> 01:09:24.799
- Hapana, ananichukia, sio Amerika.
- Unajua, Mkuu,

01:09:24.832 --> 01:09:27.169
sio kila mtu ana mashimo
kuvuta kama yangu.

01:09:27.202 --> 01:09:29.037
Nadhani sielewi.

01:09:29.071 --> 01:09:31.238
Hukuniajiri
licha ya maisha yangu ya zamani ya mrengo wa kushoto.

01:09:31.273 --> 01:09:33.008
Uliniajiri kwa sababu yake.

01:09:34.009 --> 01:09:35.978
Kwa hivyo unaweza kunidhibiti.

01:09:36.011 --> 01:09:38.612
Naam, mimi si hivyo hila.

01:09:38.645 --> 01:09:40.680
Mimi ni askari mnyenyekevu tu.

01:09:40.715 --> 01:09:42.225
Wewe si mnyenyekevu
wala askari tu.

01:09:42.250 --> 01:09:43.261
Alisomea engineering katika MIT

01:09:43.285 --> 01:09:45.120
Hatia kama inavyodaiwa.

01:09:45.153 --> 01:09:46.654
Naam, sasa sisi
kuelewa kila mmoja,

01:09:46.687 --> 01:09:48.131
labda unaweza kunipata
kibali changu cha usalama

01:09:48.156 --> 01:09:50.959
ili niweze kuigiza
muujiza huu kwako.

01:09:55.864 --> 01:09:57.607
<i>Mkuu
Groves, ulikuwa unafahamu</i>

01:09:57.631 --> 01:09:59.935
<i>ya Dk. Oppenheimer
vyama vya mrengo wa kushoto</i>

01:09:59.968 --> 01:10:01.635
<i>ulipomteua?</i>

01:10:01.669 --> 01:10:03.314
Nilijua hapo
kulikuwa na tuhuma juu yake.

01:10:03.338 --> 01:10:05.207
Nilikuwa namfahamu
alikuwa na uliokithiri sana

01:10:05.240 --> 01:10:06.607
asili huria.

01:10:06.640 --> 01:10:08.252
Kwa maoni yako, ingekuwa
yeye milele kwa uangalifu

01:10:08.276 --> 01:10:09.577
kufanya kitendo cha kukosa uaminifu?

01:10:09.610 --> 01:10:11.213
Ningeshangaa ikiwa angefanya hivyo.

01:10:11.246 --> 01:10:14.316
Kwa hivyo ulikuwa kamili
kujiamini katika uadilifu wake.

01:10:14.349 --> 01:10:15.750
Huko Los Alamos, ndio,

01:10:15.783 --> 01:10:17.119
ambayo ni wapi mimi
kweli alimjua.

01:10:17.152 --> 01:10:19.121
Mkuu, ulifanya yako
maafisa wa usalama

01:10:19.154 --> 01:10:20.621
kwenye mradi nakushauri

01:10:20.654 --> 01:10:22.133
dhidi ya kibali
ya Dk. Oppenheimer?

01:10:22.157 --> 01:10:25.961
Hawakuweza na wasingeweza
kumsafisha mpaka niliposisitiza.

01:10:25.994 --> 01:10:28.629
Na ni salama kusema kwamba wewe
alikuwa na ujuzi mzuri sana

01:10:28.662 --> 01:10:29.907
ya Dk. Oppenheimer
faili ya usalama.

01:10:29.931 --> 01:10:31.599
nilifanya.

01:10:31.632 --> 01:10:32.810
Kweli, basi kuna tu
swali moja kweli

01:10:32.834 --> 01:10:34.302
Nahitaji kujibiwa hapa leo.

01:10:34.336 --> 01:10:36.038
Kwa kuzingatia
miongozo ya sasa ya AEC,

01:10:36.071 --> 01:10:38.773
ungeweka wazi
Dk. Oppenheimer leo?

01:10:38.807 --> 01:10:40.876
Je! unayo miongozo?

01:10:47.949 --> 01:10:50.618
Chini ya sasa
Miongozo ya AEC,

01:10:50.651 --> 01:10:52.686
ungeweka wazi
Dk. Oppenheimer leo?

01:11:04.900 --> 01:11:08.702
Fizikia na Mpya
Mexico, je!

01:11:08.736 --> 01:11:11.772
Mungu wangu. Safari gani.

01:11:11.807 --> 01:11:13.275
Ndio maana unahitaji muunganisho.

01:11:13.308 --> 01:11:14.843
Ninamteua Lomanitz.

01:11:16.011 --> 01:11:17.079
Utakuwa sawa.

01:11:17.112 --> 01:11:18.280
Kwa njia hii, waheshimiwa.

01:11:28.256 --> 01:11:30.092
- Dk Lawrence.
- Leslie.

01:11:30.125 --> 01:11:32.693
Ningependa kukukumbusha nini
tulizungumza huko Berkeley.

01:11:32.726 --> 01:11:35.063
Compartmentalization. I
kuelewa kabisa.

01:11:38.233 --> 01:11:39.234
Sawa.

01:11:40.402 --> 01:11:41.837
Asante.

01:11:49.743 --> 01:11:50.988
<i>Salamu
kutoka Berkeley.</i>

01:11:51.012 --> 01:11:53.148
Niko hapa kusasisha
juu ya maendeleo yetu

01:11:53.181 --> 01:11:54.715
na kuomba mchango wako.

01:11:54.748 --> 01:11:56.127
Ili kufanya hivyo, ninaenda
kuwa na kushiriki

01:11:56.151 --> 01:11:59.821
mambo machache ambayo Mkuu
Groves aliniambia nisifanye hivyo.

01:11:59.855 --> 01:12:01.655
Samahani Mkuu, I
alisema nimeelewa,

01:12:01.689 --> 01:12:02.756
si kwamba nilikubali.

01:12:02.790 --> 01:12:04.326
'Kaya.

01:12:04.359 --> 01:12:06.394
Waungwana, kwa biashara.

01:12:06.428 --> 01:12:08.796
Kulikuwa na fununu za
ujasusi huko Los Alamos.

01:12:08.830 --> 01:12:10.308
Haijathibitishwa.
Haijathibitishwa.

01:12:10.332 --> 01:12:11.799
naambiwa

01:12:11.833 --> 01:12:13.144
kwamba walikuwepo
Wakomunisti kwenye mradi huo.

01:12:13.168 --> 01:12:14.936
Hatukujua
kuajiri Wakomunisti wowote.

01:12:14.970 --> 01:12:16.746
Nataka tu kujua,
yeyote kati yao alihusika

01:12:16.770 --> 01:12:18.240
katika majadiliano ya Super?

01:12:18.273 --> 01:12:20.451
Naonekana kukukumbuka ukidai
kaka yako njoo Los Alamos.

01:12:20.475 --> 01:12:22.743
Ndugu yangu alikuwa ameondoka
Chama wakati huo.

01:12:22.776 --> 01:12:24.012
Vipi kuhusu Lomanitz?

01:12:24.045 --> 01:12:25.779
Lomanitz hakuwahi
Alifanya kazi Los Alamos

01:12:25.814 --> 01:12:26.815
Alikuwa kiungo.

01:12:26.848 --> 01:12:28.016
Usalama wetu ulikuwa mkali,

01:12:28.049 --> 01:12:29.427
kama Kanali wa zamani
Nichols anajua vizuri.

01:12:29.451 --> 01:12:31.019
Usalama wetu ulikuwa kama
tight kama inaweza kuwa

01:12:31.052 --> 01:12:32.420
kutokana na
watu wanaohusika,

01:12:32.454 --> 01:12:34.289
lakini majaribio yalifanywa.

01:12:34.322 --> 01:12:35.333
Hiyo inapaswa kumaanisha nini?

01:12:35.357 --> 01:12:36.925
Sote tumesoma faili yake hapa.

01:12:37.959 --> 01:12:39.961
Je, tunahitaji kuzungumza
Kuhusu Jean Tatlock

01:12:40.495 --> 01:12:42.663
Au tukio la Chevalier?

01:12:47.269 --> 01:12:48.669
'Nisamehe.

01:12:51.973 --> 01:12:53.942
Hiyo ni
Lomanitz, mstari wa kwanza.

01:12:59.814 --> 01:13:00.849
Habari, Rossi.

01:13:00.882 --> 01:13:04.085
<i>Je! O-Sawa, tulia tu.</i>

01:13:05.053 --> 01:13:08.290
Kumekuwa na upotoshaji mwingine.
Lomanitz ameandikishwa hivi punde.

01:13:08.323 --> 01:13:10.791
- Tuko vitani, Daktari.
- Usiwe mpumbavu, Nichols.

01:13:10.825 --> 01:13:12.827
Tunamhitaji huyu mtoto.
Irekebishe, je!

01:13:12.861 --> 01:13:14.062
Haikuwa kosa.

01:13:14.095 --> 01:13:15.439
Rafiki yako Lomanitz
imekuwa ikijaribu

01:13:15.463 --> 01:13:17.731
kuunganisha Maabara ya Mionzi.

01:13:17.765 --> 01:13:19.067
Aliahidi kuacha yote hayo.

01:13:19.100 --> 01:13:21.002
Naam, hajafanya hivyo.

01:13:21.036 --> 01:13:22.904
Afisa usalama katika
Berkeley ana wasiwasi kuhusu

01:13:22.938 --> 01:13:25.240
Kujipenyeza kwa Kikomunisti
kupitia muungano huo,

01:13:25.273 --> 01:13:27.876
-F.A...
- F.A.E.C.T.

01:13:30.278 --> 01:13:33.982
Nikiwa huko wiki ijayo,
Nitashuka ili nimwone.

01:13:36.251 --> 01:13:37.986
Kibali chako cha Q kilipitia.

01:13:41.523 --> 01:13:42.967
Ni muhimu wewe
si kudumisha au upya

01:13:42.991 --> 01:13:45.260
vyama vyovyote vinavyotia shaka.

01:13:49.998 --> 01:13:52.500
<i>Daktari, je!
fikiria mawasiliano ya kijamii</i>

01:13:52.534 --> 01:13:54.869
kati ya mtu aliyechumbiwa
juu ya kazi ya siri ya vita

01:13:54.903 --> 01:13:56.271
na Wakomunisti ilikuwa hatari?

01:13:56.304 --> 01:13:59.975
Ufahamu wangu wa hatari
itakuwa kubwa zaidi leo.

01:14:00.008 --> 01:14:02.911
I mean, ni haki ya kusema
kwamba katika miaka ya vita,

01:14:02.944 --> 01:14:06.147
<i>ulihisi kwamba mawasiliano kama hayo
zilikuwa hatari.</i>

01:14:12.587 --> 01:14:15.557
<i>Walikuwa conceivably
hatari, ndiyo.</i>

01:14:15.590 --> 01:14:17.859
<i>Namaanisha, kwa kweli,</i>

01:14:17.892 --> 01:14:19.928
<i>Wakomunisti wanaojulikana.</i>

01:14:22.063 --> 01:14:24.299
<i>Angalia...</i>

01:14:24.332 --> 01:14:25.867
Nimekuwa na siri nyingi

01:14:25.900 --> 01:14:28.870
<i>kichwani mwangu kwa muda mrefu.</i>

01:14:29.838 --> 01:14:31.115
<i>Haijalishi nani
Ninashirikiana na.</i>

01:14:31.139 --> 01:14:34.042
sizungumzii
siri hizo.

01:14:41.449 --> 01:14:43.084
Ulisema
katika taarifa yako

01:14:43.118 --> 01:14:49.057
ambayo ulipaswa kuona
Jean Tatlock mnamo 1943.

01:14:50.525 --> 01:14:52.193
Uliondoka.

01:14:53.428 --> 01:14:54.863
Si neno.

01:14:54.896 --> 01:14:57.365
Ulifikiria nini
hilo lingenifanya?

01:14:58.466 --> 01:14:59.534
Niliandika.

01:14:59.567 --> 01:15:01.970
Kurasa zisizo na kitu.

01:15:04.239 --> 01:15:06.574
Ulienda wapi?

01:15:06.608 --> 01:15:09.044
- Siwezi kukuambia.
- Kwa nini sivyo?

01:15:09.077 --> 01:15:11.813
Kwa sababu wewe ni Mkomunisti.

01:15:13.348 --> 01:15:15.216
Kwa nini ulilazimika kumuona?

01:15:15.250 --> 01:15:18.353
Kwa sababu alikuwa nayo
ilionyesha hamu kubwa

01:15:18.386 --> 01:15:20.055
kuniona kabla hatujaondoka.

01:15:20.088 --> 01:15:21.256
Wakati huo sikuweza,

01:15:21.289 --> 01:15:25.093
lakini nilihisi hivyo
ilibidi anione.

01:15:25.126 --> 01:15:27.629
Alikuwa anapitia
matibabu ya akili.

01:15:27.662 --> 01:15:29.898
Alikuwa na furaha sana.

01:15:29.931 --> 01:15:31.933
Umegundua kwanini
ilibidi akuone?

01:15:37.038 --> 01:15:39.107
Kwa sababu alikuwa bado
kwa upendo na mimi.

01:15:46.314 --> 01:15:48.383
Alitumia usiku
pamoja, sivyo?

01:15:56.358 --> 01:15:57.392
Ndiyo.

01:16:03.064 --> 01:16:06.935
Unaingia na kutoka katika maisha yangu,

01:16:06.968 --> 01:16:09.437
na huna
kuniambia kwanini.

01:16:09.471 --> 01:16:10.939
Sasa hiyo ni nguvu.

01:16:10.972 --> 01:16:13.007
Si kwamba ninafurahia.

01:16:13.975 --> 01:16:16.111
Ningependa kuwa hapa
kwako kama unahitaji.

01:16:16.144 --> 01:16:18.613
Lakini unayo mengine
vipaumbele sasa.

01:16:18.646 --> 01:16:21.416
Nina mke na mtoto.

01:16:22.417 --> 01:16:25.220
Hiyo sivyo pia
ya sisi ni kuzungumza juu.

01:16:28.656 --> 01:16:30.525
Jean.

01:16:30.558 --> 01:16:32.694
Uliniuliza nije.

01:16:32.727 --> 01:16:35.096
Na ninafurahi nilifanya.

01:16:35.730 --> 01:16:38.299
Lakini siwezi kukuona tena.

01:16:40.702 --> 01:16:42.404
Lakini vipi ikiwa nitakuhitaji?

01:16:45.974 --> 01:16:48.943
Ulisema utafanya
jibu kila wakati.

01:16:51.413 --> 01:16:52.547
Sio neno?

01:16:53.816 --> 01:16:54.892
<i>Je, ulifikiri hivyo
inaendana na usalama mzuri?</i>

01:16:54.916 --> 01:16:57.585
Kwa kweli, ilikuwa.

01:16:57.619 --> 01:16:59.988
<i>Si neno.</i>

01:17:00.021 --> 01:17:02.190
Ulifanya lini
kumuona baada ya hapo?

01:17:10.598 --> 01:17:12.267
Sikumwona tena.

01:17:18.473 --> 01:17:21.109
Naweza kufanya ya mwisho
treni kurudi Princeton.

01:17:21.142 --> 01:17:24.312
Kitty, sikusema chochote
ambayo sikuwa nimekuambia.

01:17:24.345 --> 01:17:26.481
Leo umesema
historia, sivyo?

01:17:26.514 --> 01:17:28.049
Huu ni usikilizaji uliofungwa.

01:17:29.751 --> 01:17:31.362
Ikiwa hawana
toa nakala,

01:17:31.386 --> 01:17:33.388
- Nina hakika utafanya.
- Nilikuwa chini ya kiapo.

01:17:33.421 --> 01:17:35.190
Naam, ulikuwa
chini ya kiapo kwa ajili yangu

01:17:35.223 --> 01:17:37.025
ulipoenda kumuona Jean.

01:17:37.692 --> 01:17:39.127
Unajua, wewe...

01:17:40.028 --> 01:17:42.330
unakaa hapo siku baada ya siku,

01:17:42.363 --> 01:17:45.400
kuwaacha wachague
maisha yetu vipande vipande.

01:17:48.403 --> 01:17:50.104
Kwa nini usipigane?

01:17:53.241 --> 01:17:56.377
Robert, mimi ni
si kumweka pale juu.

01:18:01.516 --> 01:18:04.385
Dk. Oppenheimer, ni
heshima. Tafadhali, kaa.

01:18:04.419 --> 01:18:08.022
Hakuna haja, nilitaka tu
kuangalia kama ni lazima

01:18:08.056 --> 01:18:10.225
zungumza na Lomanitz nikiwa
hapa, kutokana na wasiwasi wako.

01:18:10.258 --> 01:18:12.360
Kweli, ningesema hivyo
juu yako, Profesa,

01:18:12.393 --> 01:18:14.562
- lakini ningekuwa mwangalifu.
- Uh-huh. Kueleweka.

01:18:14.596 --> 01:18:17.332
Oh, na, um,
kuhusu Muungano,

01:18:17.365 --> 01:18:19.133
Nilitaka kukupa
kichwa juu ya ...

01:18:19.167 --> 01:18:20.502
juu ya mtu anayeitwa Eltenton.

01:18:20.535 --> 01:18:22.036
A vichwa-up?

01:18:22.070 --> 01:18:26.007
Ndiyo, ili tu apate
kuangalia sifa ni yote.

01:18:26.809 --> 01:18:28.243
Naam, ningependa
pata maelezo zaidi.

01:18:28.276 --> 01:18:30.612
Naam, mimi ... nina
miadi sasa

01:18:30.645 --> 01:18:32.080
na kesho naondoka mapema.

01:18:32.113 --> 01:18:33.648
Naam, kurudi kama
mapema upendavyo.

01:18:33.681 --> 01:18:36.017
Kwa kuwa huna wakati sasa.

01:18:36.684 --> 01:18:38.520
Ulirudi asubuhi iliyofuata.

01:18:38.553 --> 01:18:40.555
Nilifanya, ilibidi, kwa kweli.

01:18:41.489 --> 01:18:44.092
<i>Wakati huu, huko
alikuwa mwanaume mwingine.</i>

01:18:44.759 --> 01:18:46.261
Alisema anaitwa Pash.

01:18:46.294 --> 01:18:48.796
Pash. Ulikutana na Kanali Pash?

01:18:48.831 --> 01:18:50.374
Kanali Pash,
unaweza kusoma tafadhali

01:18:50.398 --> 01:18:54.202
kutoka kwa memo yako
Tarehe 29 Juni, 1943?

01:18:56.304 --> 01:18:58.406
"Matokeo ya ufuatiliaji
inayoendeshwa kwa mada

01:18:58.439 --> 01:19:01.276
"onyesha zaidi iwezekanavyo
Miunganisho ya Chama cha Kikomunisti.

01:19:01.309 --> 01:19:03.478
"Somo lilikutana na
alitumia muda mwingi

01:19:03.511 --> 01:19:05.713
"pamoja na Jean mmoja
Tatlock, Mkomunisti,

01:19:05.747 --> 01:19:07.215
rekodi ya nani imeambatanishwa."

01:19:07.248 --> 01:19:09.117
Somo likiwa
Dk Oppenheimer?

01:19:09.150 --> 01:19:11.619
- Ndiyo.
- Ambaye ulikuwa haujakutana naye?

01:19:11.653 --> 01:19:13.454
Sio basi,
lakini hivi karibuni.

01:19:13.488 --> 01:19:14.866
Yeye ni mkuu wa
usalama kwa mradi huo.

01:19:14.890 --> 01:19:16.124
Je, nisimjue?

01:19:16.157 --> 01:19:17.492
Hapana, anapaswa kukufahamu.

01:19:17.525 --> 01:19:19.427
Nisingekuweka kamwe
katika chumba na Pash.

01:19:19.460 --> 01:19:20.728
Kwa nini sivyo?

01:19:20.762 --> 01:19:22.831
Wakati Pash kwanza
kusikia kuhusu Lomanitz,

01:19:22.865 --> 01:19:25.800
aliwaambia FBI
alikuwa atamteka nyara,

01:19:25.834 --> 01:19:27.302
mpeleke kwenye mashua

01:19:27.335 --> 01:19:30.338
na kumhoji
kwa njia ya Kirusi.

01:19:32.473 --> 01:19:35.310
General Groves ameweka
nina jukumu fulani,

01:19:35.343 --> 01:19:37.579
na ni kama kuwa na
mtoto ambaye siwezi kumuona.

01:19:37.612 --> 01:19:39.714
- Ah.
- Kwa udhibiti wa kijijini.

01:19:39.747 --> 01:19:43.351
Kwa hivyo kukutana nawe ni kweli ...

01:19:44.452 --> 01:19:45.897
Sitachukua pia
muda wako mwingi.

01:19:45.921 --> 01:19:48.189
Hapana, hapana, hata kidogo.
Muda wowote utakaochagua.

01:19:48.222 --> 01:19:51.125
Mm. Bwana Johnson aliambia
mimi wa mazungumzo

01:19:51.159 --> 01:19:52.904
ulikuwa jana ndani
ambayo ninavutiwa sana.

01:19:52.928 --> 01:19:55.196
Imekuwa na wasiwasi siku nzima.

01:19:55.229 --> 01:19:57.732
Ndio, sikufanya hivyo
nataka kuzungumza na Lomanitz

01:19:57.765 --> 01:19:59.300
bila idhini.

01:19:59.334 --> 01:20:00.544
Hiyo sio maalum
maslahi niliyo nayo.

01:20:00.568 --> 01:20:02.537
Ni kitu a
kidogo zaidi...

01:20:03.571 --> 01:20:05.340
sawa, kwa maoni yangu,
serious zaidi.

01:20:05.373 --> 01:20:08.309
Sasa, wakati FBI alisema
habari kama hizo

01:20:08.343 --> 01:20:09.888
haitaruhusiwa kuingia
mahakama, Pash aliweka wazi

01:20:09.912 --> 01:20:13.681
hakuwa na nia ya kuondoka
shahidi yeyote aliyeachwa kushitakiwa.

01:20:13.715 --> 01:20:15.283
Sasa, FBI walimkashifu,

01:20:15.316 --> 01:20:16.885
lakini huyo ndiye mwanaume
unacheza na.

01:20:16.919 --> 01:20:19.621
Nakusanya umesikia
kuna vyama vingine

01:20:19.654 --> 01:20:22.357
nia ya kazi
wa Maabara ya Mionzi.

01:20:22.390 --> 01:20:26.294
Mwanaume aliyeunganishwa
Balozi wa Soviet

01:20:26.327 --> 01:20:29.364
imeonyeshwa, kupitia
watu wa kati,

01:20:29.397 --> 01:20:30.933
kwa watu kwenye mradi huu,

01:20:30.966 --> 01:20:34.402
kwamba alikuwa katika nafasi
kusambaza habari.

01:20:34.435 --> 01:20:37.271
Oh, kwa nini mtu yeyote juu ya
mradi unataka kufanya hivyo?

01:20:38.706 --> 01:20:41.242
Kusema ukweli, naona hivyo
kunaweza kuwa na mabishano

01:20:41.275 --> 01:20:43.678
kwa Amiri Jeshi Mkuu
kuwajulisha Warusi ...

01:20:43.711 --> 01:20:45.580
hao ni washirika wetu...

01:20:45.613 --> 01:20:48.516
lakini sipendi wazo la
inatoka kwa mlango wa nyuma.

01:20:48.549 --> 01:20:51.285
Huenda isiumie kuwa
kwa kuitazama.

01:20:52.687 --> 01:20:53.856
Na ulisema hivyo kwa Pash?

01:20:53.889 --> 01:20:55.390
Nilikuwa najaribu kuiweka

01:20:55.423 --> 01:20:58.259
katika muktadha wa
Urusi sio Ujerumani.

01:20:58.292 --> 01:21:02.697
Boris Pash ni mtoto wa
askofu wa Orthodox ya Urusi.

01:21:02.730 --> 01:21:06.234
Alizaliwa hapa, lakini mnamo 1918.
akarudi Urusi

01:21:06.267 --> 01:21:07.702
kupigana na Wabolshevik.

01:21:07.735 --> 01:21:09.914
Huyu ni mtu aliyeua
Wakomunisti kwa mikono yake mwenyewe.

01:21:09.938 --> 01:21:13.408
Mimi sio mwamuzi wa nani anafaa
au haipaswi kuwa na habari.

01:21:13.441 --> 01:21:15.486
Ni kazi yangu kuizuia
kutokana na kupita kinyume cha sheria.

01:21:15.510 --> 01:21:17.712
Je, ungekuwa a
maalum zaidi kidogo?

01:21:20.581 --> 01:21:23.451
Kuna mwanaume ambaye
jina lilitajwa kwangu

01:21:23.484 --> 01:21:25.586
mara kadhaa. Eltenton.

01:21:26.621 --> 01:21:29.724
Lo, naamini yeye ni
kemia anayefanya kazi katika Shell.

01:21:29.757 --> 01:21:32.293
Alizungumza na rafiki yake

01:21:32.326 --> 01:21:36.230
nani anafahamiana naye
mtu kwenye mradi.

01:21:37.465 --> 01:21:39.902
Na ulifikiri Pash atafanya
kuridhika na hilo?

01:21:39.935 --> 01:21:42.470
Nilikuwa najaribu
wape Eltenton

01:21:42.503 --> 01:21:43.839
bila kufungua mkebe wa minyoo.

01:21:43.872 --> 01:21:45.841
Niliwaambia a
hadithi ya jogoo-na-ng'ombe.

01:21:45.874 --> 01:21:47.408
Je, ulidanganya
Mkuu Groves pia?

01:21:47.442 --> 01:21:50.979
Hapana nilikubali kwake
kwamba nilimdanganya Pash.

01:21:51.013 --> 01:21:52.456
Je, unakumbuka
mazungumzo haya

01:21:52.480 --> 01:21:54.883
kuhusu tukio la Chevalier?

01:21:54.917 --> 01:21:57.318
Nimeona wengi sana
matoleo yake. Um...

01:21:57.351 --> 01:21:58.519
Sikuchanganyikiwa hapo awali,

01:21:58.553 --> 01:21:59.988
lakini nina hakika
kufika huko sasa.

01:22:00.022 --> 01:22:01.331
Na nini
ulikuwa hitimisho lako?

01:22:01.355 --> 01:22:03.725
Kwamba alikuwa chini yake
ushawishi wa

01:22:03.758 --> 01:22:06.627
Mmarekani wa kawaida
tabia ya mvulana wa shule

01:22:06.661 --> 01:22:10.264
kwamba kuna kitu kibaya
kuhusu kumwambia rafiki.

01:22:10.298 --> 01:22:12.333
Naam, sasa.

01:22:12.366 --> 01:22:14.802
Labda tujue kupitia
mawasiliano yalifanywa na nani?

01:22:14.837 --> 01:22:17.039
Hiyo ingehusisha... kuhusisha watu

01:22:17.072 --> 01:22:19.041
ambao hawatakiwi kuwa
kushiriki katika hili.

01:22:19.074 --> 01:22:21.844
Je, huyo ni mtu a
mwanachama wa mradi huo?

01:22:21.877 --> 01:22:26.414
Mjumbe wa kitivo, ndio,
lakini sio kwenye mradi, hapana.

01:22:26.447 --> 01:22:27.548
Ah.

01:22:27.582 --> 01:22:29.350
Hivyo Eltenton alifanya mbinu yake

01:22:29.383 --> 01:22:32.620
kupitia kwa mwanachama wa
kitivo hapa Berkeley?

01:22:34.355 --> 01:22:36.825
Nijuavyo mimi. Kama
nijuavyo, ndio.

01:22:36.859 --> 01:22:39.494
Lakini kuna-kunaweza kuwa

01:22:39.527 --> 01:22:42.263
zaidi ya mtu mmoja aliyehusika.

01:22:45.666 --> 01:22:48.871
Waungwana, ikiwa mimi ... ikiwa
naona sina ushirikiano,

01:22:48.904 --> 01:22:51.840
Nadhani unaweza kuelewa
hiyo ni kwa sababu ya msisitizo wangu

01:22:51.874 --> 01:22:54.475
katika kutokuwa na hatia
watu kwenye matatizo.

01:22:54.509 --> 01:22:56.310
<i>Unajaribu
kumlinda rafiki yako.</i>

01:22:56.344 --> 01:22:57.578
Je, ni nani anayekulinda?

01:22:57.612 --> 01:22:59.014
Naam, unaweza.

01:22:59.047 --> 01:23:00.381
Kama umenipa jina.

01:23:00.414 --> 01:23:02.350
Ukiniamuru, nitafanya.

01:23:02.383 --> 01:23:03.417
Hilo ni kosa, Robert.

01:23:03.451 --> 01:23:05.286
Unahitaji kujitolea kwa jina hili.

01:23:06.121 --> 01:23:07.789
<i>Na alifanya hivyo
kukupa jina?</i>

01:23:07.823 --> 01:23:08.957
<i>Alifanya hivyo.</i>

01:23:08.991 --> 01:23:10.458
- Lakini sivyo, sivyo?
- Hapana.

01:23:10.491 --> 01:23:11.970
Hapana. Kwa kweli, ilikuwa baadhi
miezi baadaye, sivyo?

01:23:11.994 --> 01:23:13.896
Ilikuwa.

01:23:13.929 --> 01:23:15.030
Unaniona naendelea.

01:23:15.063 --> 01:23:16.798
Naam, wewe ni ...

01:23:16.832 --> 01:23:18.666
wewe ni mvumilivu,
lakini hiyo ni kazi yako.

01:23:18.699 --> 01:23:22.403
Na-na kazi yangu ni kulinda
watu wanaofanya kazi kwa ajili yangu.

01:23:22.436 --> 01:23:24.438
Badala yetu
kwenda kwa hatua fulani,

01:23:24.472 --> 01:23:26.574
ambayo inaweza kuja
umakini wako...

01:23:27.943 --> 01:23:29.710
na kukusumbua,

01:23:29.744 --> 01:23:32.848
Ningependa kujadili
walio na wewe kwanza.

01:23:32.881 --> 01:23:34.382
Sijapanga mpango.

01:23:34.415 --> 01:23:36.751
Itabidi tu
digete jambo zima.

01:23:40.388 --> 01:23:43.091
<i>Katika miezi ndani
kati ya mahojiano yako</i>

01:23:43.125 --> 01:23:46.761
na Dk. Oppenheimer na wake
hatimaye kumtaja Chevalier,

01:23:46.794 --> 01:23:48.096
ulitumia rasilimali

01:23:48.130 --> 01:23:49.606
kujaribu kutafuta jina
ya mpatanishi?

01:23:49.630 --> 01:23:52.100
Rasilimali nyingi, ndio.

01:23:52.134 --> 01:23:54.368
Bila jina, kazi yetu
ilikuwa ngumu sana.

01:23:54.402 --> 01:23:55.838
Na ulifanya lini
kupokea jina?

01:23:55.871 --> 01:23:57.105
Nilikuwa nimeenda wakati huo

01:23:57.139 --> 01:23:59.574
-Oppenheimer hatimaye alitoa.
-Umekwenda?

01:23:59.607 --> 01:24:01.776
Walihisi wakati wangu ungekuwa
kuwa bora kutumika katika Ulaya

01:24:01.810 --> 01:24:04.545
kuamua hali
ya mradi wa bomu la Nazi.

01:24:04.579 --> 01:24:05.746
Nani alifanya?

01:24:06.849 --> 01:24:08.583
Jenerali Groves.

01:24:08.616 --> 01:24:10.384
Alinihamisha hadi London.

01:24:16.825 --> 01:24:18.927
<i>Ni mapema kidogo
kwa sherehe ya Krismasi.</i>

01:24:18.961 --> 01:24:20.963
Kitu kiko juu.

01:24:20.996 --> 01:24:23.031
Tolman amekuwa mbali.

01:24:23.065 --> 01:24:24.765
Wapi?

01:24:24.799 --> 01:24:26.367
Ruthu hatasema.

01:24:30.906 --> 01:24:31.907
Habari!

01:24:36.078 --> 01:24:37.612
Njoo, Ruthie.

01:24:37.645 --> 01:24:39.714
Huwezi kuniambia, unaweza kumwambia nani?

01:24:39.747 --> 01:24:42.483
Kugawanyika,
Oppie.

01:24:42.516 --> 01:24:43.895
Ni nini kinakufanya ufikirie mimi
unajua yuko wapi?

01:24:43.919 --> 01:24:45.620
Maana wewe
fanya kazi nzuri sana

01:24:45.653 --> 01:24:48.422
ya kujua alipo Bw. Tolman
ni wakati inahesabu.

01:24:48.456 --> 01:24:49.992
Kama sasa?

01:24:50.025 --> 01:24:53.461
Makini!

01:24:56.664 --> 01:24:58.599
Krismasi ya mapema
sasa kwa ajili yenu nyote.

01:25:06.674 --> 01:25:09.044
<i>Marubani wa Uingereza
niweke kwenye bomu.</i>

01:25:09.077 --> 01:25:11.079
Ilinionyesha the-the
oksijeni, unajua,

01:25:11.113 --> 01:25:12.848
lakini niliivuruga.

01:25:12.881 --> 01:25:15.483
Lo, waliponifungua ndani
Scotland, nilikuwa nimepoteza fahamu.

01:25:15.516 --> 01:25:17.718
Lakini nilijifanya
Ningekuwa napumzika.

01:25:18.686 --> 01:25:20.122
Tafadhali furahia sherehe yako.

01:25:21.489 --> 01:25:22.790
Je!
ni kubwa ya kutosha?

01:25:22.824 --> 01:25:24.092
Ili kumaliza vita?

01:25:24.126 --> 01:25:27.029
Ili kumaliza vita vyote.

01:25:29.865 --> 01:25:33.936
Uh, Heisenberg alitafuta
mimi huko Copenhagen.

01:25:33.969 --> 01:25:35.703
Ilikuwa baridi,

01:25:35.736 --> 01:25:37.772
mwanafunzi wangu wa zamani
kufanya kazi kwa Wanazi.

01:25:37.806 --> 01:25:41.709
Aliniambia baadhi
mambo ya kunivuta.

01:25:42.610 --> 01:25:45.948
Fission endelevu
athari katika uranium.

01:25:45.981 --> 01:25:48.183
Hiyo inasikika zaidi
kinu kuliko bomu.

01:25:48.216 --> 01:25:49.650
Je, alitaja
usambazaji wa gesi?

01:25:49.684 --> 01:25:51.954
Alionekana umakini zaidi
juu ya maji mazito.

01:25:51.987 --> 01:25:53.688
Kama msimamizi?

01:25:53.721 --> 01:25:55.090
Ndio, badala ya grafiti.

01:25:58.126 --> 01:25:59.493
Je!

01:25:59.527 --> 01:26:01.696
Alichukua mkondo mbaya.

01:26:01.729 --> 01:26:04.199
Tuko mbele. Na na wewe
hapa ili kutusaidia, Niels.

01:26:04.232 --> 01:26:06.500
Samahani, unaweza...

01:26:06.534 --> 01:26:09.470
unaweza kutupa a
sasa, waungwana?

01:26:15.643 --> 01:26:18.180
Siko hapa kusaidia, Robert.

01:26:18.213 --> 01:26:20.115
Nilijua unaweza
fanya hivi bila mimi.

01:26:20.148 --> 01:26:21.249
Basi kwa nini umekuja?

01:26:21.283 --> 01:26:22.717
Kuzungumza baada ya.

01:26:22.750 --> 01:26:24.719
Nguvu unayokaribia kufichua

01:26:24.752 --> 01:26:26.955
itaishi milele zaidi ya Wanazi.

01:26:28.023 --> 01:26:29.623
Na ulimwengu haujaandaliwa.

01:26:29.657 --> 01:26:31.059
"Unaweza kuinua jiwe

01:26:31.093 --> 01:26:33.728
bila kuwa tayari
nyoka aliyefunuliwa."

01:26:33.761 --> 01:26:35.139
Tunapaswa kufanya
wanasiasa wanaelewa,

01:26:35.163 --> 01:26:37.265
hii si silaha mpya.

01:26:37.299 --> 01:26:38.766
Ni ulimwengu mpya.

01:26:38.799 --> 01:26:42.170
Nitakuwa huko nje nikifanya
Ninachoweza, lakini wewe ...

01:26:42.204 --> 01:26:44.772
wewe ni Prometheus wa Amerika.

01:26:44.806 --> 01:26:47.042
Mtu aliyewapa nguvu

01:26:47.075 --> 01:26:49.111
kujiangamiza wenyewe,

01:26:49.144 --> 01:26:50.778
na wataliheshimu hilo.

01:26:50.812 --> 01:26:52.981
Na kazi yako kweli inaanza.

01:26:56.918 --> 01:27:00.055
Samahani, Oppie,
lakini kuna simu.

01:27:01.189 --> 01:27:03.925
Kutoka San Francisco.

01:27:10.198 --> 01:27:11.900
Robert!

01:27:15.137 --> 01:27:16.670
Robert?

01:27:17.339 --> 01:27:19.908
Robert. Robert.

01:27:19.941 --> 01:27:22.144
Mungu, kuna nini?

01:27:22.177 --> 01:27:23.945
Nini kilitokea?

01:27:24.813 --> 01:27:26.747
Baba yake aliita.

01:27:26.781 --> 01:27:28.917
Walimkuta
jana katika kuoga.

01:27:29.918 --> 01:27:31.053
WHO?

01:27:32.054 --> 01:27:34.056
Alichukua vidonge.

01:27:34.089 --> 01:27:35.991
<i>Imeacha dokezo, haijatiwa saini.</i>

01:27:36.992 --> 01:27:37.959
Alichukua barbiturates,

01:27:37.993 --> 01:27:39.928
lakini kulikuwa na klorini
hydrate katika damu yake.

01:27:43.298 --> 01:27:44.632
Kulikuwa na noti.

01:27:44.665 --> 01:27:46.968
Jean Tatlock?

01:27:52.740 --> 01:27:54.742
Tulikuwa pamoja.

01:27:54.775 --> 01:27:57.578
Alisema alinihitaji. Mimi...

01:27:59.680 --> 01:28:02.616
Nikamwambia mimi...mimi
si ...

01:28:02.650 --> 01:28:04.286
Nikamwambia siwezi...

01:28:04.319 --> 01:28:05.987
Hapana, ilikuwa ... ilikuwa mimi.

01:28:08.990 --> 01:28:11.093
Huwezi kupata kutenda dhambi

01:28:11.126 --> 01:28:12.928
na kisha tuwe wote
kukuonea huruma

01:28:12.961 --> 01:28:15.831
kwamba ilikuwa na matokeo.

01:28:17.899 --> 01:28:20.102
Unajivuta pamoja.

01:28:23.771 --> 01:28:25.907
Unajua, watu
hapa inategemea wewe.

01:28:28.410 --> 01:28:29.878
Donald, ungependa

01:28:29.911 --> 01:28:30.988
kuchangia hapa?
Tafadhali, nisaidie.

01:28:31.012 --> 01:28:32.223
Wewe ni
peke yako, rafiki.

01:28:32.247 --> 01:28:33.357
Bob, siachi kazi yangu

01:28:33.381 --> 01:28:34.715
kwa sababu plutonium
ni mionzi.

01:28:34.748 --> 01:28:36.284
Hatujui tu
inaweza kufanya nini

01:28:36.318 --> 01:28:38.053
kwa mwanamke
mfumo wa uzazi...

01:28:38.086 --> 01:28:39.997
Mfumo wako wa uzazi ni zaidi
wazi kuliko yangu, labda.

01:28:40.021 --> 01:28:42.891
Je, tunaweza tafadhali? The
kifaa implosion ni pa.

01:28:42.924 --> 01:28:44.326
Halo, huwezi kuharakisha kila kitu.

01:28:44.359 --> 01:28:45.903
- Oppie, tafadhali.
- Kweli, kuna kukimbilia

01:28:45.927 --> 01:28:47.728
na kuna kuendelea
nayo, kwa hivyo chagua moja.

01:28:47.761 --> 01:28:49.763
Subiri. Jina la Neddermeyer
kufanya kazi yake.

01:28:49.797 --> 01:28:50.731
Teller haisaidii.

01:28:50.764 --> 01:28:52.300
Husaidii.

01:28:52.334 --> 01:28:53.734
Nimekuwa nikiuliza
kwa mahesabu

01:28:53.767 --> 01:28:54.912
juu ya implosion
lenses kwa wiki.

01:28:54.936 --> 01:28:56.404
Waingereza wanaweza kufanya hivyo. Fuchs.

01:28:56.438 --> 01:28:57.738
Kabisa.

01:28:57.771 --> 01:28:59.141
Ni kazi yako, Teller.

01:28:59.174 --> 01:29:00.976
Ninajishughulisha na utafiti.

01:29:01.009 --> 01:29:03.677
Juu ya bomu ya hidrojeni
hata hatujengi.

01:29:11.785 --> 01:29:13.155
Sitamfanyia kazi mtu huyo.

01:29:14.923 --> 01:29:17.025
Mwache aende zake. Yeye ni prima donna.

01:29:17.058 --> 01:29:19.294
Nakubali. Yeye
wanapaswa kuondoka Los Alamos.

01:29:19.327 --> 01:29:20.829
Sawa.

01:29:20.862 --> 01:29:22.730
Kisty, unachukua nafasi ya Neddermeyer.

01:29:22.763 --> 01:29:24.166
Seth, ninaweka
wewe kwenye plutonium.

01:29:24.199 --> 01:29:27.302
Lilli, nenda ukafanye kazi
Kisty. Kwa sababu anakuhitaji.

01:29:27.335 --> 01:29:29.905
Fuchs, unachukua nafasi ya Teller.

01:29:29.938 --> 01:29:32.307
Ninakuweka pekee
kwenye kifaa cha implosion.

01:29:32.340 --> 01:29:36.111
Na hakuna mtu
kuondoka Los Alamos.

01:29:50.358 --> 01:29:52.327
- Hawataniacha niondoke.
- Hapana.

01:29:52.360 --> 01:29:53.962
Sitakuruhusu uondoke.

01:29:54.829 --> 01:29:57.933
Msahau Hans. Kusahau fission.

01:29:57.966 --> 01:30:01.102
Kaa hapa, tafiti
unachotaka.

01:30:01.136 --> 01:30:03.737
Fusion, hidrojeni
bomba, chochote.

01:30:03.771 --> 01:30:04.940
Tutakutana kujadili.

01:30:04.973 --> 01:30:06.441
Huna muda wa kukutana.

01:30:06.474 --> 01:30:08.043
Wewe ni mwanasiasa sasa, Robert.

01:30:08.076 --> 01:30:10.711
Umeacha fizikia nyuma
miaka mingi, mingi iliyopita.

01:30:11.546 --> 01:30:13.348
Mara moja kwa wiki.

01:30:13.381 --> 01:30:15.250
Saa moja. Wewe na mimi.

01:30:20.422 --> 01:30:22.991
Sasa ongeza kizuizi hiki cha kutisha.

01:30:26.928 --> 01:30:29.364
<i>Kwa hivyo Super
ilikuwa chini ya maendeleo</i>

01:30:29.397 --> 01:30:31.366
<i>kwenye saa yako huko Los Alamos?</i>

01:30:31.399 --> 01:30:32.901
Ndiyo.

01:30:32.934 --> 01:30:34.802
Na bado, baada ya vita,

01:30:34.836 --> 01:30:36.438
ulijaribu kukataa kuwa haiwezekani.

01:30:36.471 --> 01:30:37.973
Hapana, hapana, hapana. Mimi...

01:30:38.006 --> 01:30:39.841
Nilitaja kiufundi
matatizo nayo.

01:30:39.874 --> 01:30:41.519
Wewe... Hukujaribu kufanya hivyo
kuua kwenye mkutano wa AEC

01:30:41.543 --> 01:30:43.111
- baada ya mtihani wa bomu wa Kirusi?
- Hapana.

01:30:43.144 --> 01:30:45.247
Lakini hiyo ilikuwa
mapendekezo ya AEC,

01:30:45.280 --> 01:30:47.549
- haikuwa hivyo?
- Baada ya masaa ya majadiliano

01:30:47.582 --> 01:30:49.851
<i>kuhusu jibu bora.</i>

01:30:49.884 --> 01:30:54.990
Bomu la H ni mara 1,000
nguvu ya bomu la A.

01:30:56.157 --> 01:30:59.928
Lengo lake pekee lililokusudiwa
itakuwa miji mikubwa zaidi.

01:30:59.961 --> 01:31:02.063
Ni silaha ya mauaji ya halaiki.

01:31:02.097 --> 01:31:04.399
Izzy, chora miduara kadhaa
upande huu wa ramani

01:31:04.432 --> 01:31:06.067
wangetulenga wapi.

01:31:06.101 --> 01:31:08.136
- Kuanzia New York. D.C.
- Hiyo ni haki.

01:31:08.169 --> 01:31:10.939
Ni silaha ya mashambulizi
bila thamani ya ulinzi.

01:31:10.972 --> 01:31:12.507
- Kuzuia.
- "Kuzuia"?

01:31:12.540 --> 01:31:14.142
Je, tunahitaji kweli
kuzuia zaidi

01:31:14.175 --> 01:31:16.578
kuliko ya sasa yetu
arsenal ya mabomu ya atomiki?

01:31:16.611 --> 01:31:19.314
Y-Unazama kwa futi kumi
maji au-au 10,000,

01:31:19.347 --> 01:31:21.025
kuna tofauti gani?

01:31:21.049 --> 01:31:23.018
Tunaweza tayari kuzama
Urusi. Wanaijua.

01:31:23.051 --> 01:31:25.329
- Na sasa wanaweza kutuzamisha.
- Kwa hivyo tunazidi kuongezeka ...

01:31:36.231 --> 01:31:39.067
Kama nilivyosema, Teller's
miundo bado ni kama

01:31:39.100 --> 01:31:41.036
isiyowezekana kama wao
walikuwa wakati wa vita.

01:31:41.069 --> 01:31:44.039
Bomu la hidrojeni linaweza kutengenezwa
kufanya kazi, Oppie, unajua hilo.

01:31:44.072 --> 01:31:45.216
Siamini tunapaswa kujitoa

01:31:45.240 --> 01:31:47.142
rasilimali zetu zote
kwa nafasi hiyo.

01:31:47.175 --> 01:31:50.045
Basi ungekuwaje na Truman
kuwahakikishia watu wa Marekani?

01:31:50.078 --> 01:31:52.280
Kwa kikomo tu
kuenea kwa silaha za atomiki

01:31:52.314 --> 01:31:55.617
kupitia kimataifa
udhibiti wa nishati ya nyuklia.

01:31:55.650 --> 01:31:57.218
Unayomaanisha
serikali ya dunia?

01:31:57.252 --> 01:32:00.188
Umoja wa Mataifa kama
Roosevelt alikusudia.

01:32:00.221 --> 01:32:03.124
Naam, mimi ... niliuliza nini
Truman anapaswa kufanya, sawa?

01:32:03.158 --> 01:32:06.061
Dunia imebadilika, ndivyo
si ufashisti bali Ukomunisti

01:32:06.094 --> 01:32:07.562
ambayo sasa inatishia uhai wetu.

01:32:07.595 --> 01:32:11.232
Lewis, unaelewa,
ikiwa tutaunda bomu ya hidrojeni,

01:32:11.266 --> 01:32:14.135
Warusi hawatakuwa na
uchaguzi lakini kujenga wao wenyewe?

01:32:14.169 --> 01:32:15.937
Je, wanaweza kuwa wanafanya kazi
kwenye moja tayari?

01:32:15.970 --> 01:32:18.473
Kulingana na habari iliyokusanywa
kutoka kwa jasusi huko Los Alamos.

01:32:18.506 --> 01:32:19.974
Hakuna jasusi huko Los Alamos.

01:32:20.008 --> 01:32:21.085
- Mabwana.
- Hakuwepo?

01:32:21.109 --> 01:32:22.344
Tusikengeushwe.

01:32:22.377 --> 01:32:24.079
Ninasema tunatumia wakati huu

01:32:24.112 --> 01:32:25.523
kupata makubaliano
kutoka kwa Warusi

01:32:25.547 --> 01:32:28.616
kwa kujitolea kwamba tutafanya
si kujenga bomu ya hidrojeni.

01:32:28.650 --> 01:32:30.285
Kwa hivyo kufichua uwepo wake.

01:32:30.318 --> 01:32:32.320
Ambayo unaonekana kushawishika
tayari wanajua.

01:32:32.354 --> 01:32:33.955
Sawa.

01:32:33.988 --> 01:32:36.091
Katika hatua hii, ningependa
wajumbe wa kamati

01:32:36.124 --> 01:32:40.061
kukutana kwa faragha
kukamilisha mapendekezo yetu.

01:32:41.196 --> 01:32:43.198
Sina hakika na wewe
wanataka kwenda chini ya barabara hii.

01:32:43.231 --> 01:32:45.500
Lewis, kwa heshima, sisi
ni kamati ya ushauri,

01:32:45.533 --> 01:32:47.302
tutawapa ushauri wetu.

01:32:47.335 --> 01:32:48.436
Usiku mwema.

01:32:52.640 --> 01:32:56.911
Dk Oppenheimer?
Habari. William Borden.

01:32:56.945 --> 01:32:58.279
Kamati ya Pamoja
juu ya Nishati ya Atomiki?

01:32:58.313 --> 01:32:59.514
Oh, ndiyo, ndiyo.

01:32:59.547 --> 01:33:01.182
Wakati wa vita, nilikuwa rubani.

01:33:02.317 --> 01:33:05.053
Usiku mmoja, kuruka
nyuma kutoka kwa uvamizi,

01:33:05.086 --> 01:33:07.989
Niliona ajabu
kuonekana kama kimondo.

01:33:09.190 --> 01:33:11.960
<i>Roketi ya V-2 ilielekea Uingereza.</i>

01:33:11.993 --> 01:33:13.995
Siwezi kusaidia lakini
fikiria itakuwaje

01:33:14.028 --> 01:33:17.932
kwa roketi kama hiyo ya adui
kubeba kichwa cha atomiki.

01:33:26.708 --> 01:33:28.052
Naam, hebu tuhakikishe
sisi sio wale

01:33:28.076 --> 01:33:29.377
ili kufanya hilo liwezekane.

01:33:36.084 --> 01:33:38.987
Oppie, sidhani kama unataka
kwenda dhidi ya Strauss.

01:33:39.020 --> 01:33:41.089
Ikiwa sisi sote tunazungumza,
wananisikiliza.

01:33:41.122 --> 01:33:43.191
Unapozungumza,
wanamsikia nabii.

01:33:43.224 --> 01:33:45.193
Wakati Strauss anazungumza,
wanasikia wenyewe.

01:33:45.226 --> 01:33:47.028
Watamsikiliza nabii.

01:33:47.061 --> 01:33:50.331
Nabii hawezi kuwa
vibaya. Si mara moja.

01:33:50.365 --> 01:33:52.133
<i>Haikufanya hivyo
unamtuhumu Oppenheimer</i>

01:33:52.167 --> 01:33:54.068
<i>ya kuhujumu
maendeleo ya Super?</i>

01:33:54.102 --> 01:33:55.703
Sikuwahi kuwa mmoja wa hao

01:33:55.737 --> 01:33:59.007
kuzunguka masharti
kama "hujuma."

01:33:59.040 --> 01:34:01.009
<i>Lakini
Mheshimiwa Borden alikuwa?</i>

01:34:01.042 --> 01:34:02.310
Kama ninavyoelewa, ikiwezekana.

01:34:02.343 --> 01:34:04.446
Bwana Borden alikuwaje
kuweza kuweka pamoja

01:34:04.479 --> 01:34:05.747
hati ya mashtaka ya kina kama hii?

01:34:05.780 --> 01:34:07.315
<i>Hakuwa tena a
mfanyakazi wa serikali,</i>

01:34:07.348 --> 01:34:09.984
bado anaonekana kuwa nayo
alikuwa na ufikiaji usio na kikomo

01:34:10.018 --> 01:34:11.519
kwa faili ya Dr. Oppenheimer.

01:34:11.553 --> 01:34:14.456
<i>Huenda Bw. Nichols wametoa
yeye kufikia faili?</i>

01:34:14.489 --> 01:34:16.391
Au mtu mwingine, katika AEC?

01:34:16.424 --> 01:34:19.260
Hiyo ni mbaya sana
tuhuma, Seneta.

01:34:19.294 --> 01:34:21.763
Je, ni nia yako
kupendekeza kwamba Dk Oppenheimer

01:34:21.796 --> 01:34:23.731
sio mwaminifu kwa
Marekani?

01:34:23.765 --> 01:34:26.301
Siku zote nilidhani,
na bado kudhani,

01:34:26.334 --> 01:34:29.037
kwamba yeye ni mwaminifu kwake
Marekani.

01:34:29.070 --> 01:34:30.514
Ninaamini hivi. Na
nitaamini

01:34:30.538 --> 01:34:33.341
mpaka naona conclusive sana
ushahidi kwa kinyume.

01:34:33.374 --> 01:34:35.143
<i>Je wewe au
hamuamini</i>

01:34:35.176 --> 01:34:37.545
<i>kwamba Dk Oppenheimer
ni hatari kwa usalama?</i>

01:34:45.753 --> 01:34:47.388
Na kama naweza,

01:34:47.422 --> 01:34:50.225
wakati Hitler alipiga yake
akili nje katika chumba cha kulala,

01:34:50.258 --> 01:34:51.803
ni maoni yangu mnyenyekevu
kwamba hakuna haja

01:34:51.827 --> 01:34:53.294
kwa hilo bomu
kuonekana popote

01:34:53.328 --> 01:34:55.096
isipokuwa kwa tovuti hiyo ya majaribio.

01:34:55.129 --> 01:34:57.131
Lakini sisi angalau
inabidi kuchukua muda

01:34:57.165 --> 01:34:59.167
kufikiria kama njia

01:34:59.200 --> 01:35:01.469
kuhalalisha miisho yoyote
muda mrefu zaidi, kwa sababu ...

01:35:03.805 --> 01:35:06.374
Ujerumani inakaribia kujisalimisha.

01:35:08.276 --> 01:35:11.613
Sio adui tena
ambao ni tishio kubwa zaidi

01:35:11.646 --> 01:35:13.448
kwa wanadamu, ni kazi yetu.

01:35:15.851 --> 01:35:18.586
Hitler amekufa, ni kweli.

01:35:20.288 --> 01:35:21.824
Lakini Wajapani wanapigana.

01:35:21.857 --> 01:35:23.525
Kushindwa kwao kunaonekana kuwa na uhakika.

01:35:23.558 --> 01:35:26.561
Si kama wewe ni G.I.
kujiandaa kuvamia.

01:35:27.863 --> 01:35:29.163
Tunaweza kumaliza vita hivi.

01:35:29.197 --> 01:35:30.598
Lakini
tunahalalisha vipi

01:35:30.632 --> 01:35:32.200
kutumia silaha hii
juu ya wanadamu?

01:35:35.236 --> 01:35:38.640
Sisi ni wananadharia, ndiyo?

01:35:38.673 --> 01:35:40.275
Ndiyo. Ndiyo.

01:35:40.308 --> 01:35:44.345
Tunafikiria siku zijazo na
mawazo yetu yanatutisha.

01:35:45.413 --> 01:35:47.549
Lakini hawataiogopa
mpaka waelewe,

01:35:47.582 --> 01:35:50.485
na hawataelewa
mpaka wameitumia.

01:35:50.518 --> 01:35:51.686
Wakati ulimwengu unajifunza

01:35:51.719 --> 01:35:54.222
siri ya kutisha
wa Los Alamos,

01:35:54.255 --> 01:35:57.692
kazi yetu hapa itahakikisha a
amani wanadamu hawajawahi kuona.

01:35:57.725 --> 01:36:01.095
Amani kulingana na aina
ya ushirikiano wa kimataifa

01:36:01.129 --> 01:36:03.164
ambayo Roosevelt alifikiria kila wakati.

01:36:08.269 --> 01:36:09.504
<i>Maendeleo?</i>

01:36:09.537 --> 01:36:12.307
Miaka miwili na a
thamani ya dola bilioni?

01:36:12.340 --> 01:36:14.108
Kweli, ni ngumu kuweka bei juu yake.

01:36:14.142 --> 01:36:15.710
Si kweli, tu
ongeza bili.

01:36:15.743 --> 01:36:17.445
"Usafirishaji wa bure vijijini."

01:36:17.478 --> 01:36:20.248
Watoto themanini walijifungua
mwaka wa kwanza.

01:36:20.281 --> 01:36:22.617
Mwaka huu, tumekuwa
alikuwa na kumi kwa mwezi.

01:36:22.650 --> 01:36:25.386
Udhibiti wa uzazi umetoka kidogo
wa mamlaka yangu, Jenerali.

01:36:26.254 --> 01:36:28.590
- Wazi.
- Mkuu.

01:36:33.561 --> 01:36:34.897
Kichwa chini, kila mtu.

01:36:34.930 --> 01:36:37.098
Fuchs, kichwa chini.

01:36:39.601 --> 01:36:40.768
Hmm?

01:36:43.638 --> 01:36:45.373
Huyo ndiye.

01:36:45.406 --> 01:36:48.309
Mabomu mawili yanayowezekana. Nahitaji tarehe.

01:36:50.612 --> 01:36:52.447
Septemba.

01:36:52.480 --> 01:36:53.481
Julai.

01:36:53.514 --> 01:36:55.450
Hiyo ndiyo tamu
doa, waungwana.

01:36:55.483 --> 01:36:57.652
Agosti.

01:36:57.685 --> 01:36:59.420
Julai.

01:36:59.454 --> 01:37:01.255
Mtihani mnamo Julai.

01:37:01.289 --> 01:37:02.925
Lakini nahitaji ndugu yangu.

01:37:07.295 --> 01:37:09.239
Frank anajua jangwa,
ameacha siasa,

01:37:09.263 --> 01:37:11.699
amekuwa akifanya kazi naye
Lawrence kwa miaka miwili sasa.

01:37:18.673 --> 01:37:20.508
Tunaita mtihani gani?

01:37:21.609 --> 01:37:25.380
"Piga moyo wangu,
mungu wa watu watatu."

01:37:25.413 --> 01:37:26.514
Je!

01:37:27.883 --> 01:37:29.283
Utatu.

01:37:36.959 --> 01:37:38.326
Ulisisitiza

01:37:38.359 --> 01:37:39.670
juu ya kuleta
ndugu yako Frank,

01:37:39.694 --> 01:37:41.305
- Mkomunisti anayejulikana.
- Mkomunisti wa zamani.

01:37:41.329 --> 01:37:43.765
Umeleta inayojulikana
Mkomunisti wa zamani

01:37:43.798 --> 01:37:47.669
kwenye siri zaidi ya Amerika
na mradi muhimu wa ulinzi.

01:37:47.702 --> 01:37:50.805
Nilijua kaka yangu anaweza
kuaminiwa. Kabisa.

01:37:50.839 --> 01:37:52.808
Na ulihisi yako
hukumu ilikuwa nzuri

01:37:52.841 --> 01:37:54.676
juu ya nani kwenye timu
inaweza kuaminiwa?

01:37:55.677 --> 01:37:56.812
Fuchs, kichwa chini.

01:37:56.845 --> 01:37:58.579
Sawa, kila mtu yuko tayari?

01:37:59.948 --> 01:38:01.884
Hmm?

01:38:01.917 --> 01:38:03.685
Oh.

01:38:06.822 --> 01:38:07.956
Oh.

01:38:07.990 --> 01:38:09.724
Naam, natumaini wewe
kujifunza kitu.

01:38:09.757 --> 01:38:11.669
Ndio, tumejifunza tutaenda
haja ya kuwa mbali zaidi.

01:38:11.693 --> 01:38:13.261
Naam, fahamu. Haraka.

01:38:13.294 --> 01:38:14.963
Tunaondoka kuelekea Washington
asubuhi.

01:38:14.997 --> 01:38:17.198
Tutawapa tarehe.

01:38:31.345 --> 01:38:33.015
Uko mbali sana
kutoka Chicago, Leo.

01:38:33.048 --> 01:38:34.549
Ikiwa hatuchukui hatua sasa,

01:38:34.582 --> 01:38:36.293
watatumia
jambo hili dhidi ya Japan.

01:38:36.317 --> 01:38:38.286
Tulipanga mkutano na Truman,

01:38:38.319 --> 01:38:39.587
lakini mtu alimuua.

01:38:39.620 --> 01:38:41.489
Unakutana na
Katibu wa Vita.

01:38:41.522 --> 01:38:43.691
Kwa sababu tu tunaijenga,

01:38:43.725 --> 01:38:45.727
haimaanishi tufike
kuamua jinsi inavyotumika.

01:38:45.760 --> 01:38:48.529
Historia itatuhukumu, Robert.

01:38:48.563 --> 01:38:51.867
Katika Chicago, sisi kuweka
pamoja maombi.

01:38:51.900 --> 01:38:53.836
Mimi si... mimi si
kuingia katika hilo.

01:38:58.907 --> 01:39:00.843
Niambie tu wasiwasi wako,
nami nitazisambaza.

01:39:00.876 --> 01:39:01.977
Wasiwasi wangu?

01:39:02.010 --> 01:39:03.979
Ujerumani imeshindwa.

01:39:04.012 --> 01:39:05.780
Japan haiendi
kushikilia peke yako.

01:39:05.814 --> 01:39:07.715
Ungewezaje kujua hilo?
Umetuingiza kwenye hili.

01:39:07.749 --> 01:39:09.526
Wewe na Einstein pamoja
barua yako kwa Roosevelt

01:39:09.550 --> 01:39:12.353
- kusema tunaweza kujenga bomu.
- dhidi ya Ujerumani.

01:39:12.386 --> 01:39:15.323
Sivyo hivyo silaha
utengenezaji kazi, Szilard.

01:39:15.356 --> 01:39:16.500
Oppie,
inabidi usaidie.

01:39:16.524 --> 01:39:17.826
ya Fermi
katika mkutano huo.

01:39:17.860 --> 01:39:19.436
- Lawrence yuko kwenye mkutano.
- Wao si wewe.

01:39:19.460 --> 01:39:21.629
Wewe ndiye mkuu
muuzaji wa sayansi.

01:39:21.662 --> 01:39:24.265
Unaweza kushawishi
mtu yeyote wa chochote.

01:39:24.967 --> 01:39:26.367
Hata wewe mwenyewe.

01:39:26.969 --> 01:39:28.369
'Nisamehe.

01:39:29.403 --> 01:39:32.673
Dhoruba ya moto huko Tokyo
kuua watu 100,000.

01:39:32.707 --> 01:39:34.509
Wengi wao wakiwa raia.

01:39:34.542 --> 01:39:37.079
Nina wasiwasi kuhusu Amerika
ambapo tunafanya mambo haya

01:39:37.112 --> 01:39:38.847
na hakuna mtu anayepinga.

01:39:38.881 --> 01:39:41.917
Pearl Harbor na miaka mitatu ya
migogoro ya kikatili katika Pasifiki

01:39:41.950 --> 01:39:44.485
alitununua latitudo nyingi
na umma wa Marekani.

01:39:44.519 --> 01:39:46.554
Inatosha
kufyatua bomu la atomiki?

01:39:46.587 --> 01:39:48.456
Lo, bomu la A
inaweza kusababisha

01:39:48.489 --> 01:39:50.391
uharibifu mwingi kama
milipuko ya Tokyo.

01:39:50.424 --> 01:39:51.793
Je, tunakadiria nini?

01:39:51.827 --> 01:39:54.662
Katika jiji la ukubwa wa kati, uh,

01:39:54.695 --> 01:39:56.098
20 au 30,000 wamekufa.

01:39:56.131 --> 01:39:57.933
Ndio, lakini, uh,

01:39:57.966 --> 01:40:01.003
usiidharau
athari za kisaikolojia za ...

01:40:01.036 --> 01:40:02.436
ya mlipuko wa atomiki.

01:40:02.470 --> 01:40:06.707
Nguzo ya moto
Urefu wa futi 10,000.

01:40:06.741 --> 01:40:10.078
Madhara ya nutroni mauti kwa
maili moja kwa pande zote,

01:40:10.112 --> 01:40:13.015
kutoka kwa kifaa kimoja.

01:40:13.048 --> 01:40:15.383
Imeshuka kutoka kwa a
sikugundua B-29,

01:40:15.416 --> 01:40:17.685
bomu la atomiki litakuwa

01:40:17.718 --> 01:40:20.555
ufunuo wa kutisha
wa nguvu za kimungu.

01:40:20.588 --> 01:40:23.859
Kama hiyo ni kweli, basi
itakuwa ya uhakika.

01:40:23.892 --> 01:40:25.961
Vita vya Pili vya Ulimwengu vingeisha.

01:40:25.994 --> 01:40:27.695
Vijana wetu wangekuja nyumbani.

01:40:27.728 --> 01:40:28.864
Malengo ya kijeshi?

01:40:29.998 --> 01:40:32.667
Lo, hakuna kubwa ya kutosha.

01:40:32.700 --> 01:40:38.472
Labda mmea muhimu wa vita
na wafanyikazi waliowekwa karibu.

01:40:38.506 --> 01:40:40.843
Na tunaweza kutoa onyo
kupunguza vifo vya raia.

01:40:40.876 --> 01:40:43.045
Wangetuma kila kitu
wana juu yetu,

01:40:43.078 --> 01:40:44.679
na ningekuwa kwenye ndege hiyo.

01:40:44.712 --> 01:40:47.916
Lakini ikiwa tutatangaza
na inashindwa kuondoka,

01:40:47.950 --> 01:40:50.651
tungepoteza nafasi yoyote
ya kujisalimisha kwa Kijapani.

01:40:50.685 --> 01:40:53.788
Je, hakuna njia
kuonyesha bomu kwa Japan

01:40:53.822 --> 01:40:55.523
kuchochea kujisalimisha?

01:40:55.556 --> 01:40:58.626
Tunakusudia kuionyesha
kwa maneno yasiyo na utata zaidi.

01:40:58.659 --> 01:40:59.360
Mara mbili.

01:40:59.393 --> 01:41:01.462
Mara moja kuonyesha nguvu ya silaha

01:41:01.495 --> 01:41:03.999
na ya pili kuonyesha hivyo
tunaweza kuendelea kufanya hivi

01:41:04.032 --> 01:41:05.533
mpaka wajisalimishe.

01:41:05.566 --> 01:41:08.937
Tunayo orodha ya 12
miji ya kuchagua...

01:41:08.971 --> 01:41:10.873
Samahani, 11.

01:41:10.906 --> 01:41:12.607
Nimeondoa Kyoto kwenye orodha

01:41:12.640 --> 01:41:16.444
kwa sababu ya umuhimu wake wa kitamaduni
kwa watu wa Japan.

01:41:16.477 --> 01:41:19.114
Pia, mke wangu na mimi
asali huko.

01:41:19.147 --> 01:41:20.648
Ni jiji la kifahari.

01:41:24.219 --> 01:41:25.921
Acha nifanye jambo hili rahisi
kwa ajili yenu, mabwana.

01:41:25.954 --> 01:41:28.456
Kulingana na akili yangu,
ambayo siwezi kushiriki nawe,

01:41:28.489 --> 01:41:30.926
watu wa Japani
hatajisalimisha

01:41:30.959 --> 01:41:32.727
kwa hali yoyote

01:41:32.760 --> 01:41:36.164
fupi ya mafanikio na jumla
uvamizi wa visiwa vya nyumbani.

01:41:36.198 --> 01:41:39.167
Watu wengi watapoteza maisha,
Marekani na Japan.

01:41:39.201 --> 01:41:41.435
Matumizi ya atomiki
bomu kwenye miji ya Japan

01:41:41.469 --> 01:41:43.437
itaokoa maisha.

01:41:43.471 --> 01:41:45.773
Ikiwa tunahifadhi faida ya maadili.

01:41:45.807 --> 01:41:47.943
- Jinsi gani?
- Kweli, ikiwa tunatumia silaha hii

01:41:47.976 --> 01:41:50.913
bila kuwajulisha washirika wetu,
wataona ni tishio.

01:41:50.946 --> 01:41:52.114
Na tutakuwa katika mbio za silaha.

01:41:52.147 --> 01:41:54.216
Jinsi gani tunaweza kuwa wazi
na Soviets?

01:41:54.249 --> 01:41:55.817
Usiri hautafanya
kuacha Soviets

01:41:55.851 --> 01:41:58.220
kutoka kuwa sehemu
ya ulimwengu wa atomiki.

01:41:58.253 --> 01:42:00.554
Tumeambiwa wao
hawana uranium.

01:42:00.588 --> 01:42:01.789
Umepewa taarifa zisizo sahihi.

01:42:01.823 --> 01:42:03.658
Bomu la Urusi ni
suala la muda.

01:42:03.691 --> 01:42:07.095
Mpango unahitaji kuendelea
kwa kasi kamili baada ya vita.

01:42:07.129 --> 01:42:09.730
Ah, Katibu
Stimson, kama naweza...

01:42:09.764 --> 01:42:13.768
Sio wanasayansi wote kwenye
mradi wako katika makubaliano.

01:42:13.801 --> 01:42:16.671
Kwa kweli, hii inaweza kuwa wakati
kuzingatia maoni mengine.

01:42:16.704 --> 01:42:18.615
- Ikiwa unazungumza na mwanasayansi katika ...
- Mradi wa Manhattan

01:42:18.639 --> 01:42:20.008
imekuwa ikisumbuliwa tangu mwanzo

01:42:20.042 --> 01:42:23.845
na wanasayansi fulani
ya busara yenye shaka

01:42:23.879 --> 01:42:24.947
na uaminifu usio na uhakika.

01:42:24.980 --> 01:42:27.215
Mmoja wao alijaribu tu
kukutana na rais.

01:42:27.249 --> 01:42:29.084
Sasa tunahitaji wanaume hawa,

01:42:29.117 --> 01:42:30.651
lakini mara tu inapotumika,

01:42:30.685 --> 01:42:32.955
tunapaswa kukata aina yoyote kama hiyo
wanasayansi kutoka kwa mpango huo.

01:42:32.988 --> 01:42:34.555
Je, hukubali, Daktari?

01:42:35.690 --> 01:42:37.525
Ikiwa Kirusi
bomu haliepukiki,

01:42:37.558 --> 01:42:40.829
labda tuwaalike
wanasayansi wa juu kwa Utatu.

01:42:40.862 --> 01:42:43.165
Rais Truman
hana nia

01:42:43.198 --> 01:42:44.765
ya kuongeza matarajio

01:42:44.799 --> 01:42:47.601
kwamba Stalin ajumuishwe
katika mradi wa atomiki.

01:42:47.635 --> 01:42:49.004
Kumjulisha
mafanikio yetu

01:42:49.037 --> 01:42:50.647
na kuiwasilisha kama
njia ya kushinda vita

01:42:50.671 --> 01:42:53.574
si lazima kufanya
ahadi zisizotekelezeka.

01:42:53.607 --> 01:42:55.153
Lakini amani ya Potsdam
mkutano wa Julai

01:42:55.177 --> 01:42:57.079
atakuwa Rais
Nafasi ya mwisho ya Truman

01:42:57.112 --> 01:42:59.247
kufanya mazungumzo hayo.

01:42:59.281 --> 01:43:01.183
Unaweza kutupa a
kufanya kazi na bomu wakati huo?

01:43:02.150 --> 01:43:05.887
Kabisa. Tutajaribu
moto kabla ya mkutano huo.

01:43:10.624 --> 01:43:13.161
<i>Sufuri ya chini
machapisho ya uchunguzi</i>

01:43:13.195 --> 01:43:14.662
<i>kwa yadi 10,000</i>

01:43:14.695 --> 01:43:16.865
kaskazini, kusini na magharibi.

01:43:16.898 --> 01:43:20.202
- Tunaanzia wapi?
- Uh, kusini 10,000.

01:43:20.235 --> 01:43:23.571
Na kambi ya msingi ni kumi
maili kusini, hapa.

01:43:23.604 --> 01:43:26.540
Na kuna zaidi
chapisho la uchunguzi

01:43:26.574 --> 01:43:28.743
kwenye kilima hicho umbali wa maili 20.

01:43:28.776 --> 01:43:31.746
Ni nini hicho, Frank? Anzisha
mistari tayari imeingia.

01:43:31.779 --> 01:43:35.283
Jeshi la anga liliomba a
mstari wa taa kwa B-29 yao.

01:43:35.317 --> 01:43:37.752
B-29 nini? Yetu
bomu kwenye mnara.

01:43:37.785 --> 01:43:39.154
Wanataka
kutumia mtihani

01:43:39.187 --> 01:43:41.023
ili kuthibitisha salama
umbali wa uendeshaji.

01:43:41.056 --> 01:43:42.290
Hiyo ni hatari.

01:43:42.324 --> 01:43:43.959
Sio hatari kama
kuangusha moja juu ya Japan

01:43:43.992 --> 01:43:45.769
na kutumaini kwamba tulikuwa
sawa kuhusu eneo la mlipuko.

01:43:45.793 --> 01:43:47.905
Usituache tupunguze kasi,
tunapiga risasi tarehe 15.

01:43:47.929 --> 01:43:51.166
- Ya 15? Hiyo sio...
- Tarehe 15.

01:43:51.199 --> 01:43:53.534
Ya 15.

01:43:54.635 --> 01:43:56.580
Kwa hivyo nitakuwa hapa
katika kituo cha uchunguzi wa kusini

01:43:56.604 --> 01:43:58.807
<i>pamoja na Frank na Kistiakowsky.</i>

01:43:58.840 --> 01:44:01.343
Mtakuwa wote
alitumwa kwa Base Camp,

01:44:01.376 --> 01:44:04.578
Uchunguzi wa Magharibi
au Uchunguzi wa Mbali.

01:44:14.222 --> 01:44:16.124
Lo! Makini
kwa kisu.

01:44:16.158 --> 01:44:18.592
Huko, kwa uangalifu.

01:44:19.693 --> 01:44:21.229
Je, hizo ni umbali salama?

01:44:21.263 --> 01:44:23.764
Wao ni msingi
mahesabu yako.

01:44:23.798 --> 01:44:26.700
Ni wakati wa kusimama nyuma yako
sayansi, Hans. Kihalisi.

01:44:50.125 --> 01:44:51.592
Ndiyo.

01:44:56.264 --> 01:44:58.100
Vipi kuhusu wingu la mionzi?

01:44:58.133 --> 01:44:59.367
Bila upepo mkali,

01:44:59.401 --> 01:45:00.978
inapaswa kukaa ndani
maili mbili hadi tatu.

01:45:01.002 --> 01:45:03.405
Hatua za uokoaji
zipo mahali.

01:45:03.438 --> 01:45:05.240
Lakini tunahitaji nzuri
hali ya hewa kwa kuonekana,

01:45:05.273 --> 01:45:06.740
kwa hivyo lazima iwe sawa.

01:45:07.843 --> 01:45:09.111
Kila mtu nje.

01:45:19.287 --> 01:45:20.431
Tunaenda usiku wa tarehe 15.

01:45:20.455 --> 01:45:22.390
Ni tarehe ya mwisho ngumu,

01:45:22.424 --> 01:45:25.726
hivyo kama kuna mtu ana
chochote, sema sasa.

01:45:26.428 --> 01:45:27.761
Sawa, acha, acha.

01:45:27.795 --> 01:45:29.663
Kila mtu, magodoro.

01:45:29.697 --> 01:45:31.765
Weka godoro chini.

01:45:48.749 --> 01:45:51.652
Inaweza kutumia fainali
mtihani wa implosion.

01:45:52.354 --> 01:45:54.322
Haikuweza kuumiza.

01:45:54.356 --> 01:45:55.857
Fanya hivyo.

01:45:56.825 --> 01:45:59.127
Je, kuna kitu kingine chochote
hiyo inaweza kutuzuia?

01:46:33.228 --> 01:46:36.131
Inatokea, sivyo?

01:46:37.232 --> 01:46:39.000
Nitatuma ujumbe.

01:46:39.868 --> 01:46:42.504
Ikiwa imepita njia yetu,

01:46:42.537 --> 01:46:44.105
chukua shuka.

01:46:48.143 --> 01:46:49.177
Robert?

01:46:51.846 --> 01:46:53.281
Vunja mguu.

01:47:59.848 --> 01:48:02.984
Oppie imechukuliwa sana
kilotoni tatu za kawaida.

01:48:03.018 --> 01:48:05.387
- Teller yuko na 45.
- 20.

01:48:05.420 --> 01:48:07.856
Tani elfu ishirini za TNT,

01:48:07.889 --> 01:48:09.291
na hufanya mtu yeyote
wanataka hatua ya upande

01:48:09.324 --> 01:48:12.060
juu ya kuwasha kwa anga?

01:48:13.028 --> 01:48:15.964
Je, unasema
itabidi tuchelewe?

01:48:15.997 --> 01:48:17.174
Nasema itakuwa busara.

01:48:17.198 --> 01:48:18.442
Hali ya hewa hii, ina
ilifikia tovuti?

01:48:24.272 --> 01:48:26.250
Bethe anapiga simu kukuambia
mtihani wa implosion umeshindwa.

01:48:26.274 --> 01:48:27.909
Habari, Hans.

01:48:27.942 --> 01:48:29.344
Ndiyo, yuko hapa.

01:48:30.178 --> 01:48:31.513
Ndiyo.

01:48:34.082 --> 01:48:35.283
- Je!
- Hapana.

01:48:35.317 --> 01:48:37.218
- Hapana?
- Hapana.

01:48:38.053 --> 01:48:39.621
Kwa hiyo tunakaribia kumfukuza dud?

01:48:39.654 --> 01:48:41.122
- Hapana.
- Eleza.

01:48:41.156 --> 01:48:43.925
Naam, siwezi. I
tu…Ni—najua tu.

01:48:43.958 --> 01:48:45.627
Najua implosion
lenses zitafanya kazi.

01:48:45.660 --> 01:48:47.062
Tukifukuza hizi detonators

01:48:47.095 --> 01:48:48.339
na hawana
kuchochea majibu,

01:48:48.363 --> 01:48:50.031
Plutonium yenye thamani ya miaka miwili

01:48:50.065 --> 01:48:51.475
watatawanyika
kote White Sands.

01:48:51.499 --> 01:48:55.403
Mwezi wa mshahara wangu dhidi ya
pesa kumi inasema inawaka.

01:48:55.437 --> 01:48:57.439
Yesu.

01:49:02.510 --> 01:49:05.647
Upepo unapiga
hadi sifuri, sio mvua.

01:49:05.680 --> 01:49:07.115
Umeme unazunguka.

01:49:07.148 --> 01:49:08.592
Unafikiri inaweza kuwa
muda wa kuwaambia wanaume wako

01:49:08.616 --> 01:49:11.519
kupata mbali na chuma
mnara na bomu la atomiki?

01:49:14.656 --> 01:49:16.624
Hebu tufike kwenye South Observation.

01:49:16.658 --> 01:49:18.126
Wavute nje.

01:49:18.159 --> 01:49:19.570
Tunaweza kufanya yetu
dhamira hapo.

01:49:24.966 --> 01:49:26.968
Timu haijafanya hivyo
alilala kwa siku mbili.

01:49:27.001 --> 01:49:29.003
Ikiwa tutasimama chini,
weka bomu salama,

01:49:29.037 --> 01:49:30.372
hatutarudi hapa kwa wiki.

01:49:30.405 --> 01:49:32.073
Kisha tutakosa Potsdam.

01:49:32.107 --> 01:49:34.008
Lazima nipate neno
hadi Truman saa 7:00.

01:49:34.042 --> 01:49:35.276
Dirisha letu limefungwa.

01:49:35.310 --> 01:49:36.378
Hii inafanya nini?

01:49:36.411 --> 01:49:37.912
Mvua, kuvuma, umeme.

01:49:37.946 --> 01:49:39.981
- Kwa muda gani, jamani?
- Inashikilia nguvu.

01:49:40.014 --> 01:49:41.316
Itapambazuka kabla ya mapambazuko.

01:49:41.349 --> 01:49:43.027
- Ungewezaje kujua hilo?
- Najua jangwa hili.

01:49:43.051 --> 01:49:44.152
Dhoruba hupungua usiku mmoja.

01:49:44.185 --> 01:49:45.987
Kabla ya mapambazuko,
dhoruba inapasuka.

01:49:46.020 --> 01:49:48.223
Anaweza kuwa sahihi, lakini
ratiba kuchelewa iwezekanavyo.

01:49:48.256 --> 01:49:49.991
5:30!

01:49:50.024 --> 01:49:51.059
Saini utabiri wako.

01:49:51.092 --> 01:49:52.169
Ukikosea, nitakunyonga.

01:49:52.193 --> 01:49:53.995
Frank, waambie wote, 5:30.

01:49:54.028 --> 01:49:56.164
- 5:30, 5:30.
- 5:30.

01:49:58.366 --> 01:50:03.304
Miaka mitatu, 4,000
watu, dola bilioni 2.

01:50:03.338 --> 01:50:05.707
Naam, ikiwa haifanyi hivyo
ondoka...

01:50:05.740 --> 01:50:07.342
sote tumemaliza.

01:50:10.111 --> 01:50:12.080
Ninaweka dau la kilotoni tatu.

01:50:13.047 --> 01:50:14.492
Chochote kidogo, wao
sitapata ni nini.

01:50:14.516 --> 01:50:19.087
Fermi alimaanisha nini
"kuwasha kwa anga"?

01:50:19.120 --> 01:50:20.598
Naam, tulikuwa na muda
ambapo ilionekana

01:50:20.622 --> 01:50:24.459
mmenyuko wa mnyororo kutoka kwa
kifaa cha atomiki kinaweza kamwe kusimama.

01:50:25.693 --> 01:50:27.729
Kuweka moto kwenye anga.

01:50:27.762 --> 01:50:29.731
Mbona Fermi bado
kuchukua dau za upande juu yake?

01:50:29.764 --> 01:50:32.934
Iite ucheshi wa mti.

01:50:35.270 --> 01:50:38.072
Subiri, tunasema
kuna nafasi

01:50:38.106 --> 01:50:39.974
kwamba tunapobonyeza kitufe hicho,

01:50:40.008 --> 01:50:41.342
tunaharibu dunia?

01:50:41.376 --> 01:50:43.545
Hakuna chochote katika utafiti wetu
zaidi ya miaka mitatu

01:50:43.578 --> 01:50:45.213
inaunga mkono hitimisho hilo.

01:50:45.246 --> 01:50:48.216
Isipokuwa wengi zaidi
uwezekano wa mbali.

01:50:48.249 --> 01:50:49.584
Umbali gani?

01:50:49.617 --> 01:50:51.219
Uwezekano ni karibu sifuri.

01:50:52.554 --> 01:50:53.955
Je, unakaribia sufuri?

01:50:54.722 --> 01:50:57.292
Unataka nini
kutoka kwa nadharia pekee?

01:50:58.793 --> 01:51:01.162
Zero itakuwa nzuri.

01:51:04.466 --> 01:51:06.100
Katika hasa

01:51:06.134 --> 01:51:09.437
saa moja, dakika 58,

01:51:09.471 --> 01:51:11.005
tutajua.

01:51:17.045 --> 01:51:18.246
Ni kuruhusu juu.

01:51:31.125 --> 01:51:33.495
Sifuri ya kushoto ya chama cha silaha,
wanaelekea huku.

01:51:33.528 --> 01:51:34.496
Kutupa swichi.

01:51:34.529 --> 01:51:35.630
Geuza magari.

01:51:35.663 --> 01:51:38.132
Tayari kwa uokoaji wa dharura.

01:51:55.818 --> 01:51:57.058
Kioo cha Welder.

01:51:57.085 --> 01:51:58.653
Kila mtu achukue nafasi zako.

01:51:58.686 --> 01:52:01.189
Kila mtu achukue glasi ya welder.

01:52:02.690 --> 01:52:04.559
Kila mtu achukue glasi ya welder.

01:52:55.777 --> 01:52:57.178
Dakika ishirini.

01:53:00.682 --> 01:53:02.517
Dakika ishirini.

01:53:13.695 --> 01:53:15.229
Hiyo ni 20.

01:53:18.232 --> 01:53:19.701
Kwa mguu, tafadhali.

01:53:21.235 --> 01:53:23.738
- Feynman.
- Hapana.

01:53:23.771 --> 01:53:25.740
Kioo. Inasimamisha U.V.

01:53:25.773 --> 01:53:27.575
Na nini kinazuia glasi?

01:53:28.576 --> 01:53:31.546
Nitaenda msingi
kambi. Bora ya bahati.

01:53:32.680 --> 01:53:34.215
Robert.

01:53:34.817 --> 01:53:36.651
Jaribu kulipua ulimwengu.

01:53:48.529 --> 01:53:49.631
Tazama sindano hiyo.

01:53:49.664 --> 01:53:51.232
Ikiwa vimumunyisho havitoi

01:53:51.265 --> 01:53:53.201
au kushuka kwa voltage
chini ya volt moja,

01:53:53.234 --> 01:53:55.236
unabonyeza kitufe hicho, unaavya mimba.

01:53:55.269 --> 01:53:57.572
- Inaeleweka?
- Kueleweka.

01:54:04.980 --> 01:54:07.515
Mbili
dakika kwa mlipuko.

01:54:07.548 --> 01:54:09.517
Kila mtu chini.

01:54:09.550 --> 01:54:10.518
Usigeuke

01:54:10.551 --> 01:54:13.621
mpaka uone mwanga
yalijitokeza kwenye vilima.

01:54:13.655 --> 01:54:14.789
Kisha angalia mlipuko

01:54:14.823 --> 01:54:16.457
kupitia kwako tu
kioo cha welder.

01:54:16.491 --> 01:54:19.193
Tisini
sekunde hadi mlipuko.

01:54:20.829 --> 01:54:23.665
Sekunde tisini kabla ya mlipuko.

01:54:23.698 --> 01:54:25.800
Je, inasuguliwa ndani?

01:54:25.834 --> 01:54:27.201
Ndiyo.

01:54:33.541 --> 01:54:36.644
Sitini
sekunde hadi mlipuko.

01:54:51.325 --> 01:54:53.561
Mambo haya ni
ngumu moyoni mwako.

01:54:53.594 --> 01:54:55.296
Sekunde thelathini.

01:55:00.401 --> 01:55:01.803
Vilipuzi vimetozwa.

01:55:11.947 --> 01:55:15.416
Kumi na saba, kumi na sita,

01:55:15.450 --> 01:55:16.617
kumi na tano,

01:55:16.651 --> 01:55:17.820
kumi na nne,

01:55:17.853 --> 01:55:19.654
kumi na tatu,

01:55:19.687 --> 01:55:21.857
kumi na mbili,

01:55:21.890 --> 01:55:23.558
kumi na moja,

01:55:23.591 --> 01:55:25.560
kumi,

01:55:25.593 --> 01:55:27.996
tisa,

01:55:28.030 --> 01:55:29.998
nane,

01:55:30.032 --> 01:55:32.600
saba,

01:55:32.633 --> 01:55:35.003
sita...

01:55:35.037 --> 01:55:36.504
tano...

01:55:38.506 --> 01:55:40.976
nne...

01:55:41.009 --> 01:55:42.945
tatu...

01:55:42.978 --> 01:55:44.512
mbili...

01:55:45.814 --> 01:55:46.882
moja.

01:56:08.402 --> 01:56:10.338
Pofu.

01:57:19.141 --> 01:57:22.510
<i>"Na sasa
Nimekuwa Kifo.</i>

01:57:24.412 --> 01:57:26.581
<i>Mwangamizi wa ulimwengu."</i>

01:57:59.580 --> 01:58:00.949
Ilifanya kazi.

01:58:36.184 --> 01:58:38.186
- Unadaiwa dola kumi!
- Oh!

01:58:40.521 --> 01:58:41.656
- Njoo!
- Subiri.

01:58:41.689 --> 01:58:43.125
Mimi ni mzuri kwa hilo, Kisty.

01:58:43.158 --> 01:58:45.459
Wewe ni.

01:58:45.493 --> 01:58:48.196
Ndiyo, wewe ni!

01:59:12.287 --> 01:59:13.822
Umefanya vizuri.

01:59:15.523 --> 01:59:18.060
Tulifanya hivyo! Tulifanya hivyo!

01:59:18.093 --> 01:59:19.995
Umefanya vizuri.

01:59:24.799 --> 01:59:26.634
- Nipate Potsdam mara moja.
- Ndiyo, bwana.

01:59:38.113 --> 01:59:39.881
Pata ujumbe kwa Kitty.

01:59:39.915 --> 01:59:40.614
Hatuwezi kusema chochote.

01:59:40.648 --> 01:59:42.583
Mwambie achukue shuka.

01:59:50.591 --> 01:59:52.127
Tulifanya, kila mtu!

01:59:56.999 --> 01:59:58.799
Hujambo?

01:59:58.834 --> 02:00:01.269
- Habari, Kitty?
- Nini, nini? Charlotte...

02:00:01.303 --> 02:00:02.670
Charlotte, endelea, endelea.

02:00:02.703 --> 02:00:04.072
Ah, vizuri, sijui,

02:00:04.106 --> 02:00:07.309
alisema tu kukuambia
ili "kuleta shuka."

02:00:10.012 --> 02:00:11.579
Kitty?

02:00:12.680 --> 02:00:15.117
Kitty? Kitty, ni
bado upo?

02:00:22.024 --> 02:00:24.159
<i>Ikiwa wanalipua
iko juu sana angani,</i>

02:00:24.192 --> 02:00:25.559
mlipuko hautakuwa na nguvu kama hiyo.

02:00:25.593 --> 02:00:27.628
Kwa heshima, Dk. Oppenheimer,

02:00:27.661 --> 02:00:29.697
tutaichukua kutoka hapa.

02:00:39.941 --> 02:00:42.844
Truman alifanya kifupi
Stalin huko Potsdam?

02:00:42.878 --> 02:00:45.613
Kwa kifupi itakuwa
maelezo ya kupita kiasi.

02:00:45.646 --> 02:00:49.717
Alitaja a
silaha mpya yenye nguvu.

02:00:49.750 --> 02:00:54.823
Stalin alitumai tutaweza
kuitumia dhidi ya Japan.

02:00:56.058 --> 02:00:57.792
Hiyo ni?

02:00:57.826 --> 02:01:01.063
Robert, tumewapa ace,
ni kwa wao kucheza mkono.

02:01:03.198 --> 02:01:05.300
Unalenga ya 6?

02:01:05.333 --> 02:01:07.635
Ni juu ya CO
katika Pasifiki.

02:01:08.970 --> 02:01:11.039
Nije na
unaenda Washington?

02:01:12.640 --> 02:01:13.875
Kwa ajili ya nini?

02:01:16.144 --> 02:01:17.745
Naam, utanijulisha.

02:01:19.081 --> 02:01:20.714
Bila shaka.

02:01:22.284 --> 02:01:23.885
Niwezavyo.

02:01:41.303 --> 02:01:44.172
Je, Wajapani wangejisalimisha
kama walijua nini kinakuja?

02:01:45.407 --> 02:01:47.008
sijui.

02:01:49.411 --> 02:01:51.413
Umeona
Ombi la Szilard?

02:01:51.446 --> 02:01:54.182
Nini kuzimu anafanya Szilard
kujua kuhusu Wajapani?

02:01:54.216 --> 02:01:55.426
Huna saini, sivyo?

02:01:55.450 --> 02:01:58.854
Watu wengi wana. A
watu wengi wana.

02:01:58.887 --> 02:02:00.021
Edward.

02:02:01.289 --> 02:02:02.958
Ukweli kwamba tulitengeneza bomu hili

02:02:02.991 --> 02:02:05.994
haitupi tena...
haki au wajibu wowote zaidi

02:02:06.027 --> 02:02:08.130
kuamua jinsi ilivyo
kutumika kuliko mtu mwingine yeyote.

02:02:08.163 --> 02:02:10.165
Lakini sisi pekee
watu wanaojua juu yake.

02:02:10.198 --> 02:02:13.767
Nimeiambia Stimson mbalimbali
maoni ya jamii.

02:02:13.801 --> 02:02:15.203
Lakini nini maoni yako?

02:02:16.438 --> 02:02:17.973
Mara tu inapotumika ...

02:02:19.074 --> 02:02:22.776
vita vya nyuklia, labda vita vyote ...

02:02:24.379 --> 02:02:25.814
inakuwa isiyofikirika.

02:02:25.847 --> 02:02:28.850
Mpaka mtu
hutengeneza bomu kubwa zaidi.

02:02:49.437 --> 02:02:51.173
Nilidhani wangepiga simu.

02:02:51.206 --> 02:02:52.773
Ni ya 5 tu.

02:02:54.943 --> 02:02:56.945
Huko Japan, ni ya 6.

02:03:10.091 --> 02:03:11.092
Charlotte.

02:03:13.428 --> 02:03:15.130
Jaribu Groves.

02:03:16.131 --> 02:03:17.199
<i>Chochote?</i>

02:03:19.501 --> 02:03:20.869
Charlotte?

02:03:20.902 --> 02:03:22.204
ya Truman
kwenye redio.

02:03:23.138 --> 02:03:26.041
Saa kumi na sita zilizopita,

02:03:26.074 --> 02:03:31.980
ndege ya Marekani ilianguka
bomu moja kwenye Hiroshima...

02:03:33.014 --> 02:03:36.151
na kuharibu yake
manufaa kwa adui.

02:03:38.119 --> 02:03:43.992
Bomu lilikuwa na nguvu zaidi
zaidi ya tani 20,000 za TNT.

02:03:45.460 --> 02:03:47.929
Ni bomu la atomiki.

02:03:51.132 --> 02:03:52.500
Ni kuunganisha

02:03:52.534 --> 02:03:55.303
ya nguvu za msingi
ya ulimwengu.

02:03:57.339 --> 02:03:58.974
<i>Groves kwenye moja.</i>

02:03:59.007 --> 02:04:02.043
Sasa tumejiandaa
kuharibu kwa haraka zaidi

02:04:02.077 --> 02:04:04.379
na Wajapani kabisa ...

02:04:04.412 --> 02:04:06.081
Mkuu?

02:04:06.114 --> 02:04:09.150
Ninajivunia sana
wewe na watu wako wote.

02:04:09.184 --> 02:04:10.518
Ilikwenda sawa?

02:04:10.552 --> 02:04:13.521
Inavyoonekana, ilikwenda
kwa kishindo kikubwa.

02:04:13.555 --> 02:04:15.190
Naam,

02:04:15.223 --> 02:04:18.159
kila mtu hapa anahisi
nzuri kuhusu hilo.

02:04:19.594 --> 02:04:21.229
Imekuwa njia ndefu.

02:04:21.263 --> 02:04:24.065
Nadhani moja ya
mambo ya busara zaidi niliyowahi kufanya

02:04:24.099 --> 02:04:27.135
ilikuwa wakati nilichagua
mkurugenzi wa Los Alamos.

02:04:29.504 --> 02:04:31.840
<i>Tumetumia</i>

02:04:31.873 --> 02:04:33.875
<i>zaidi ya dola bilioni 2</i>

02:04:33.908 --> 02:04:38.146
<i>juu ya kisayansi kubwa zaidi
kamari katika historia,</i>

02:04:38.179 --> 02:04:41.016
<i>na tumeshinda.</i>

02:04:44.552 --> 02:04:47.255
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!

02:04:47.289 --> 02:04:49.291
Oppie! Oppie!

02:04:49.324 --> 02:04:52.527
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!

02:04:52.560 --> 02:04:54.396
Oppie! Oppie!

02:04:54.429 --> 02:04:57.198
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!

02:04:57.232 --> 02:05:00.568
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!

02:05:00.602 --> 02:05:05.206
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!

02:05:05.240 --> 02:05:06.574
Oppie! Oppie!

02:05:06.608 --> 02:05:09.177
Oppie! Oppie! Oppie! Oppie!

02:06:08.269 --> 02:06:09.371
Dunia...

02:06:11.373 --> 02:06:12.507
utakumbuka siku hii.

02:06:31.426 --> 02:06:33.161
Ni mapema mno ku...

02:06:34.028 --> 02:06:35.697
Ni mapema sana kuamua

02:06:35.730 --> 02:06:38.099
matokeo gani
ya mabomu ni.

02:06:41.035 --> 02:06:42.637
Lakini mimi itabidi bet
Wajapani hawakuipenda.

02:07:03.525 --> 02:07:05.059
Ninajivunia sana.

02:07:06.194 --> 02:07:08.329
Hivyo fahari ya nini
wamefanikiwa.

02:07:14.636 --> 02:07:18.473
Natamani tu tungekuwa nayo kwa wakati
kutumia dhidi ya Wajerumani.

02:09:08.316 --> 02:09:10.184
Dk Oppenheimer?

02:09:10.785 --> 02:09:13.087
Dk Oppenheimer?

02:09:13.121 --> 02:09:14.789
- Picha nzuri.
- Oh.

02:09:14.823 --> 02:09:17.158
Rais Truman
tutakuona sasa.

02:09:30.873 --> 02:09:33.708
Oppenheimer Dk. Ni heshima.

02:09:33.741 --> 02:09:35.677
- Mheshimiwa Rais.
- Tafadhali.

02:09:35.710 --> 02:09:37.512
Asante.

02:09:37.545 --> 02:09:39.080
Katibu Byrnes.

02:09:40.281 --> 02:09:42.283
Unajisikiaje kuwa

02:09:42.317 --> 02:09:44.352
maarufu zaidi
mtu duniani?

02:09:45.353 --> 02:09:48.423
Umesaidia kuokoa mengi
ya maisha ya Marekani.

02:09:48.456 --> 02:09:50.826
Tulichofanya
Hiroshima alikuwa...

02:09:50.859 --> 02:09:52.794
Na Nagasaki.

02:09:52.828 --> 02:09:54.830
Naam, ni wazi.

02:09:54.863 --> 02:09:58.800
Uvumbuzi wako turuhusu
walete vijana wetu nyumbani.

02:09:58.834 --> 02:10:02.203
Naam, ilikuwa vigumu
uvumbuzi wangu.

02:10:02.236 --> 02:10:04.505
Ilikuwa ni wewe kwenye jalada la <i>Wakati.</i>

02:10:07.375 --> 02:10:08.911
Jim ananiambia una wasiwasi

02:10:08.944 --> 02:10:10.712
kuhusu mbio za silaha
pamoja na Wasovieti.

02:10:10.745 --> 02:10:13.114
Uh, ndio, uh...

02:10:13.816 --> 02:10:15.316
Naam, um,

02:10:15.350 --> 02:10:20.455
ni kwamba, uh, sasa ni
nafasi yetu ya kujilinda

02:10:20.488 --> 02:10:23.358
ushirikiano wa kimataifa juu ya
nishati ya atomiki,

02:10:23.391 --> 02:10:26.427
na ... na nina wasiwasi ...

02:10:26.461 --> 02:10:28.696
Je! unajua wakati Soviets
watakuwa na bomu?

02:10:28.730 --> 02:10:30.665
Sidhani kama ningeweza kutoa...

02:10:30.698 --> 02:10:32.101
Kamwe.

02:10:32.734 --> 02:10:34.369
Kamwe.

02:10:34.402 --> 02:10:37.572
Mheshimiwa Rais, the-the
Warusi wana wanafizikia wazuri

02:10:37.605 --> 02:10:39.240
na-na... na
rasilimali nyingi.

02:10:39.273 --> 02:10:41.376
- Nyingi?
- Ndiyo.

02:10:41.409 --> 02:10:44.679
Sidhani hivyo.

02:10:44.712 --> 02:10:48.249
Naam, wata-wataweka
kila kitu wanacho na...

02:10:51.519 --> 02:10:55.390
Nasikia uko
kuondoka Los Alamos.

02:10:56.658 --> 02:10:57.759
Tufanye nini nayo?

02:10:57.792 --> 02:11:00.294
Warudishie Wahindi.

02:11:07.702 --> 02:11:10.939
Um... Dk Oppenheimer,

02:11:10.973 --> 02:11:13.307
kama unasema nini kuhusu
Soviets ni kweli,

02:11:13.341 --> 02:11:16.744
tunapaswa kuijenga Los Alamos,

02:11:16.778 --> 02:11:18.680
si kuifunga.

02:11:21.917 --> 02:11:23.718
Ah, Mheshimiwa Rais...

02:11:24.786 --> 02:11:26.287
Um...

02:11:28.957 --> 02:11:32.627
Ninahisi kuwa ninayo
damu mikononi mwangu.

02:11:52.413 --> 02:11:57.719
Unafikiri mtu yeyote ndani
Hiroshima au Nagasaki

02:11:57.752 --> 02:12:00.788
anatoa shit nani alijenga bomu?

02:12:03.959 --> 02:12:06.327
Wanajali ni nani aliyeiacha.

02:12:07.029 --> 02:12:09.297
nilifanya.

02:12:10.531 --> 02:12:13.501
Hiroshima haikuhusu.

02:12:19.640 --> 02:12:21.776
Oppenheimer Dk.

02:12:32.720 --> 02:12:35.523
Usiruhusu hilo
mtoto wa kulia amerudi humu ndani.

02:12:40.628 --> 02:12:43.664
<i>Robert aliona hivyo
kukunja mikono hakumfikisha popote.</i>

02:12:43.698 --> 02:12:47.035
<i>Kufikia wakati nilikutana
yake, alikumbatia kikamilifu</i>

02:12:47.069 --> 02:12:49.637
<i>"baba yake wa
bomu" sifa.</i>

02:12:49.670 --> 02:12:52.074
Alitumia wasifu wake
kuathiri sera.

02:13:01.549 --> 02:13:02.927
<i>Daktari, katika
miaka baada ya vita,</i>

02:13:02.951 --> 02:13:05.087
ungesema hivyo wewe
alitoa ushawishi mkubwa

02:13:05.120 --> 02:13:06.922
juu ya atomiki
sera za Marekani?

02:13:06.955 --> 02:13:09.657
<i>Nadhani mkuu
itakuwa ni overstatement.</i>

02:13:09.690 --> 02:13:11.659
Kweli? Tukiangalia
katika suala la isotopu,

02:13:11.692 --> 02:13:13.394
si wewe
kuwajibika binafsi

02:13:13.427 --> 02:13:15.463
kwa kuharibu yote
upinzani kwa mauzo yao nje?

02:13:15.496 --> 02:13:18.366
Inaweza kutumia chupa ya bia...

02:13:18.399 --> 02:13:20.078
wakati wa kutengeneza atomiki
silaha. Kwa kweli, unafanya.

02:13:20.102 --> 02:13:22.570
Nilikuwa msemaji,
lakini maoni

02:13:22.603 --> 02:13:24.405
miongoni mwa wanasayansi walikuwa na kauli moja.

02:13:24.438 --> 02:13:26.108
Wote pamoja
McCarthy anaongezeka,

02:13:26.141 --> 02:13:27.542
alijua alikuwa katika mazingira magumu.

02:13:27.575 --> 02:13:28.944
Ndugu yake aliorodheshwa

02:13:28.977 --> 02:13:31.880
na kila chuo kikuu
nchini.

02:13:32.981 --> 02:13:35.818
Lomanitz alianza kufanya kazi
reli, kuweka wimbo.

02:13:38.419 --> 02:13:39.855
Na Chevalier akaenda uhamishoni.

02:13:42.991 --> 02:13:44.425
Lakini hakuna kati ya hayo

02:13:44.458 --> 02:13:46.427
kumzuia Robert kutoka
kusukuma GAC

02:13:46.460 --> 02:13:49.330
kupendekeza udhibiti wa silaha
badala ya bomu H.

02:13:51.133 --> 02:13:52.600
Alihuzunika sana

02:13:52.633 --> 02:13:54.702
wakati Truman alikataa
mapendekezo yao.

02:13:56.437 --> 02:13:58.974
Nimemkumbuka zaidi Richard
kuliko niwezavyo kustahimili.

02:13:59.007 --> 02:14:00.775
Najua, Ruth, najua.

02:14:00.809 --> 02:14:03.912
Sehemu yangu nimefurahi kwamba hakuishi
kuona haya yote yanaenda wapi.

02:14:06.681 --> 02:14:08.116
Hapa inakuja
mvulana wa kuzaliwa.

02:14:08.150 --> 02:14:10.751
- Kufurahi.
- Kuwa na furaha.

02:14:11.752 --> 02:14:14.122
Robert, uh, mwanangu na wake
mchumba wanatamani kukutana

02:14:14.156 --> 02:14:16.124
baba wa
bomu la atomiki, na hivyo ...

02:14:16.158 --> 02:14:18.961
Naam. Siku njema.

02:14:25.033 --> 02:14:27.135
Je, huu ni wakati mbaya?

02:14:27.169 --> 02:14:28.669
Unafikiri nini, Lewis?

02:14:28.703 --> 02:14:30.771
Naam, nadhani ni lazima
imekuwa pigo kwako.

02:14:30.805 --> 02:14:32.941
Kwa ulimwengu.

02:14:32.975 --> 02:14:34.609
Ulimwengu?

02:14:34.642 --> 02:14:38.613
Fuchs ina maana gani
wengine wa dunia?

02:14:38.646 --> 02:14:40.048
Fuchs?

02:14:40.082 --> 02:14:41.682
Klaus Fuchs?

02:14:43.118 --> 02:14:45.519
Oh, mpenzi. Hujasikia.

02:14:48.689 --> 02:14:50.558
Klaus Fuchs, Muingereza
mwanasayansi kwamba kuweka

02:14:50.591 --> 02:14:53.628
kwenye implosion
timu katika Los Alamos,

02:14:53.661 --> 02:14:55.796
<i>ilibainika kuwa alikuwa...</i>

02:14:55.831 --> 02:14:59.101
alikuwa anapeleleza
Soviets wakati wote.

02:14:59.134 --> 02:15:00.668
samahani.

02:15:05.841 --> 02:15:08.743
<i>Baada ya ukweli
kuhusu Fuchs ilitoka,</i>

02:15:08.776 --> 02:15:10.879
FBI wakaongeza kasi
ufuatiliaji juu yake.

02:15:10.913 --> 02:15:14.782
Akajua simu yake imegongwa,
alifuatwa kila mahali...

02:15:16.151 --> 02:15:17.585
takataka yake ilichukua.

02:15:21.589 --> 02:15:23.058
Lakini kamwe kusimamishwa
akiongea mawazo yake.

02:15:23.091 --> 02:15:25.760
Mtu wa kujiamini.

02:15:25.793 --> 02:15:28.629
Na labda alifikiria umaarufu
kweli angeweza kumlinda.

02:15:30.132 --> 02:15:33.567
Eisenhower alipoingia madarakani,
aliona nafasi moja zaidi.

02:15:34.970 --> 02:15:36.004
Alichukua.

02:15:36.038 --> 02:15:38.506
Amerika na Urusi

02:15:38.539 --> 02:15:42.811
inaweza kufananishwa na mbili
nge katika chupa,

02:15:42.844 --> 02:15:46.214
kila mmoja anaweza
kumuua mwingine

02:15:46.248 --> 02:15:48.951
lakini kwa hatari tu
ya maisha yake mwenyewe.

02:15:48.984 --> 02:15:51.752
Sasa, kuna anuwai
vipengele vya sera hii...

02:15:51.786 --> 02:15:53.788
<i>Mengi ya
wanasayansi wananilaumu,</i>

02:15:53.822 --> 02:15:56.959
<i>lakini nilitakiwa vipi
kumlinda?</i>

02:15:56.992 --> 02:15:58.961
Siri sana kwa majadiliano,

02:15:58.994 --> 02:16:00.996
candor ndio dawa pekee.

02:16:01.029 --> 02:16:02.563
Maafisa huko Washington

02:16:02.596 --> 02:16:04.108
haja ya kuanza kusawazisha
pamoja na watu wa Marekani.

02:16:05.800 --> 02:16:08.636
Hiyo ndiyo ilikuwa nyasi ya mwisho
kwa maadui wa Robert.

02:16:08.669 --> 02:16:10.705
Kwa hivyo ilibidi apoteze yake
kibali cha usalama.

02:16:10.738 --> 02:16:13.507
Na kwa hiyo, uaminifu wake.

02:16:13.541 --> 02:16:15.944
Lakini wangewezaje kufanya hivyo?

02:16:15.978 --> 02:16:17.245
Alikuwa shujaa wa vita.

02:16:17.279 --> 02:16:18.981
Alikuwa tayari aliiambia
kila mtu kuhusu maisha yake ya nyuma.

02:16:19.014 --> 02:16:20.983
Borden aliiondoa yote.

02:16:21.016 --> 02:16:24.252
Borden angewezaje kupata ufikiaji
kwa faili ya FBI ya Oppenheimer?

02:16:24.286 --> 02:16:25.854
Inaweza kuwa Nichols?

02:16:25.887 --> 02:16:28.190
Hapana, siwezi kufikiria
angefanya hivyo.

02:16:28.223 --> 02:16:30.258
Lakini ni nani aliyefanya
alifyatua dhoruba ya moto

02:16:30.292 --> 02:16:32.294
iliyochoma njia
kutoka Ikulu ya Marekani

02:16:32.326 --> 02:16:34.996
kurudi kwenye dawati langu huko AEC.

02:16:35.030 --> 02:16:36.865
Unawaona humo ndani, sivyo?

02:16:36.897 --> 02:16:40.768
Nimekuwa nikifanya kazi yangu
maisha yote kufika hapa.

02:16:40.800 --> 02:16:42.838
Baraza la Mawaziri la Muungano
Majimbo ya Amerika.

02:16:42.870 --> 02:16:44.805
Sasa, mbele
nchi nzima,

02:16:44.840 --> 02:16:46.907
wataweka
nirudi katika nafasi yangu.

02:16:48.343 --> 02:16:51.013
Mchuuzi wa viatu duni.

02:16:51.046 --> 02:16:52.880
Lewis, tunaweza kushinda jambo hili.

02:16:52.914 --> 02:16:54.983
Na-nadhani tunaweza kupata
Seneti kufahamu

02:16:55.017 --> 02:16:57.818
kwamba umetimiza wajibu wako,
ingawa ilikuwa chungu.

02:16:57.852 --> 02:16:59.620
Sasa, mapenzi ya Hill
ushuhuda unatuunga mkono?

02:16:59.653 --> 02:17:01.630
- Hill itakuwa sawa.
-Simjui kabisa,

02:17:01.655 --> 02:17:03.825
lakini, uh, alikuwa mmoja wao
Wavulana wa Szilard huko Chicago,

02:17:03.859 --> 02:17:05.894
na hawakusamehe kamwe
Robert kwa kutokuunga mkono

02:17:05.927 --> 02:17:08.330
dua yao
dhidi ya kulipua Japan.

02:17:08.362 --> 02:17:13.566
Hii ilichukuliwa siku 31
baada ya kulipuliwa.

02:17:13.601 --> 02:17:16.338
Karibu kila mtu
mitaani,

02:17:16.370 --> 02:17:18.606
kwa karibu maili moja kuzunguka,

02:17:18.638 --> 02:17:21.843
ilikuwa mara moja na
kuchomwa moto sana.

02:17:23.077 --> 02:17:27.615
Wajapani walizungumza
watu waliovaa nguo za mistari

02:17:27.647 --> 02:17:30.618
juu ya nani ngozi
alichomwa moto kwa kupigwa.

02:17:31.684 --> 02:17:34.056
Kulikuwa na wengi ambao
walijiona kuwa na bahati,

02:17:34.089 --> 02:17:36.790
ambaye alipanda nje ya
magofu ya nyumba zao

02:17:36.825 --> 02:17:38.691
kujeruhiwa kidogo tu.

02:17:39.827 --> 02:17:41.594
Lakini walikufa hata hivyo.

02:17:42.263 --> 02:17:45.367
Walikufa siku au wiki baadaye

02:17:45.400 --> 02:17:48.736
kutoka kwa miale inayofanana na radium
zinazotolewa kwa wingi

02:17:48.769 --> 02:17:50.671
wakati wa mlipuko.

02:17:51.873 --> 02:17:53.941
Umeisoma hii
ujinga kwenye karatasi?

02:17:53.975 --> 02:17:56.777
Mwanafizikia wa Uingereza ni
akisema mabomu ya atomiki

02:17:56.812 --> 02:17:58.980
hawakuwa wa mwisho
kitendo cha Vita vya Kidunia vya pili

02:17:59.013 --> 02:18:02.150
lakini kitendo cha kwanza cha hii
vita baridi na Urusi.

02:18:02.183 --> 02:18:03.651
Mwanafizikia gani?

02:18:03.683 --> 02:18:05.087
Nadhani ulikuwa unamfahamu.

02:18:05.120 --> 02:18:06.719
Patrick Blackett.

02:18:09.191 --> 02:18:10.758
Anaweza kuwa hana makosa.

02:18:10.790 --> 02:18:12.127
Stimson sasa ananiambia

02:18:12.160 --> 02:18:15.397
tulimpiga bomu adui huyo
kimsingi alishindwa.

02:18:15.430 --> 02:18:18.967
Robert, umefanya
ushawishi wote sasa.

02:18:19.000 --> 02:18:20.700
Tafadhali.

02:18:20.734 --> 02:18:22.838
Wasihi waendelee yangu
utafiti juu ya Super.

02:18:22.870 --> 02:18:24.239
Siwezi wala sitaweza, Edward.

02:18:24.272 --> 02:18:26.374
Kwa nini sivyo?

02:18:26.407 --> 02:18:28.110
Sio haki
matumizi ya rasilimali zetu.

02:18:28.143 --> 02:18:30.245
Je, ndivyo unavyoamini kweli?

02:18:30.278 --> 02:18:32.646
J. Robert Oppenheimer.

02:18:32.680 --> 02:18:35.083
Guru wa atomi kama Sphinx.

02:18:36.384 --> 02:18:38.153
Hakuna anayejua unachoamini.

02:18:39.254 --> 02:18:41.123
Je! wewe? Hmm?

02:18:41.156 --> 02:18:43.859
<i>Mara moja ya mwisho,
mkurugenzi wetu wa programu,</i>

02:18:43.892 --> 02:18:45.861
<i>Dkt. J. Robert Oppenheimer.</i>

02:18:47.062 --> 02:18:48.830
<i>Natumaini hilo
katika miaka ijayo</i>

02:18:48.864 --> 02:18:52.868
utaangalia nyuma
kazi yako hapa kwa kujivunia.

02:18:52.901 --> 02:18:55.270
Lakini leo, kiburi hicho
lazima iwe na hasira

02:18:55.303 --> 02:18:57.638
kwa wasiwasi mkubwa.

02:18:58.906 --> 02:19:00.708
Ikiwa silaha za atomiki
zinapaswa kuongezwa

02:19:00.741 --> 02:19:03.145
kwa maghala ya
ulimwengu wa vita,

02:19:03.178 --> 02:19:06.746
basi siku itakuja
watu watakapolaani

02:19:06.780 --> 02:19:08.183
Jina la Los Alamos.

02:19:12.187 --> 02:19:14.289
Samahani, Admiral.

02:19:14.322 --> 02:19:16.324
Imesimama ili kupata hii.

02:19:16.358 --> 02:19:19.161
Inaonekana ni nzuri sana.

02:19:19.193 --> 02:19:20.304
Kuna Oppenheimer.

02:19:20.327 --> 02:19:21.897
Manukuu ni yapi?

02:19:21.930 --> 02:19:24.764
Huu, "J. Robert Oppenheimer,
Strauss alipigana ... "

02:19:26.334 --> 02:19:27.903
"na Marekani ilishinda."

02:19:28.736 --> 02:19:30.004
Hiyo itafanya kazi.

02:19:30.038 --> 02:19:32.273
Hayo yalikuwa maneno yako
kutoka siku nyingine.

02:19:32.307 --> 02:19:33.707
Tulihitaji kugeuza.

02:19:33.741 --> 02:19:35.010
Lakini ungejuaje

02:19:35.043 --> 02:19:36.844
nini <i>Wakati</i> gazeti la
nitaandika?

02:19:36.878 --> 02:19:39.114
Henry Luce ni rafiki.

02:19:45.253 --> 02:19:48.756
Umekaa hapa na kuniruhusu
niambie jinsi inafanyika,

02:19:48.789 --> 02:19:51.459
lakini umekuwa mbali
mbele wakati wote.

02:19:51.493 --> 02:19:54.462
Kuishi huko Washington

02:19:54.496 --> 02:19:56.831
ni juu ya kujua jinsi
kufanya mambo.

02:19:57.465 --> 02:19:58.867
Sawa.

02:20:00.468 --> 02:20:02.204
Wewe ulikuwa nini
Alisema kuhusu Borden?

02:20:02.237 --> 02:20:05.240
“Kwanini ushikwe ukiwa umeshika
kisu mwenyewe?"

02:20:07.075 --> 02:20:10.078
Ninaanza kufikiria Borden
alikuwa amekuwekea kisu.

02:20:12.147 --> 02:20:14.382
Itakuja chini
kwa ushawishi kiasi gani

02:20:14.416 --> 02:20:16.484
Borden ameweza
kufanya bidii kwa Teller.

02:20:16.518 --> 02:20:18.954
Je, nimesema jambo la kuchekesha?

02:20:18.987 --> 02:20:20.355
Tu "Borden, Borden, Borden"

02:20:20.388 --> 02:20:24.159
wakati sote tunajua
kwamba ni Strauss.

02:20:24.192 --> 02:20:26.161
Lewis alinileta
Princeton, Kitty.

02:20:26.194 --> 02:20:28.897
Na kisha ukafedheheka
yake mbele ya Congress.

02:20:28.930 --> 02:20:31.765
Lakini ni muhimu zaidi kuliko sandwich.

02:20:34.936 --> 02:20:36.113
- Nilifanyaje?
- Nitaita mapumziko,

02:20:36.137 --> 02:20:37.239
dakika kumi.

02:20:37.272 --> 02:20:39.507
Labda kidogo sana, Robert.

02:20:39.541 --> 02:20:40.774
Hiyo ilikuwa miaka sita iliyopita.

02:20:40.809 --> 02:20:42.510
Unajua, mwenye kulipiza kisasi kweli,

02:20:42.544 --> 02:20:44.145
mvumilivu kama watakatifu.

02:20:44.179 --> 02:20:46.982
Strauss imekuwa kikamilifu
wazi kwamba hana upande wowote.

02:20:47.015 --> 02:20:50.518
Amka. Ni Strauss.

02:20:50.552 --> 02:20:53.488
Imekuwa daima
Strauss, na unajua.

02:20:53.521 --> 02:20:55.156
Kwa nini usipigane naye?

02:20:56.191 --> 02:20:57.392
Kwa ajili ya Kristo.

02:20:58.493 --> 02:21:01.162
Haikuwa Nichols au Hoover

02:21:01.196 --> 02:21:02.864
au moja ya Truman
wavulana. Ilikuwa ni wewe.

02:21:02.897 --> 02:21:04.866
Ulimpa Borden faili.

02:21:04.899 --> 02:21:06.534
Ulimweka kwenye Oppenheimer.

02:21:06.568 --> 02:21:09.004
- Ulimshawishi ...
- Borden ...

02:21:09.037 --> 02:21:10.939
Haikufanya hivyo
kuchukua kushawishi yoyote.

02:21:10.972 --> 02:21:13.074
Chukua wakati wako,
tumia faili nzima.

02:21:13.108 --> 02:21:16.011
Andika hitimisho lako,
wapeleke kwa FBI.

02:21:16.044 --> 02:21:18.280
Nyenzo ni
dhahiri ni pana,

02:21:18.313 --> 02:21:20.982
lakini hakuna jipya hapa.

02:21:21.016 --> 02:21:22.550
Wako
mahitimisho yatakuwa.

02:21:22.584 --> 02:21:24.886
Na itabidi wajibiwe.

02:21:24.919 --> 02:21:26.388
Hoover anawapitisha kwa McCarthy?

02:21:26.421 --> 02:21:30.025
Oppenheimer inateleza sana
kwa huyo mcheshi anayejitangaza.

02:21:30.058 --> 02:21:32.927
Nimezungumza na Hoover,
atamshika McCarthy pembeni

02:21:32.961 --> 02:21:34.562
wakati unafanya hivi na AEC.

02:21:34.596 --> 02:21:36.431
- Jaribio.
- Hapana.

02:21:36.464 --> 02:21:40.235
Hakuna jaribio. Huwezi kutoa
Oppenheimer jukwaa.

02:21:40.268 --> 02:21:42.037
Huwezi kumuua.

02:21:42.070 --> 02:21:45.240
Tunahitaji uharibifu wa utaratibu
uaminifu wa Oppenheimer

02:21:45.273 --> 02:21:48.843
hivyo hawezi tena kuongea
mambo ya usalama wa taifa.

02:21:48.877 --> 02:21:50.945
Kisha nini?

02:21:52.147 --> 02:21:55.517
Chumba kidogo chakavu,
mbali na mwangaza.

02:22:01.956 --> 02:22:03.234
<i>rahisi
utaratibu wa urasimu.</i>

02:22:03.258 --> 02:22:05.894
Kibali chake cha Q
iko kwa ajili ya kufanywa upya.

02:22:05.927 --> 02:22:08.897
Unatuma yako
tuhuma kwa FBI.

02:22:10.532 --> 02:22:14.135
Hoover inawatuma kwa
AEC, unalazimishwa kuchukua hatua.

02:22:14.969 --> 02:22:16.271
Unaandika hati ya mashtaka

02:22:16.304 --> 02:22:17.939
<i>na mwambie Oppenheimer</i>

02:22:17.972 --> 02:22:20.642
<i>kibali chake cha usalama
haifanyiwi upya.</i>

02:22:20.675 --> 02:22:22.210
<i>Lakini mpe
nafasi ya kukata rufaa.</i>

02:22:22.243 --> 02:22:24.579
Kama unavyoona, Robert,
bado haijasainiwa.

02:22:24.612 --> 02:22:26.114
Naweza kuweka hii?

02:22:26.147 --> 02:22:27.082
Hapana.

02:22:27.115 --> 02:22:29.351
Ukiamua kukata rufaa,

02:22:29.384 --> 02:22:30.919
itabidi wakutumie nakala.

02:22:30.952 --> 02:22:34.189
Anapokata rufaa... na
niamini, ata...

02:22:34.222 --> 02:22:36.624
Ninateua bodi.

02:22:36.658 --> 02:22:39.127
Watafanya, ya
bila shaka, kuwa na shauri.

02:22:39.160 --> 02:22:41.096
- Mwendesha mashtaka?
- Katika yote isipokuwa jina.

02:22:41.129 --> 02:22:43.298
- WHO?
- Roger Robb.

02:22:43.331 --> 02:22:44.499
Lo.

02:22:44.532 --> 02:22:46.000
Robb atakuwa nayo
kibali cha usalama

02:22:46.034 --> 02:22:47.569
<i>kuchunguza faili ya Oppenheimer.</i>

02:22:47.602 --> 02:22:49.037
<i>Kama vile bodi ya Grey.</i>

02:22:49.070 --> 02:22:50.438
Wakili wa utetezi hatafanya hivyo.

02:22:52.273 --> 02:22:53.675
Usikilizaji uliofungwa.

02:22:53.708 --> 02:22:54.952
<i>Kinachojulikana
habari za dharau</i>

02:22:54.976 --> 02:22:57.145
katika mashitaka yako kwangu.

02:22:57.178 --> 02:22:59.647
Hakuna hadhira. Hakuna waandishi wa habari.

02:22:59.681 --> 02:23:03.151
- Hakuna mzigo wa ushahidi.
- Hakuna mzigo wa ushahidi?

02:23:04.519 --> 02:23:06.020
Hatuhukumu.

02:23:06.721 --> 02:23:09.324
Tunakataa tu.

02:23:14.295 --> 02:23:17.065
Umesema nini?

02:23:17.098 --> 02:23:20.435
"Hivi ndivyo tu
mchezo unachezwa."

02:23:20.468 --> 02:23:23.438
Naam, nisamehe naivete wangu.

02:23:23.471 --> 02:23:25.440
Amateurs hutafuta jua.

02:23:26.408 --> 02:23:27.475
Pata kuliwa.

02:23:28.543 --> 02:23:31.379
Nguvu inakaa kwenye vivuli.

02:23:31.413 --> 02:23:35.116
Lakini, bwana, wewe ni…wewe
nje ya vivuli sasa.

02:23:35.150 --> 02:23:36.584
Ndiyo, ndiyo sababu
hii inabidi ifanye kazi.

02:23:36.618 --> 02:23:38.086
Naam...

02:23:39.387 --> 02:23:41.523
Teller akishuhudia
asubuhi hii.

02:23:41.556 --> 02:23:43.958
Hiyo itasaidia. Na kisha ...

02:23:43.992 --> 02:23:45.427
Hill ni mchana.

02:23:45.460 --> 02:23:47.929
Hill itatusaidia pia.

02:23:50.165 --> 02:23:53.334
Kama unavyoona,
Robert, bado haijatiwa saini.

02:23:53.368 --> 02:23:54.402
Naweza kuweka hii?

02:23:54.436 --> 02:23:55.470
Hapana.

02:23:57.572 --> 02:23:59.574
Ukiamua kukata rufaa,

02:23:59.607 --> 02:24:02.444
basi watapata
kukutumia nakala.

02:24:06.014 --> 02:24:08.316
Chukua gari langu na
dereva. nasisitiza.

02:24:13.054 --> 02:24:14.989
Itanibidi kushauriana
wanasheria wangu, Lewis.

02:24:15.023 --> 02:24:17.725
Bila shaka. Lakini
usichukue muda mrefu sana.

02:24:17.759 --> 02:24:19.961
Siwezi kumweka Nichols pembeni.

02:24:26.100 --> 02:24:28.403
Samahani imekuja
kwa hili, Robert.

02:24:28.436 --> 02:24:29.471
Nadhani ni makosa.

02:24:42.784 --> 02:24:44.219
<i>Nichols
anataka nipigane</i>

02:24:44.252 --> 02:24:46.254
<i>ili aweze kuipata
yote kwenye rekodi.</i>

02:24:46.287 --> 02:24:48.156
Strauss anataka niondoke.

02:24:48.189 --> 02:24:51.025
Strauss anajua hilo
huwezi kufanya hivyo,

02:24:51.059 --> 02:24:53.495
ungekuwa unakubali mashtaka.

02:24:53.528 --> 02:24:55.196
Utapoteza kazi yako.

02:24:55.230 --> 02:24:57.499
Utapoteza sifa yako.
Tutapoteza nyumba yetu.

02:24:57.532 --> 02:25:00.235
Robert, tunapaswa kupigana.

02:25:02.804 --> 02:25:05.106
Kama Mshauri wa AEC,
Siwezi kukuwakilisha.

02:25:05.139 --> 02:25:06.674
Nitamwita Lloyd Garrison.

02:25:06.708 --> 02:25:08.243
Oh, yeye ni mzuri.

02:25:08.276 --> 02:25:12.013
Bora zaidi, lakini mimi
inabidi nikuonye...

02:25:12.680 --> 02:25:15.116
hii haitakuwa mapambano ya haki.

02:25:15.149 --> 02:25:17.161
<i>Wakati wa mahojiano yako</i>

02:25:17.185 --> 02:25:19.654
na Boris Pash mnamo 1943,
ulirejelea microfilm?

02:25:19.687 --> 02:25:21.189
- Hapana.
- Kichupo cha 11,

02:25:21.222 --> 02:25:22.666
ukurasa wa kwanza, aya
tatu. Hujawahi kusema,

02:25:22.690 --> 02:25:26.327
"Mtu katika mtaalam wa ubalozi
katika matumizi ya filamu ndogo"?

02:25:26.361 --> 02:25:27.695
- Samahani, samahani.
- Hapana.

02:25:27.729 --> 02:25:28.663
Ningependa
kujua hati gani

02:25:28.696 --> 02:25:30.131
Bwana Robb ananukuu kutoka

02:25:30.164 --> 02:25:31.442
na kama tunaweza kuwa
pamoja na nakala.

02:25:31.466 --> 02:25:33.535
Hati ni
classified, Bw. Garrison.

02:25:33.568 --> 02:25:35.412
Nadhani turudi
kwa taarifa za kwanza.

02:25:35.436 --> 02:25:36.804
Hii ni mkono wa kwanza.

02:25:36.839 --> 02:25:39.107
Jinsi gani, Roger?

02:25:40.475 --> 02:25:42.310
Kulikuwa na rekodi
ya mahojiano.

02:25:46.281 --> 02:25:48.182
Wewe basi
mteja wangu kaa hapa

02:25:48.216 --> 02:25:49.717
na uwezekano wa kujiapisha mwenyewe,

02:25:49.751 --> 02:25:52.287
na wakati huu wote,
ulikuwa na rekodi?

02:25:52.320 --> 02:25:53.688
Hakuna mtu aliyemwambia mteja wako

02:25:53.721 --> 02:25:55.123
kupotosha
majibu yake ya awali.

02:25:55.156 --> 02:25:57.225
Kupotosha... Ni-ni
ilikuwa miaka 12 iliyopita.

02:25:57.258 --> 02:25:58.560
Je, tunaweza kusikia rekodi hii?

02:25:58.593 --> 02:26:00.170
Huna
kibali, Bw. Garrison.

02:26:00.194 --> 02:26:01.830
Lakini unasoma
kwenye rekodi.

02:26:01.864 --> 02:26:03.498
Tafadhali, tafadhali.

02:26:03.531 --> 02:26:07.135
Je, tukio hili linavutiwa
katika mtego au katika ukweli?

02:26:07.168 --> 02:26:09.604
Kama ni ukweli, uko wapi
ufichuzi?

02:26:09.637 --> 02:26:11.272
Orodha ya mashahidi iko wapi?

02:26:11.306 --> 02:26:13.842
Mheshimiwa Garrison, hii si
jaribio, kama unavyojua vizuri.

02:26:13.876 --> 02:26:15.743
Sheria za ushahidi hazitumiki.

02:26:15.777 --> 02:26:17.645
Tunashughulika na
usalama wa taifa.

02:26:17.679 --> 02:26:19.180
Ndio, bwana, kwa heshima zote,

02:26:19.213 --> 02:26:21.583
Nashindwa kuona jinsi gani
usalama wa taifa

02:26:21.616 --> 02:26:23.318
inazuia mashtaka
kutokana na kutupatia

02:26:23.351 --> 02:26:25.362
- na orodha ya mashahidi.
- Labda tuna uhitaji

02:26:25.386 --> 02:26:26.697
- mapumziko mafupi.
- Mabwana,

02:26:26.721 --> 02:26:28.456
unayo maneno yangu.

02:26:28.489 --> 02:26:30.634
Ukisema wanatoka kwa a
nakala, basi nitaikubali.

02:26:30.658 --> 02:26:33.428
Tayari nimeelezea nimefanya
juu ya hadithi ya jogoo-na-ng'ombe.

02:26:33.461 --> 02:26:36.798
Lakini kwa nini mtu yeyote afanye
hadithi ya kina kama hii?

02:26:36.832 --> 02:26:38.901
Kwa sababu nilikuwa mjinga.

02:26:38.934 --> 02:26:40.535
Kwa nini uongo?

02:26:40.568 --> 02:26:43.171
Naam, wazi na
nia ya kutokufichua

02:26:43.204 --> 02:26:45.273
aliyekuwa mpatanishi.

02:26:45.306 --> 02:26:47.342
Rafiki yako, Haakon
Chevalier, Mkomunisti.

02:26:47.375 --> 02:26:49.644
Bado ni rafiki yako?

02:26:49.677 --> 02:26:51.112
Ndiyo.

02:26:53.214 --> 02:26:56.150
Dr. Rabi,
asante kwa kuja.

02:26:56.184 --> 02:26:57.896
Je! unajua nani mwingine
upande wa mashtaka umeita?

02:26:57.920 --> 02:27:00.254
Mtangazaji, ni wazi.

02:27:01.222 --> 02:27:02.490
Walimuuliza Lawrence.

02:27:02.523 --> 02:27:03.358
Alisema nini?

02:27:03.391 --> 02:27:06.294
Hakuwa anaenda
kuwasaidia, lakini ...

02:27:06.327 --> 02:27:07.261
Lakini?

02:27:07.295 --> 02:27:09.297
Strauss alimwambia hivyo
wewe na Ruth Tolman

02:27:09.330 --> 02:27:11.766
<i>wamekuwa na
mapenzi kwa miaka.</i>

02:27:11.799 --> 02:27:12.901
<i>Muda wote ulioishi</i>

02:27:12.935 --> 02:27:14.569
pamoja nao huko Pasadena.

02:27:14.602 --> 02:27:16.270
Alimshawishi Lawrence

02:27:16.304 --> 02:27:17.873
kwamba Richard alikufa
ya moyo uliovunjika.

02:27:17.906 --> 02:27:19.207
Huo ni upuuzi.

02:27:19.240 --> 02:27:21.776
- Sehemu gani?
- Moyo uliovunjika.

02:27:21.810 --> 02:27:23.846
Richard hakuwahi kujua.

02:27:23.879 --> 02:27:25.647
Je, Lawrence atatoa ushahidi?

02:27:25.680 --> 02:27:27.181
sijui.

02:27:27.715 --> 02:27:29.350
Dr. Rabi,

02:27:29.384 --> 02:27:32.453
nafasi gani za serikali
unashikilia kwa sasa?

02:27:32.487 --> 02:27:35.390
Mimi ndiye mwenyekiti wa chama
Kamati Kuu ya Ushauri

02:27:35.423 --> 02:27:38.326
kwa AEC, kufanikiwa
Oppenheimer Dk.

02:27:38.359 --> 02:27:41.195
Na muda gani
unamjua Dr Oppenheimer?

02:27:41.229 --> 02:27:42.831
Tangu 1928.

02:27:42.865 --> 02:27:44.933
Mimi... namfahamu vizuri kabisa.

02:27:44.967 --> 02:27:46.935
Vizuri vya kutosha
sema kwa kuzaa

02:27:46.969 --> 02:27:49.537
uaminifu na tabia yake?

02:27:49.570 --> 02:27:53.574
Dk. Oppenheimer ni mwanamume
ya tabia iliyotukuka.

02:27:53.608 --> 02:27:56.277
Na yeye ni mwaminifu kwa
Marekani,

02:27:56.310 --> 02:27:57.545
kwa marafiki zake,

02:27:57.578 --> 02:28:00.248
kwa taasisi
ambayo yeye ni sehemu yake.

02:28:01.716 --> 02:28:02.750
Kula.

02:28:21.736 --> 02:28:23.438
Hiyo ilikuwa nini?

02:28:23.471 --> 02:28:25.506
Hakuna cha kuwa na wasiwasi kuhusu.

02:28:27.742 --> 02:28:29.477
<i>Baada ya
Mtihani wa bomu la A-Russia,</i>

02:28:29.510 --> 02:28:31.980
Dr Lawrence alikuja kuona
wewe kuhusu bomu ya hidrojeni?

02:28:32.014 --> 02:28:33.816
Ingekuwa bora ukimuuliza.

02:28:33.849 --> 02:28:35.383
Naam, nakusudia kabisa.

02:28:35.416 --> 02:28:37.986
Je, unaweza kusema hivyo
Oppenheimer alikuwa Dk

02:28:38.020 --> 02:28:40.022
kupingwa bila kubadilika
kwa H-bomu?

02:28:40.055 --> 02:28:42.858
Hapana, alifikiria
kwamba programu ya fusion

02:28:42.891 --> 02:28:45.994
itakuja kwa gharama zetu
mpango mzuri sana wa fission.

02:28:46.028 --> 02:28:47.863
Lakini hilo lilithibitisha
isiwe hivyo.

02:28:47.896 --> 02:28:50.531
Katika tukio hilo zote mbili zinaweza kufanywa.

02:28:50.565 --> 02:28:52.868
Tuseme kwamba bodi hii
hakujisikia kuridhika

02:28:52.901 --> 02:28:54.036
kwamba katika ushuhuda wake hapa,

02:28:54.069 --> 02:28:56.337
Dk. Oppenheimer alikuwa
umekuwa mkweli kabisa.

02:28:56.370 --> 02:28:59.574
Ungesemaje kama
au si yeye asafishwe?

02:28:59.607 --> 02:29:01.509
Kwa nini upitie yote
hii dhidi ya mwanaume

02:29:01.542 --> 02:29:03.745
ambaye amefanikisha
nini Dr Oppenheimer ana?

02:29:03.778 --> 02:29:05.413
Angalia rekodi yake.

02:29:05.446 --> 02:29:07.515
Tuna A-bomu na
mfululizo mzima wake.

02:29:07.548 --> 02:29:09.484
Tuna nzima
mfululizo wa mabomu makubwa.

02:29:09.517 --> 02:29:11.486
Unataka nini zaidi?

02:29:11.519 --> 02:29:12.386
Nguva?

02:29:12.420 --> 02:29:14.722
Lakini nimejua
Katibu Strauss

02:29:14.756 --> 02:29:16.357
kwa miaka mingi,

02:29:16.390 --> 02:29:19.660
na ninahisi ni lazima
kuelezea msaada wa joto

02:29:19.694 --> 02:29:22.363
kwa sayansi na wanasayansi
Lewis ameonyesha.

02:29:22.396 --> 02:29:23.631
Tutavunja sasa,

02:29:23.664 --> 02:29:25.466
isipokuwa kuna yoyote
biashara ya haraka.

02:29:25.500 --> 02:29:28.036
Seneta, ningependa
napenda kuomba tena

02:29:28.070 --> 02:29:30.738
kwamba tumepewa
na orodha ya mashahidi.

02:29:30.772 --> 02:29:33.541
Nami nitawakumbusha
mteule ambao hatufanyi kila wakati

02:29:33.574 --> 02:29:35.576
kuwa na taarifa hizo
mapema.

02:29:35.610 --> 02:29:39.047
Tunajua kwamba Dk Hill
itakuwa hapa baada ya chakula cha mchana.

02:29:39.081 --> 02:29:40.715
Mheshimiwa Mwenyekiti, ijayo yetu
shahidi aliyepangwa,

02:29:40.748 --> 02:29:45.286
Dk Lawrence, ina inaonekana
kuja na colitis.

02:29:46.754 --> 02:29:49.657
Hivyo tutaweza kuendelea na
William Borden badala yake.

02:29:50.926 --> 02:29:52.326
Mheshimiwa Borden, karibu.

02:29:52.360 --> 02:29:53.829
Tafadhali kaa.

02:29:54.997 --> 02:29:57.398
Bwana Borden,

02:29:57.431 --> 02:30:00.002
wakati wa uchunguzi wako
kwa Dk. Oppenheimer,

02:30:00.035 --> 02:30:01.669
ulifikia
hitimisho fulani?

02:30:01.702 --> 02:30:04.006
- Nilifanya.
- Na ilikuja wakati

02:30:04.039 --> 02:30:05.506
ulipojieleza
hitimisho hizo

02:30:05.540 --> 02:30:07.542
katika barua kwa
Bw. J. Edgar Hoover

02:30:07.575 --> 02:30:09.510
wa Ofisi ya Shirikisho
ya Uchunguzi?

02:30:09.544 --> 02:30:10.955
- Hiyo ni sahihi.
- Kabla ya kuandika

02:30:10.979 --> 02:30:12.756
ya barua, ulijadili
uandishi wa barua

02:30:12.780 --> 02:30:15.083
na mtu yeyote anayehusishwa na
Tume ya Nishati ya Atomiki?

02:30:15.117 --> 02:30:16.717
sikufanya hivyo.

02:30:16.751 --> 02:30:18.096
Asante, na wewe
unayo nakala ya barua?

02:30:18.120 --> 02:30:19.720
Nina moja
mbele yangu.

02:30:19.754 --> 02:30:21.857
Je! ungependa kuwa hivyo
fadhili kama kuisoma, bwana?

02:30:21.890 --> 02:30:23.424
"Mpendwa Mheshimiwa Hoover,

02:30:23.457 --> 02:30:24.903
madhumuni ya hili
barua ni kueleza…”

02:30:24.927 --> 02:30:26.971
Lo, samahani, nina
samahani, ikiwa ningeweza kuwa na ...

02:30:26.995 --> 02:30:29.363
Kusudi ni nini
ya kuchelewa?

02:30:29.397 --> 02:30:30.866
Yeye tu gonna
soma barua.

02:30:30.899 --> 02:30:32.433
Mheshimiwa Mwenyekiti,

02:30:32.466 --> 02:30:34.468
hii ni ya kwanza kuwa nayo
kuonekana kwa barua hii,

02:30:34.502 --> 02:30:35.770
na ninaona taarifa hapa, uh,

02:30:35.803 --> 02:30:37.772
angalau moja, ya a
aina ambayo sidhani

02:30:37.805 --> 02:30:39.774
mtu yeyote angependa
tazama nenda kwenye rekodi.

02:30:39.807 --> 02:30:42.577
Hizi ni tuhuma ambazo
hazijafanywa hapo awali.

02:30:42.610 --> 02:30:44.545
Hiyo sio sehemu ya
mashtaka kutoka kwa Nichols.

02:30:44.579 --> 02:30:46.714
Mashtaka ya aina hiyo
Sidhani kama wa hapa.

02:30:46.747 --> 02:30:48.917
Shahidi aliandika hivi
barua kwa hiari yake mwenyewe,

02:30:48.951 --> 02:30:51.519
kuweka ushahidi ambao una
tayari mbele ya bodi.

02:30:51.552 --> 02:30:53.155
Hitimisho lake ni
ushuhuda halali,

02:30:53.188 --> 02:30:55.090
kama vile...
hitimisho chanya

02:30:55.123 --> 02:30:56.457
ya marafiki wa Dk. Oppenheimer.

02:30:56.490 --> 02:30:57.993
Inakata njia zote mbili.

02:30:58.026 --> 02:31:00.461
Wakili amekaa kwa muda gani
kumiliki barua hii?

02:31:00.494 --> 02:31:01.864
sidhani mimi
inapaswa kuwa chini

02:31:01.897 --> 02:31:04.465
kuhojiwa
na wewe, Bw. Garrison.

02:31:04.498 --> 02:31:06.144
Bw. Garrison, aliyopewa
kwamba sisi kwenye bodi

02:31:06.168 --> 02:31:07.668
wote wamesoma barua,

02:31:07.702 --> 02:31:10.038
si ingekuwa bora
iko kwenye rekodi?

02:31:10.072 --> 02:31:11.539
Hebu tuendelee.

02:31:13.541 --> 02:31:15.010
"Mpendwa Mheshimiwa Hoover,

02:31:15.043 --> 02:31:18.479
"lengo la barua hii
ni kueleza maoni yangu

02:31:18.512 --> 02:31:19.815
"kulingana na miaka ya masomo

02:31:19.848 --> 02:31:22.617
"ya zilizopo
ushahidi wa siri,

02:31:22.650 --> 02:31:24.685
"kwamba pengine kuliko sivyo,

02:31:24.719 --> 02:31:29.590
"J. Robert Oppenheimer ni
wakala wa Umoja wa Kisovyeti.

02:31:29.624 --> 02:31:31.960
"Ifuatayo
hitimisho ni haki.

02:31:31.994 --> 02:31:36.832
"Moja, kati ya 1929 na 1942,
pengine kuliko sivyo,

02:31:36.865 --> 02:31:38.166
"J. Robert Oppenheimer

02:31:38.200 --> 02:31:40.501
"ilikuwa ya kutosha
Mkomunisti mgumu,

02:31:40.534 --> 02:31:42.637
"kwamba alijitolea
habari kwa Soviet.

02:31:42.670 --> 02:31:45.007
"Mbili, labda zaidi kuliko sivyo,

02:31:45.040 --> 02:31:49.610
"tangu amekuwa akifanya kazi
kama wakala wa ujasusi.

02:31:49.644 --> 02:31:52.480
"Tatu, labda zaidi kuliko sivyo,

02:31:52.513 --> 02:31:54.749
" tangu hapo ameigiza
chini ya agizo la Soviet

02:31:54.782 --> 02:31:57.518
katika kushawishi United
Sera ya kijeshi ya nchi ... "

02:31:57.551 --> 02:31:58.786
Samahani, Robert.

02:31:58.820 --> 02:32:00.164
"atomiki
nishati, akili

02:32:00.188 --> 02:32:01.565
- na sera ya kidiplomasia."
- Ni mtu yeyote

02:32:01.589 --> 02:32:03.225
atawahi kusema ukweli

02:32:03.258 --> 02:32:05.027
kuhusu nini kinaendelea hapa?

02:32:05.060 --> 02:32:08.596
<i>Tutafanya hivyo
sasa sikia kutoka kwa Dk. David Hill.</i>

02:32:17.839 --> 02:32:19.174
Dk Hill,

02:32:19.207 --> 02:32:21.843
ungejali
kutoa tamko?

02:32:22.978 --> 02:32:24.545
Asante.

02:32:24.578 --> 02:32:28.250
Nimeombwa kutoa ushahidi
Kuhusu Lewis Strauss

02:32:28.283 --> 02:32:30.685
Mwanaume ambaye ametoa
miaka ya utumishi

02:32:30.718 --> 02:32:33.688
katika nyadhifa za juu serikalini

02:32:33.721 --> 02:32:38.659
na ambaye anajulikana kuwa na bidii,
mchapakazi na mwenye akili.

02:32:39.660 --> 02:32:41.172
Maoni ninayopaswa
Express ni yangu mwenyewe,

02:32:41.196 --> 02:32:44.900
lakini ninaamini kuwa ninayo mengi
kusema itasaidia kuonyesha

02:32:44.933 --> 02:32:48.636
kwa nini wengi
wanasayansi katika nchi hii

02:32:48.669 --> 02:32:51.672
angependelea kumuona Bw. Strauss

02:32:51.706 --> 02:32:53.541
nje ya serikali kabisa.

02:32:55.576 --> 02:32:58.080
Wewe ni... Wewe ni
akimaanisha uadui

02:32:58.113 --> 02:32:59.580
ya wanasayansi fulani

02:32:59.613 --> 02:33:01.249
iliyoelekezwa kwa Bw. Strauss

02:33:01.283 --> 02:33:03.517
kwa sababu yake
kujitolea kwa usalama

02:33:03.551 --> 02:33:06.554
kama inavyoonyeshwa katika
Mambo ya Oppenheimer?

02:33:09.024 --> 02:33:10.292
Hapana.

02:33:10.325 --> 02:33:12.727
Kwa sababu ya
ulipizaji kisasi wa kibinafsi

02:33:12.760 --> 02:33:14.997
alionyesha kupinga
Oppenheimer Dk.

02:33:16.664 --> 02:33:18.799
Agizo.

02:33:18.834 --> 02:33:19.868
Agiza!

02:33:19.901 --> 02:33:25.173
Inaonekana kwa wanasayansi wengi
kuzunguka nchi hii

02:33:25.207 --> 02:33:26.741
kwamba Robert Oppenheimer
sasa inakuwa

02:33:26.774 --> 02:33:29.011
pilloried na kuweka
kupitia majaribu

02:33:29.044 --> 02:33:32.147
kwa sababu alijieleza
maoni yake ya uaminifu.

02:33:33.148 --> 02:33:35.217
Dk. Bush, nilifikiri mimi
alikuwa akifanya huduma

02:33:35.250 --> 02:33:36.985
kwa nchi yangu lini
kusikiliza kesi hii.

02:33:37.019 --> 02:33:41.156
Hakuna bodi katika nchi hii
inapaswa kukaa katika hukumu ya mtu

02:33:41.189 --> 02:33:43.825
kwa sababu alijieleza
maoni yenye nguvu.

02:33:43.859 --> 02:33:46.928
Ikiwa unataka kujaribu hiyo
kesi, unapaswa kunijaribu.

02:33:46.962 --> 02:33:50.966
Samahani, waheshimiwa,
ikiwa nitachanganyikiwa,

02:33:50.999 --> 02:33:52.200
lakini mimi niko.

02:33:52.234 --> 02:33:54.202
Dr Hill, tumesikia tayari

02:33:54.236 --> 02:33:56.670
alichofanya Bw. Strauss
si kuleta mashtaka

02:33:56.704 --> 02:33:59.774
au kushiriki katika mashauri
dhidi ya Dk Oppenheimer.

02:33:59.807 --> 02:34:02.310
Suala la Oppenheimer lilikuwa

02:34:02.344 --> 02:34:04.712
kuanzishwa na kuendelea

02:34:04.745 --> 02:34:07.115
kwa kiasi kikubwa kupitia
animus ya Lewis Strauss.

02:34:08.716 --> 02:34:11.353
Oppenheimer alifanya mincemeat
nje ya nafasi ya Strauss

02:34:11.386 --> 02:34:12.988
kwenye usafirishaji wa
isotopu kwenda Norway,

02:34:13.021 --> 02:34:17.025
na Strauss hakusamehe kamwe
huyu udhalilishaji hadharani.

02:34:17.059 --> 02:34:19.660
Mjadala mwingine kati ya
walijikita kuzunguka

02:34:19.693 --> 02:34:22.663
tofauti zao katika
hukumu juu ya jinsi bomu H

02:34:22.696 --> 02:34:24.765
<i>ingechangia
usalama wa taifa.</i>

02:34:24.799 --> 02:34:26.767
Strauss akageuka
mfumo wa usalama wa wafanyikazi

02:34:26.801 --> 02:34:31.039
ili kuharibu
Ufanisi wa Oppenheimer,

02:34:31.073 --> 02:34:33.607
na Strauss aliweza
tafuta wanaume wachache wenye tamaa

02:34:33.641 --> 02:34:36.677
ambaye pia hakukubaliana naye
Nafasi za Oppenheimer

02:34:36.710 --> 02:34:39.747
na kumhusudu ufahari wake
katika duru za serikali.

02:34:39.780 --> 02:34:42.384
Nimewahi
kudhani, na bado kudhani,

02:34:42.417 --> 02:34:44.652
kwamba yeye ni mwaminifu kwake
Marekani.

02:34:44.685 --> 02:34:46.097
Ninaamini hivi. Na
nitaamini

02:34:46.121 --> 02:34:48.689
mpaka naona conclusive sana
ushahidi kwa kinyume.

02:34:48.722 --> 02:34:50.691
Je, wewe au huamini

02:34:50.724 --> 02:34:53.028
kwamba Dk Oppenheimer
ni hatari kwa usalama?

02:34:56.764 --> 02:34:58.033
Katika idadi kubwa ya kesi,

02:34:58.066 --> 02:35:00.035
Nimemwona Dk Oppenheimer
tenda kwa njia

02:35:00.068 --> 02:35:03.939
ambayo ilikuwa kwangu sana
ngumu kuelewa.

02:35:03.972 --> 02:35:05.974
Sikukubaliana nayo kabisa
katika masuala mengi,

02:35:06.007 --> 02:35:08.110
na matendo yake
kusema ukweli alionekana kwangu

02:35:08.143 --> 02:35:09.677
kuchanganyikiwa na ngumu.

02:35:09.710 --> 02:35:11.246
Kwa kiasi hiki, nahisi,

02:35:11.279 --> 02:35:14.382
Nataka kuona muhimu
maslahi ya nchi hii

02:35:14.416 --> 02:35:16.251
mikononi mwa mimi
kuelewa vizuri zaidi

02:35:16.284 --> 02:35:18.420
na kwa hivyo amini zaidi.

02:35:18.453 --> 02:35:21.223
- Asante, Daktari.
- Asante.

02:35:25.026 --> 02:35:26.128
samahani.

02:35:28.762 --> 02:35:30.932
<i>Umetikisa
mkono wake wa kutisha?</i>

02:35:30.966 --> 02:35:33.869
Oh, ningekuwa
mate usoni mwake.

02:35:33.902 --> 02:35:35.446
Sina uhakika bodi itafanya
wameshukuru hilo.

02:35:35.470 --> 02:35:37.048
Je, sivyo
kiungwana inakutosha?

02:35:37.072 --> 02:35:40.408
Vema, nadhani ninyi nyote
kuwa muungwana kupita kiasi.

02:35:40.442 --> 02:35:42.410
Grey lazima aone nini
Robb anafanya.

02:35:42.444 --> 02:35:44.379
Kwa nini asifanye hivyo
tu kumfungia?

02:35:44.412 --> 02:35:47.015
Na wewe unamshika mkono Teller.

02:35:47.048 --> 02:35:49.918
Unahitaji kuacha
kucheza shahidi.

02:35:50.919 --> 02:35:53.321
Chini ya sasa
Miongozo ya AEC,

02:35:53.355 --> 02:35:55.756
ungeweka wazi
Dk. Oppenheimer leo?

02:36:01.930 --> 02:36:04.299
Chini ya tafsiri yangu

02:36:04.332 --> 02:36:06.468
Sheria ya Nishati ya Atomiki,

02:36:06.501 --> 02:36:08.336
ambayo haikuwepo

02:36:08.370 --> 02:36:11.206
nilipoajiri
Dk. Oppenheimer mwaka 1942...

02:36:12.440 --> 02:36:15.844
Sikumsafisha leo,

02:36:15.877 --> 02:36:17.846
uh, kama ningekuwa kwenye tume.

02:36:17.879 --> 02:36:19.457
Nzuri. Asante,
Mkuu. Hiyo ndiyo yote.

02:36:19.481 --> 02:36:21.483
Lakini sidhani kama ningefanya
safisha yoyote kati ya watu hao.

02:36:21.516 --> 02:36:23.684
Ni hayo tu.

02:36:26.188 --> 02:36:28.323
Oppenheimer Dk
hakuwa na jukumu

02:36:28.356 --> 02:36:29.858
katika uteuzi
au kibali

02:36:29.891 --> 02:36:31.193
wa Klaus Fuchs, je!

02:36:31.226 --> 02:36:32.494
Hapana. Hakuna hata kidogo.

02:36:32.527 --> 02:36:34.129
Na haungetaka
kuondoka kwenye bodi hii

02:36:34.162 --> 02:36:36.932
na pendekezo lolote leo
kwamba uko hapa kuhoji

02:36:36.965 --> 02:36:39.000
uaminifu wake wa msingi
kwa Marekani

02:36:39.034 --> 02:36:40.435
katika uendeshaji wa Los Alamos?

02:36:40.468 --> 02:36:42.037
La hasha.

02:36:42.070 --> 02:36:44.072
Natumai sikuongoza
mtu yeyote kuamini vinginevyo

02:36:44.105 --> 02:36:45.739
kwa papo hapo.

02:36:45.773 --> 02:36:46.875
Asante Mkuu.

02:37:04.926 --> 02:37:07.195
Sawa. Hatupaswi
waendelee kusubiri.

02:37:07.229 --> 02:37:08.496
Atakuwa hapa.

02:37:08.530 --> 02:37:09.965
Hata wewe unamtaka hapa?

02:37:09.998 --> 02:37:12.500
Ni mjinga tu au kijana

02:37:12.534 --> 02:37:14.436
nadhani kumjua mtu
uhusiano wa mtu mwingine,

02:37:14.469 --> 02:37:16.770
na wewe sio, Lloyd.

02:37:18.340 --> 02:37:20.308
Kitty na mimi,

02:37:20.342 --> 02:37:22.410
sisi ni watu wazima.

02:37:22.444 --> 02:37:25.280
<i>Tumepitia
moto pamoja.</i>

02:37:25.313 --> 02:37:27.882
Atafanya vizuri.

02:37:27.916 --> 02:37:29.985
Je, unaweza kuelezea
maoni yako kuhusu Ukomunisti

02:37:30.018 --> 02:37:32.053
kama pro, anti, neutral?

02:37:32.087 --> 02:37:33.955
Kwa nguvu sana dhidi ya.

02:37:33.989 --> 02:37:36.124
Si-sijawa na la kufanya
na Ukomunisti katika... tangu...

02:37:36.157 --> 02:37:38.994
tangu 1936...

02:37:39.027 --> 02:37:41.896
tangu kabla sijakutana na Robert.

02:37:42.497 --> 02:37:44.332
Ni hayo tu.

02:37:44.366 --> 02:37:45.934
<i>Rekodi inaonyesha</i>

02:37:45.967 --> 02:37:47.569
<i>hiyo Oppenheimer
hakuhojiwa</i>

02:37:47.602 --> 02:37:50.839
<i>kwa kutopendelea na kutopendezwa
mshauri wa bodi ya Grey.</i>

02:37:50.872 --> 02:37:52.274
<i>Alihojiwa
na mwendesha mashtaka</i>

02:37:52.307 --> 02:37:53.975
<i>ambaye alitumia hila zote</i>

02:37:54.009 --> 02:37:55.810
<i>ya mwenye busara zaidi
historia ya kisheria.</i>

02:37:55.844 --> 02:37:57.279
Wewe
zinachaji sasa

02:37:57.312 --> 02:38:00.282
kwamba bodi ya Grey
kuruhusiwa kufunguliwa mashitaka.

02:38:00.315 --> 02:38:03.018
Ikiwa ningekuwa kwenye bodi ya Grey,

02:38:03.051 --> 02:38:05.020
Ningepinga
dhidi ya mbinu

02:38:05.053 --> 02:38:07.956
ya mtu ambaye alitumikia, kwa kweli,
kama mwendesha mashtaka.

02:38:07.989 --> 02:38:11.192
Mtu asiyeteuliwa na bodi

02:38:11.226 --> 02:38:13.295
lakini na Lewis Strauss.

02:38:15.297 --> 02:38:16.331
Huyu alikuwa nani?

02:38:17.632 --> 02:38:19.467
Samahani?

02:38:19.501 --> 02:38:20.568
Huyu alikuwa nani?

02:38:20.602 --> 02:38:22.037
Ah, Roger Robb.

02:38:22.070 --> 02:38:24.406
Bibi Oppenheimer.

02:38:28.610 --> 02:38:31.046
Je, ulikuwa na Mkomunisti
Kadi ya uanachama wa chama?

02:38:32.480 --> 02:38:34.582
Mimi... sina uhakika.

02:38:34.616 --> 02:38:36.117
Je, huna uhakika?

02:38:39.087 --> 02:38:40.088
Naam...

02:38:42.490 --> 02:38:44.225
Naam?

02:38:53.168 --> 02:38:56.137
Ninamaanisha, labda,
kitendo cha kujiunga na Chama

02:38:56.171 --> 02:38:59.941
inahitajika kutuma pesa
na kupokea kadi, hapana?

02:39:03.111 --> 02:39:04.245
Ndiyo.

02:39:09.617 --> 02:39:11.019
Pole.

02:39:11.653 --> 02:39:13.254
Ndiyo. Mm.

02:39:15.090 --> 02:39:17.092
Ni tu ilikuwa yote
zamani sana,

02:39:17.125 --> 02:39:18.960
- Mheshimiwa Robb, sivyo?
- Si kweli.

02:39:18.993 --> 02:39:20.228
Muda mrefu wa kutosha kusahau.

02:39:20.261 --> 02:39:21.639
Je, ulirudisha
kadi au kuipasua?

02:39:21.663 --> 02:39:23.264
Kadi ambayo uwepo wake
Nimesahau?

02:39:23.298 --> 02:39:25.100
Chama chako cha Kikomunisti
kadi ya uanachama.

02:39:25.133 --> 02:39:26.868
Huna wazo hata kidogo.

02:39:29.170 --> 02:39:31.940
Inaweza kutofautisha
kufanywa kati

02:39:31.973 --> 02:39:33.641
Ukomunisti wa Kisovieti na Ukomunisti?

02:39:33.675 --> 02:39:35.243
Naam, katika siku
nilipokuwa mwanachama,

02:39:35.276 --> 02:39:36.916
Nilidhani walikuwa
hakika mambo mawili.

02:39:36.945 --> 02:39:38.213
- Oh?
- Nilidhani hivyo

02:39:38.246 --> 02:39:40.115
Chama cha Kikomunisti
ya Marekani

02:39:40.148 --> 02:39:42.550
alikuwa na wasiwasi na
matatizo yetu ya ndani.

02:39:42.584 --> 02:39:44.052
Sasa siamini tena hili.

02:39:44.085 --> 02:39:45.129
Amini yote
jambo limeunganishwa pamoja

02:39:45.153 --> 02:39:46.421
na kuenea duniani kote,

02:39:46.454 --> 02:39:48.656
nami nimeamini haya
tangu nilipohama Chama

02:39:48.690 --> 02:39:50.158
Miaka 16 iliyopita.

02:39:50.191 --> 02:39:51.493
- Lakini ...
- Miaka kumi na saba iliyopita.

02:39:51.526 --> 02:39:52.927
Kosa langu.

02:39:52.961 --> 02:39:55.597
- Lakini ulisema ...
- Samahani, 18.

02:39:55.630 --> 02:39:57.899
Miaka kumi na nane iliyopita.

02:39:58.700 --> 02:40:00.010
Je!
kujua ukweli

02:40:00.034 --> 02:40:01.212
mume wako alikuwa
kutoa michango

02:40:01.236 --> 02:40:04.305
kwa Raia wa Uhispania
Vita vya marehemu kama 1942?

02:40:04.339 --> 02:40:06.217
Nilijua kwamba Robert alitoa
pesa mara kwa mara.

02:40:06.241 --> 02:40:07.485
Je, ulijua hili
pesa zilikuwa zinakwenda

02:40:07.509 --> 02:40:08.943
kwenye chaneli za Chama cha Kikomunisti?

02:40:08.977 --> 02:40:10.412
Je, humaanishi "kupitia"?

02:40:10.445 --> 02:40:12.213
- Msamaha?
- Nadhani unamaanisha

02:40:12.247 --> 02:40:14.048
"kupitia Chama cha Kikomunisti
vituo," sivyo?

02:40:14.082 --> 02:40:15.316
- Ndiyo!
- Ndiyo?

02:40:15.350 --> 02:40:17.252
- Ndiyo!
- Ndiyo.

02:40:17.285 --> 02:40:20.989
Basi itakuwa sawa kusema
kwamba hii ilimaanisha kwamba kufikia 1942,

02:40:21.022 --> 02:40:22.323
mume wako alikuwa hajaacha

02:40:22.357 --> 02:40:24.292
kuwa na chochote cha kufanya
na Chama cha Kikomunisti?

02:40:24.325 --> 02:40:26.127
Si lazima
jibu ndiyo au hapana.

02:40:26.161 --> 02:40:27.538
Unaweza kujibu hilo
kwa njia yoyote unayotaka.

02:40:27.562 --> 02:40:29.431
Najua hilo, asante.

02:40:29.464 --> 02:40:31.166
Ni swali lako.

02:40:31.199 --> 02:40:33.101
- Haijasemwa ipasavyo.
- Je, unaelewa

02:40:33.134 --> 02:40:34.369
- ninapata nini?
- Ninafanya.

02:40:34.402 --> 02:40:35.679
Basi kwa nini usifanye hivyo
jibu hivyo?

02:40:35.703 --> 02:40:37.305
Maana sipendi maneno yako.

02:40:37.338 --> 02:40:39.274
"Kuwa na chochote cha kufanya
na Chama cha Kikomunisti."

02:40:39.307 --> 02:40:41.109
Kwa sababu Robert kamwe
alikuwa na chochote cha kufanya

02:40:41.142 --> 02:40:42.444
pamoja na Mkomunisti
Chama kama vile.

02:40:42.477 --> 02:40:45.113
Najua alitoa pesa
kwa wakimbizi wa Uhispania.

02:40:45.146 --> 02:40:47.081
Najua alichukua
maslahi ya kiakili

02:40:47.115 --> 02:40:48.316
katika mawazo ya Kikomunisti...

02:40:48.349 --> 02:40:49.460
Je, kuna aina mbili
ya Wakomunisti?

02:40:49.484 --> 02:40:51.186
Wakomunisti wa kiakili

02:40:51.219 --> 02:40:53.154
na mzee wako wazi
Kamati ya kawaida?

02:40:54.155 --> 02:40:55.723
Naam, sikuweza
jibu hilo.

02:40:55.757 --> 02:40:58.526
I
pia hakuweza.

02:41:04.666 --> 02:41:06.468
Jioni.

02:41:06.501 --> 02:41:08.236
Robert, wewe
hawezi kushinda jambo hili.

02:41:08.269 --> 02:41:10.214
Ni mahakama ya kangaroo na
matokeo yaliyopangwa mapema.

02:41:10.238 --> 02:41:12.173
Kwa nini ujiweke
kupitia zaidi yake?

02:41:12.774 --> 02:41:15.210
Nina sababu zangu.

02:41:15.811 --> 02:41:17.245
Sawa.

02:41:17.278 --> 02:41:18.413
Usiku mwema.

02:41:23.117 --> 02:41:24.519
Ana uhakika.

02:41:25.453 --> 02:41:27.489
Sina hakika wewe
kuelewa, Albert.

02:41:27.522 --> 02:41:28.623
Hapana?

02:41:28.656 --> 02:41:32.160
Niliiacha nchi yangu
kamwe kurudi.

02:41:32.794 --> 02:41:34.762
Umeitumikia nchi yako vyema.

02:41:34.796 --> 02:41:38.433
Ikiwa hii ndio malipo
anakupa, basi ...

02:41:38.466 --> 02:41:42.103
labda unapaswa
mpe mgongo.

02:41:42.136 --> 02:41:44.772
Damn it, mimi kutokea kwa
penda nchi hii.

02:41:44.806 --> 02:41:47.408
Kisha waambie waende kuzimu.

02:41:47.442 --> 02:41:48.343
Inashangaza kutosha,

02:41:48.376 --> 02:41:51.446
hii sio tena a
kusikilizwa kwa uthibitisho,

02:41:51.479 --> 02:41:53.648
sasa ni majaribio...

02:41:53.681 --> 02:41:55.416
kuhusu kesi!

02:41:56.417 --> 02:41:57.728
Sio vizuri yeye
kuwaambia kila mtu

02:41:57.752 --> 02:41:59.053
ulianzisha mashauri.

02:41:59.087 --> 02:42:01.456
Hawezi kuthibitisha jambo la mungu.

02:42:01.489 --> 02:42:04.158
Hakika hawezi kuthibitisha hilo
Nilitoa faili kwa Borden.

02:42:04.192 --> 02:42:06.528
Hatuko mahakamani bwana.

02:42:06.561 --> 02:42:07.762
Hakuna mzigo wa ushahidi.

02:42:07.795 --> 02:42:10.164
Sawa. Hawahukumu...

02:42:10.198 --> 02:42:11.466
kukataa tu.

02:42:11.499 --> 02:42:14.402
Kwa nini Hill aje
hapa ili kuniangusha?

02:42:14.435 --> 02:42:16.070
Nini angle yake?

02:42:16.104 --> 02:42:18.206
Je, watu wanahitaji sababu
kufanya jambo sahihi?

02:42:18.239 --> 02:42:19.842
- Kama anavyoona.
- Nilikuambia,

02:42:19.875 --> 02:42:22.544
Oppenheimer sumu
wanasayansi dhidi yangu,

02:42:22.577 --> 02:42:24.279
kutoka kwa mkutano huo wa kwanza.

02:42:24.312 --> 02:42:27.549
<i>Sijui nini Oppenheimer
akamwambia siku hiyo,</i>

02:42:27.582 --> 02:42:30.318
lakini Einstein hakutaka
hata kukutana na macho yangu.

02:42:31.419 --> 02:42:34.522
<i>Oppenheimer anajua jinsi
kujidanganya mwenyewe.</i>

02:42:34.556 --> 02:42:35.824
Na huko Los Alamos,

02:42:35.858 --> 02:42:38.192
aliwinda
naivete wa wanasayansi

02:42:38.226 --> 02:42:40.528
ambao walidhani watapata kusema
jinsi tulivyotumia kazi zao,

02:42:40.562 --> 02:42:43.565
lakini usifikirie yeye
alikuwa mjinga mwenyewe.

02:42:43.598 --> 02:42:44.867
Daktari.

02:42:44.900 --> 02:42:46.869
Wakati wa kazi yako
bomu ya hidrojeni,

02:42:46.902 --> 02:42:50.572
ulikatazwa
kwa shida zozote za kimaadili?

02:42:50.605 --> 02:42:52.240
Ndiyo, bila shaka.

02:42:52.273 --> 02:42:53.584
Lakini bado uliendelea
na kazi yako, sivyo?

02:42:53.608 --> 02:42:55.844
Ndiyo, kwa sababu hii ilikuwa
kazi ya uchunguzi,

02:42:55.878 --> 02:42:58.112
haikuwa
maandalizi ya silaha.

02:42:58.146 --> 02:43:00.214
Unamaanisha ilikuwa zaidi ya
a... safari ya kitaaluma.

02:43:00.248 --> 02:43:02.150
Hapana, si jambo la kitaaluma

02:43:02.183 --> 02:43:03.594
kama unaweza kujenga
bomu ya hidrojeni.

02:43:03.618 --> 02:43:05.219
Ni suala la maisha na kifo.

02:43:05.253 --> 02:43:06.621
Kufikia 1942, ulikuwa
kusukuma kikamilifu

02:43:06.654 --> 02:43:08.232
maendeleo ya
bomu la hidrojeni, sivyo?

02:43:08.256 --> 02:43:09.490
Kusukuma sio neno sahihi.

02:43:09.524 --> 02:43:11.459
Kuiunga mkono na
kuifanyia kazi, ndio.

02:43:11.492 --> 02:43:13.829
Hivyo ni lini haya maadili
mashaka huwa na nguvu sana

02:43:13.862 --> 02:43:15.496
uliyoyapinga kikamilifu

02:43:15.530 --> 02:43:17.198
maendeleo ya
bomu ya hidrojeni?

02:43:17.231 --> 02:43:19.200
Ilipopendekezwa
kuwa ndio sera

02:43:19.233 --> 02:43:21.402
ya Marekani kufanya
mambo haya kwa gharama yoyote

02:43:21.436 --> 02:43:23.438
bila kuzingatia
usawa kati ya silaha hizi

02:43:23.471 --> 02:43:26.541
na silaha za atomiki kama
sehemu ya arsenal yetu.

02:43:27.910 --> 02:43:29.845
Maadili yanasumbua nini
inahusiana na hilo?

02:43:29.878 --> 02:43:31.914
Wha... Maadili yanasumbua nini

02:43:31.947 --> 02:43:33.481
- inahusiana nayo?
- Ndiyo.

02:43:33.514 --> 02:43:35.583
Oppenheimer alitaka
kumiliki bomu la atomiki.

02:43:35.617 --> 02:43:37.518
Alitaka kuwa mwanaume
aliyeihamisha Dunia.

02:43:37.552 --> 02:43:40.722
Anazungumza juu ya kuweka
jini wa nyuklia

02:43:40.755 --> 02:43:42.223
kurudi kwenye chupa.

02:43:42.256 --> 02:43:43.391
Naam, niko hapa kukuambia

02:43:43.424 --> 02:43:45.627
kwamba namjua J.
Robert Oppenheimer,

02:43:45.660 --> 02:43:49.764
na kama angeweza kufanya yote
juu, angefanya yote sawa.

02:43:49.797 --> 02:43:52.835
Unajua hajawahi kusema hata siku moja
kwamba anajuta Hiroshima?

02:43:52.868 --> 02:43:55.737
Angeifanya kote. Kwa nini?

02:43:55.770 --> 02:43:57.205
Kwa sababu ilimfanya

02:43:57.238 --> 02:43:58.874
muhimu zaidi
mtu aliyewahi kuishi.

02:43:58.907 --> 02:44:01.242
Naam, tume...

02:44:01.275 --> 02:44:03.378
tumetumia bure
bomu la atomiki...

02:44:03.411 --> 02:44:05.513
Kwa kweli, daktari,
ulisaidia katika kuchagua

02:44:05.546 --> 02:44:06.958
lengo la kuacha
bomu la atomiki huko Japan,

02:44:06.982 --> 02:44:08.650
- si wewe?
- Ndiyo.

02:44:08.683 --> 02:44:10.327
Kweli, basi ulijua,
hukufanya hivyo kwa kuangusha

02:44:10.351 --> 02:44:12.520
bomu hilo la atomiki kwenye
lengo ulilochagua,

02:44:12.553 --> 02:44:13.965
kwamba maelfu
raia wangeuawa

02:44:13.989 --> 02:44:15.723
au kujeruhiwa, ni sawa?

02:44:15.757 --> 02:44:17.659
Ndio, sio wengi
kama ilivyotokea...

02:44:17.692 --> 02:44:19.895
Oh. Naam, ni ngapi
waliuawa au kujeruhiwa?

02:44:19.928 --> 02:44:21.796
- 70,000.
- 70,000

02:44:21.830 --> 02:44:22.898
huko Hiroshima na ...

02:44:22.931 --> 02:44:24.365
110,000 kwa wote.

02:44:24.399 --> 02:44:25.800
Katika siku
ya kila bomu?

02:44:27.769 --> 02:44:28.937
Ndiyo.

02:44:28.971 --> 02:44:30.547
Na katika wiki na
miaka iliyofuata?

02:44:30.571 --> 02:44:33.274
Imewekwa mahali fulani
kati ya 50 na 100,000.

02:44:33.307 --> 02:44:35.410
- 220,000 walikufa angalau?
- Ndiyo.

02:44:35.443 --> 02:44:37.345
Kuna makosa yoyote ya kimaadili kuhusu hilo?

02:44:38.713 --> 02:44:39.815
Ya kutisha.

02:44:39.848 --> 02:44:41.416
Lakini hata hivyo ulishuhudia humu ndani

02:44:41.449 --> 02:44:43.819
kwamba kulipuliwa kwa Hiroshima
ilifanikiwa sana.

02:44:43.852 --> 02:44:45.420
- Imefanikiwa kiufundi.
- Oh!

02:44:45.453 --> 02:44:47.221
Kitaalam, ilikuwa
mafanikio sana.

02:44:47.255 --> 02:44:48.732
Na pia inadaiwa
wamesaidia kumaliza vita.

02:44:48.756 --> 02:44:50.725
Je, ungekuwa ndani
msaada wa kushuka

02:44:50.758 --> 02:44:52.694
ya bomu la hidrojeni kwenye Hiroshima?

02:44:52.727 --> 02:44:54.262
Hiyo haingekuwa na maana hata kidogo.

02:44:54.295 --> 02:44:56.731
- Kwa nini?
- Lengo ni ndogo sana.

02:44:56.764 --> 02:44:59.267
Naam, tuseme kulikuwa na
imekuwa shabaha huko Japan

02:44:59.300 --> 02:45:00.778
kubwa ya kutosha kwa a
silaha ya nyuklia,

02:45:00.802 --> 02:45:02.579
ungekuwa umepingwa
kwa kuiacha?

02:45:02.603 --> 02:45:04.448
Hili halikuwa tatizo
ambayo nilikumbana nayo...

02:45:04.472 --> 02:45:05.917
Naam, ninakabiliana
wewe nayo sasa, bwana.

02:45:05.941 --> 02:45:07.709
Yote ilikuwa ni sehemu ya mpango wake.

02:45:07.742 --> 02:45:09.310
Alitaka utukufu,

02:45:09.343 --> 02:45:11.512
hatia isiyo ya kweli ya
anayejiona kuwa muhimu

02:45:11.546 --> 02:45:13.015
kuvaa kama taji ya fuckin '.

02:45:13.048 --> 02:45:16.484
Sema, “Hapana, hatuwezi
nenda kwenye barabara hii,"

02:45:16.517 --> 02:45:19.320
hata kama alijua tunapaswa kufanya hivyo.

02:45:19.353 --> 02:45:20.899
Je! ungekuwa
kinyume na kushuka

02:45:20.923 --> 02:45:22.590
ya thermonuclear
silaha juu ya Japan

02:45:22.623 --> 02:45:24.869
- kwa sababu ya kasoro za maadili?
- Ndio, naamini ningefanya, bwana.

02:45:24.893 --> 02:45:26.594
Naam, je!
kupinga kushuka

02:45:26.627 --> 02:45:28.639
ya bomu la atomiki huko Hiroshima
kwa sababu ya ukiukwaji wa maadili?

02:45:28.663 --> 02:45:30.307
Tumeweka hoja zetu...

02:45:30.331 --> 02:45:31.733
Hapana, wewe, wewe, wewe.
nakuuliza.

02:45:31.766 --> 02:45:33.410
- Niliweka ... niliweka ...
- Sio sisi. Wewe, wewe, wewe!

02:45:33.434 --> 02:45:35.037
Hoja zetu
dhidi ya kuiacha,

02:45:35.070 --> 02:45:36.604
lakini sikuidhinisha.

02:45:36.637 --> 02:45:38.339
Unamaanisha baada ya
kufanya kazi usiku na mchana

02:45:38.372 --> 02:45:39.741
kwa miaka mitatu
kutengeneza bomu,

02:45:39.774 --> 02:45:41.614
kisha ukabishana
matumizi yake?

02:45:41.642 --> 02:45:44.345
Niliulizwa na
Katibu wa Vita

02:45:44.378 --> 02:45:45.747
maoni ya nini
wanasayansi walikuwa.

02:45:45.780 --> 02:45:48.516
Nilimpa maoni
dhidi na maoni ya.

02:45:48.549 --> 02:45:50.561
Uliunga mkono kuangusha
ya bomu la atomi huko Japan.

02:45:50.585 --> 02:45:52.063
- Unamaanisha nini "msaada"?
- Je!

02:45:52.087 --> 02:45:53.564
- Uliunga mkono!
- Unamaanisha nini "msaada"?

02:45:53.588 --> 02:45:54.933
Kweli, umesaidia kuchagua
walengwa, sivyo?

02:45:54.957 --> 02:45:56.591
Nilifanya kazi yangu.

02:45:56.624 --> 02:45:58.368
Sikuwa katika uundaji wa sera
nafasi katika Los Alamos.

02:45:58.392 --> 02:46:00.038
Ningefanya chochote
Niliombwa kufanya.

02:46:00.062 --> 02:46:02.330
Naam, basi ungekuwa na
alijenga bomu H pia,

02:46:02.363 --> 02:46:03.498
- si wewe?
- Sikuweza.

02:46:03.531 --> 02:46:05.433
Sikukuuliza hivyo, Daktari!

02:46:05.466 --> 02:46:07.802
Na ripoti ya GAC
uliyoandika pamoja

02:46:07.836 --> 02:46:09.704
baada ya Soviet
mtihani wa atomiki alisema

02:46:09.737 --> 02:46:12.406
bomu Super lazima
isijengwe kamwe!

02:46:12.440 --> 02:46:13.775
Tulimaanisha nini,
nilichomaanisha ni...

02:46:13.808 --> 02:46:15.878
- Nini wewe, nani? WHO?
- Nilichomaanisha ...

02:46:17.645 --> 02:46:19.085
Na sivyo
Warusi hufanya chochote

02:46:19.114 --> 02:46:21.382
ili kuongeza nguvu zao?

02:46:21.415 --> 02:46:23.393
Ikiwa tulifanya
hivyo, wangelazimika kuifanya.

02:46:23.417 --> 02:46:25.453
Juhudi zetu zingeweza tu
ongeza juhudi zao,

02:46:25.486 --> 02:46:27.588
kama ilivyokuwa na
bomu la atomiki.

02:46:27.622 --> 02:46:31.026
"Kama ilivyokuwa na
bomu la atomiki," haswa!

02:46:31.059 --> 02:46:35.797
Hakuna ukiukwaji wa maadili ndani
1945, mengi mnamo 1949.

02:46:39.935 --> 02:46:41.769
Dk. Oppenheimer...

02:46:43.437 --> 02:46:46.041
nguvu yako ilikuwa lini
imani za maadili zinakua

02:46:46.074 --> 02:46:48.877
kwa heshima na
bomu ya hidrojeni?

02:46:55.918 --> 02:46:58.821
Ilipodhihirika kwangu

02:46:58.854 --> 02:47:02.490
ambayo tungependelea
kutumia silaha yoyote tuliyokuwa nayo.

02:47:04.927 --> 02:47:07.428
<i>J. Robert
Oppenheimer, shahidi.</i>

02:47:07.461 --> 02:47:10.065
Nilimpa haswa
alichokuwa akitaka.

02:47:10.098 --> 02:47:12.366
Ili kukumbukwa kwa Utatu,

02:47:12.400 --> 02:47:15.003
sio Hiroshima,

02:47:15.037 --> 02:47:17.471
sio Nagasaki.

02:47:20.008 --> 02:47:22.710
Anapaswa kunishukuru.

02:47:22.743 --> 02:47:25.680
Naam, yeye si.

02:47:27.515 --> 02:47:29.117
Bado tuna kura za kutosha,

02:47:29.151 --> 02:47:30.819
au ni taji
wakati wa kazi yangu

02:47:30.853 --> 02:47:34.990
karibu kuwa wengi zaidi
kudhalilishwa hadharani kwa maisha yangu?

02:47:35.023 --> 02:47:37.592
Seneti kamili iko karibu kupiga kura.

02:47:37.625 --> 02:47:38.793
Utapitia.

02:47:38.827 --> 02:47:40.461
Kubwa, kisha kukusanya
vyombo vya habari vya kuchekesha.

02:47:40.494 --> 02:47:42.463
Dk. J.
Robert Oppenheimer.

02:47:42.496 --> 02:47:45.466
Bodi hii, ikiwa
nilisikia ushuhuda kutoka kwenu

02:47:45.499 --> 02:47:48.636
na mengi yako ya sasa
na wenzake wa zamani,

02:47:48.669 --> 02:47:50.671
imekuja kwa
hitimisho la kauli moja

02:47:50.705 --> 02:47:53.808
kwamba wewe ni raia mwaminifu.

02:47:55.110 --> 02:47:56.744
Hata hivyo,

02:47:56.777 --> 02:48:00.414
katika nuru yako
vyama vinavyoendelea

02:48:00.448 --> 02:48:01.716
na kupuuza

02:48:01.749 --> 02:48:03.886
kwa usalama
vifaa vya nchi hii,

02:48:03.919 --> 02:48:07.455
pamoja na yako
tabia fulani ya kutatanisha

02:48:07.488 --> 02:48:10.025
kwenye mpango wa bomu ya hidrojeni

02:48:10.058 --> 02:48:11.592
na ya kusikitisha
ukosefu wa uwazi

02:48:11.626 --> 02:48:13.996
katika baadhi yako
majibu kwa bodi hii,

02:48:14.029 --> 02:48:16.899
tumepiga kura mbili kwa moja

02:48:16.932 --> 02:48:20.035
kukataa kufanywa upya kwa
kibali chako cha usalama.

02:48:20.068 --> 02:48:23.171
Maoni kamili yaliyoandikwa, na
upinzani kutoka kwa Bw. Evans,

02:48:23.205 --> 02:48:26.707
itatolewa kwa
AEC katika siku zijazo.

02:48:26.741 --> 02:48:28.409
Hiyo ndiyo yote.

02:48:32.180 --> 02:48:33.514
- Gordon...
- Roger.

02:48:38.552 --> 02:48:40.454
<i>Robert.</i>

02:48:41.089 --> 02:48:42.623
Robert.

02:48:45.093 --> 02:48:46.594
Usi...

02:48:48.964 --> 02:48:52.167
Usichukue shuka.

02:48:53.567 --> 02:48:54.970
Pata a
picha naye.

02:48:55.003 --> 02:48:56.238
Bwana, bwana.

02:48:56.271 --> 02:48:58.739
Mbili
dakika. Dakika mbili.

02:48:58.773 --> 02:48:59.984
- Utapata risasi yako.
- Tafadhali, bwana.

02:49:00.008 --> 02:49:01.575
Tumesubiri kwa muda mrefu sana.

02:49:01.609 --> 02:49:02.619
- Jioni, bwana.
- Njoo nje.

02:49:02.643 --> 02:49:03.678
Bwana, bwana!

02:49:03.711 --> 02:49:05.047
Je, ni rasmi?

02:49:07.149 --> 02:49:08.549
Naam, kulikuwa na,

02:49:08.582 --> 02:49:11.719
uh, michache
punguzo zisizotarajiwa.

02:49:16.158 --> 02:49:18.827
Nimekataliwa. Ndio?

02:49:18.860 --> 02:49:20.829
- Ninaogopa hivyo, bwana.
- Sawa.

02:49:28.536 --> 02:49:29.603
Je, ni akina nani walioshikiliwa?

02:49:29.637 --> 02:49:32.573
Um, walikuwa watatu,

02:49:32.606 --> 02:49:35.543
wakiongozwa na seneta mdogo
kutoka Massachusetts.

02:49:35.576 --> 02:49:36.988
Kijana akijaribu
ajifanyie jina,

02:49:37.012 --> 02:49:39.580
hakupenda ulicho nacho
alifanya kwa Oppenheimer.

02:49:39.613 --> 02:49:40.748
Jina lake nani?

02:49:40.781 --> 02:49:42.985
Oh, Kennedy.

02:49:43.018 --> 02:49:44.820
John F. Kennedy.

02:49:48.290 --> 02:49:49.690
Kitty?

02:49:55.763 --> 02:49:59.167
Je, ulifikiri kwamba kama wewe
waache waweke lami na kukunyooshea manyoya,

02:49:59.201 --> 02:50:01.769
kwamba dunia
ungekusamehe?

02:50:05.307 --> 02:50:06.741
Haitafanya hivyo.

02:50:09.111 --> 02:50:10.511
Tutaona.

02:50:20.288 --> 02:50:22.290
Goddamn it.

02:50:23.825 --> 02:50:26.761
Wewe
aliniambia nitakuwa sawa.

02:50:26.794 --> 02:50:29.164
Ndio, sikuwa nayo
ukweli wote, sivyo?

02:50:29.197 --> 02:50:30.765
Hapa kuna ukweli.

02:50:30.798 --> 02:50:32.642
Rais Eisenhower
alishinda medali ya Uhuru

02:50:32.666 --> 02:50:34.102
kwenye kifua changu mwaka jana

02:50:34.136 --> 02:50:36.637
kwa sababu nimefanya kila wakati
nini haki kwa nchi hii.

02:50:36.670 --> 02:50:39.174
Hawanitaki
katika chumba cha Baraza la Mawaziri?

02:50:39.207 --> 02:50:41.642
Naam, hiyo ni ... hiyo ni sawa.

02:50:41.675 --> 02:50:44.012
Labda wanapaswa tu
mwalike Oppenheimer badala yake.

02:50:44.046 --> 02:50:45.080
Labda watafanya hivyo.

02:50:46.081 --> 02:50:47.315
Nilikuambia,

02:50:47.349 --> 02:50:49.985
aliwageuza wanasayansi
dhidi yangu mmoja baada ya mwingine,

02:50:50.018 --> 02:50:52.187
akianza na Einstein. I
nilikuambia kuhusu, uh, Einstein.

02:50:52.220 --> 02:50:53.654
Nilimwona karibu na bwawa.

02:50:53.687 --> 02:50:55.190
Ulifanya, lakini unajua, bwana,

02:50:55.223 --> 02:50:57.225
kwani hakuna anayejua kweli

02:50:57.259 --> 02:50:58.894
walichosema
kila mmoja siku hiyo,

02:50:58.927 --> 02:51:02.964
inawezekana hawakufanya hivyo
kuzungumzia wewe kabisa?

02:51:02.998 --> 02:51:06.134
Je, inawezekana walizungumza
kuhusu kitu, uh,

02:51:06.168 --> 02:51:07.601
muhimu zaidi?

02:51:07.635 --> 02:51:09.071
Mheshimiwa Strauss!

02:51:12.407 --> 02:51:14.809
Hapa! Mheshimiwa Strauss!

02:51:17.946 --> 02:51:21.216
Oh.

02:51:22.384 --> 02:51:23.684
Asante.

02:51:23.717 --> 02:51:26.221
Albert.

02:51:26.254 --> 02:51:28.223
Ah.

02:51:28.256 --> 02:51:30.758
Mwanaume wa wakati huu.

02:51:33.862 --> 02:51:37.232
Uliwahi kushikilia a-a
mapokezi kwangu.

02:51:37.265 --> 02:51:39.067
Katika Berkeley. Wewe
alinipa tuzo.

02:51:39.101 --> 02:51:40.969
- Hmm?
- Ndiyo.

02:51:41.870 --> 02:51:44.272
Ninyi nyote mlifikiri hivyo
Nilikuwa nimepoteza uwezo

02:51:44.306 --> 02:51:47.242
kuelewa nilichoanza.

02:51:47.275 --> 02:51:50.711
Kwa hivyo tuzo kweli
haikuwa kwangu,

02:51:50.744 --> 02:51:53.148
ilikuwa kwa ajili yenu nyote, hmm?

02:51:55.016 --> 02:51:57.018
Sasa ni zamu yako

02:51:57.052 --> 02:52:01.755
kukabiliana na matokeo
ya mafanikio yako.

02:52:02.690 --> 02:52:03.992
Na siku moja,

02:52:04.025 --> 02:52:06.660
wakati wameadhibiwa
unatosha...

02:52:08.063 --> 02:52:11.967
watakuhudumia
lax na saladi ya viazi.

02:52:15.703 --> 02:52:17.738
Fanya hotuba...

02:52:18.772 --> 02:52:20.275
<i>kukupa medali.</i>

02:52:21.977 --> 02:52:24.146
Habari, Frank.

02:52:24.179 --> 02:52:25.413
Una furaha, nina furaha.

02:52:32.387 --> 02:52:35.723
<i>Kukupiga mgongoni,
niambie yote yamesamehewa.</i>

02:52:37.259 --> 02:52:39.660
<i>Kumbuka tu...</i>

02:52:40.295 --> 02:52:42.164
<i>haitakuwa kwa ajili yako.</i>

02:52:46.434 --> 02:52:48.069
<i>Itakuwa kwa ajili yao.</i>

02:53:02.217 --> 02:53:03.751
Albert.

02:53:04.986 --> 02:53:08.456
Nilipokuja kwako na
mahesabu hayo,

02:53:08.490 --> 02:53:10.724
tulifikiri tunaweza
kuanza mmenyuko wa mnyororo

02:53:10.758 --> 02:53:14.229
hiyo ingeharibu
dunia nzima.

02:53:14.262 --> 02:53:17.731
Mm, nakumbuka vizuri.

02:53:17.765 --> 02:53:19.834
Je!

02:53:22.470 --> 02:53:24.206
Naamini tulifanya hivyo.